(94, '', 'LUMANTEK EZ-HS1 HDMI TO 3G/HS/SD-SDI CONVERTER', 21, 64, '', 'Converter', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp;LUMANTEK&nbsp; EZ-HS1&nbsp; HDMI TO 3G/HS/SD-SDI CONVERTER</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Description</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ez-converters are designed to keep low temperatures and consume less than 2 watts of power.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They are compact in size and, however, can handle resolutions between 480i and 1080p60.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are two models of ez-converter from which you can choose according to your needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video Input / Output Format:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 720 x 480i @ 59.94 / 60, 720 x 576i @ 50&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 1280 x 720p @ 50, 1280x 720p @ 59.94 / 60&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 1920 x 1080i @ 50, 1920 x 1080i @ 59.94 / 60&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 1920 x 1080p @ 23.94, 1920x1080p @ 25, 1920 x 1080p @ 29.97 / 30&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 1920 x 1080p @ 50, 1920 x 1080p @ 59.94 / 60&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio Sample Rate: 48KHz&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video Input Connector: HDMI (Type A) x 1&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video Output Connector: BNC x 2&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DC Input Power: 5V ~ 18V&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Consumptionn: &lt;2W&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions: 86.4 x 66.8 x 28.4 mm</p>\r\n', '1012201852215fd26e65cadb8.png', 3750, 0, 0, '2020-12-10 18:52:21', 0, '2020-12-10 18:52:21'),
