(104, '', 'Lumantek HD Encodulator MPEG-2 & H.264 HD ENCODER FOR IN-HOUSE BROADCASTING', 21, 64, '', 'Converter', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lumantek HD Encodulator MPEG-2 &amp; H.264 HD ENCODER FOR IN-HOUSE BROADCASTING</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HD Modulator</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>LUMANTEK HD Encodulator is HD encoder packaged with modulators in a single 1RU. Supported modulations include DTV standards such as ATSC, QAM, DVB-T, and DTMB.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD Encodulator is perfect for in-house broadcasting (MATV) since it allows cost-effective distribution within multi-storied buildings or high-density areas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MPEG-2 &amp; H.264</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Integrated with full HD Professional Broadcasting level encoder chipset, HD Encodulator guarantees professional HD quality encoded videos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PSIP / SI / PSI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By enabling PSIP, SI, and PSI, you can virtually set the channel number and customize.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DTV Modulator</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD Encodulator is integrated with DTV Modulators (DVB-T, DVB-C, QAM-B, ATSC, DTMB)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HD Encodulator [HAT-2110]</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input Ports</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 set x Component</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x SDI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x ASI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD Encodulator [HAT-2110]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output Ports</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x ASI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x RF</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x LAN (TS over IP)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Broadcast with HD Encodulator</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LUMANTEK&#39;s HD Encodulator is the perfect device for in-house broadcasting. It encodes videos into MPEG2 or H.264 and modulates to different formats. It can be controlled with a software and receives many types of input interfaces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HD Encodulator</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD MPEG2 &amp; MPEG4 ENCODER FOR TERRESTRIAL &amp; CABLE DISTRIBUTION</p>\r\n\r\n<p>User Interface</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Front Panel 4-line text