p>\r\n\r\n<p>AAC-LC, HE-AAC v1, HE-AAC v2 Stereo Encoder (for ISDB-T)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Sample rate: 32 / 44.1 / 48 KHz&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Sample rate: 32 / 44.1 / 48 KHz&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Pass through of Dolby Digital Stereo / 5.1 Ch, MPEG-1 Layer II and AAC-LC audio support</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported Modulations</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ATSC (8VSB) Modulation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Symbol Rate 10.762 MSps&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- SNR (MER): &gt;35 dB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DTMB Modulation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Modulation Support: Single carrier and TDS-OFDM s&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Modulation Mode: QPSK, 16 QAM, 32 QAM, 64 QAM&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Standards:GB20600-2006, ISO/IEC 13838-1, EN 50083-9&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- OGY/T 229.1-2008 (SIP)&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- SNR (MER): &gt;40 dB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DVB-C (ITU-T J.83 Annex A/C) Modulation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Constellation Types 16 QAM, 32 QAM, 64 QAM, 128 QAM, 256 QAM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Symbol Rates 0.87 ~ 7.2 MSps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Channel Bandwidth 1 ~ 8.280 MHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SNR (MER) &gt;40 dB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DVB-T Modulation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Modulation Mode QPSK, 16 QAM, 64 QAM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Transmission Mode 2K, 4K, 8K</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Channel Bandwidth 5, 6, 7, 8 MHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Code Rate 1/2, 2/3, 3/4, 5/6, 7/8</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Guard Interval 1/4, 1/8, 1/16, 1/32</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Frequency Range 50 ~ 870 MHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SNR (MER) &gt;40 dB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>QAM-B (ITU-T J.83 Annex B) Modulation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Constellation Types &amp; Symbol Rates: 64 QAM: 5.057 MSps , 256 QAM: 5.361 MSps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Channel Bandwidth: 6 MHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- SNR (MER): &gt;40 dB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RF Output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Connector: F-Type 75&Omega; 1ea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Maximum Output Level for 1 ch: +10 dBm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Maximum Output Level for 2 ch: +4 dBm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Maximum Output Level for 3 ch: 0 dBm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Maximum Output Level for 4 ch: -3 