(126, '', 'SWIT S-1073F 7\" Full HD Waveform LCD Monitor with S-7006S V-Mount Battery Plate', 6, 21, '', 'จอมอนิเตอร์ Swit', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>SWIT S-1073F 7&quot; Full HD Waveform LCD Monitor with S-7006S V-Mount Battery Plate</strong></em>7-inch FHD Waveform LCD Monitor<br />\r\n◆ 7&rdquo; optical bonding LCD, 1920&times;1200<br />\r\n◆ All metal housing, thinner and robust<br />\r\n◆ 2K/3G/HD/SD-SDI input and loop out<br />\r\n◆ HDMI input, loop out, converted to SDI out<br />\r\n◆ 16-ch Embedded audio meters with alert<br />\r\n◆ Select any 2 audio channels to output<br />\r\n◆ 9-step quick zoom-in and mapping<br />\r\n◆ Red/blue Focus assist and precision adjust<br />\r\n◆ Multi-camera logs to Rec709 conversion<br />\r\n◆ User 3DLUT cube import via USB stick<br />\r\n◆ Waveform,&nbsp;Vector scope, Histogram R/G/B/Y<br />\r\n◆ AFD, timecode, H/V delay, Zebra stripes<br />\r\n◆ Marker 4:3, 13:9, 14:9, 15:9, 1.85:1, 2.35:1<br />\r\n◆ False color, R/G/B/Mono, 100% colorbar<br />\r\n◆ GPI control and soft Tally display<br />\r\n◆ V / Gold mount and various DV plate install<br />\r\n◆ USB firmware upgrade<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7-inch Full HD LCD<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOptical bonding</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The S-1073F adopts a 7-inch LCD panel with LED backlight, optical bonding technical. The native resolution is Full HD 1920&times;1200, contrast 1000:1, and viewing angle is Horizontal: 160&deg; / Vertical: 160&deg;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input/Output Interfaces<br />\r\nSDI &amp; HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>S-1073F monitor supports:</li>\r\n	<li>2K/3G/HD/SD-SDI input &times; 2</li>\r\n	<li>2K/3G/HD/SD-SDI loop output &times; 1&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI 1.3 input &times; 1</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI 1.3 loop output &times; 1&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI to SDI output &times; 1 (share SDI loop port)</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm analog audio input &times; 1</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm analog audio output &times; 1</li>\r\n	<li>GPI/TALLY input &times; 1</li>\r\n	<li>USB &times; 1 (firmware upgrade)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Build-in HDMI to SDI Conversion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>S-1073F supports build-in HDMI to SDI conversion; share the SDI loop output port. It&rsquo;s same format conversion and supports the following HDMI formats: 480i, 576i, 720p (60 / 59.94 / 50), 1080i (60 / 59.94 / 50), 1080p (30 / 29.97 / 25 / 24 / 23.98)Note: When both SDI and HDMI input, if the current display source is SDI, the SDI output port is SDI loop; and if the current display source is HDMI, the SDI output port is HDMI conversion output.ล</p>\r\n', '1612201609215fda3131db23b.jpg', 46000, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 16:09:21', 0, '2020-12-16 16:09:21'),
