(162, '', 'จำหน่าย Lilliput 339/DW 7 นิ้ว FPV Monitor with Dual Built-in 5.8GHz Wireless (White)', 6, 19, '', 'จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput 339/DW 7&quot; FPV Monitor with Dual Built-in 5.8GHz Wireless Receiver (White)&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The white 339/DW 7&quot; FPV Monitor&nbsp;from Lilliput has dual built-in 5.8 GHz wireless receivers that cover 4 bands and a total of 32 channels. It has a display resolution of 1280 x 800 with an aspect ratio of 16:9. The included dual antennas can receive two different video signal channels and overlay the video signals on one monitor. Also multiple Picture-in-Picture (PiP) modes can be selected. The built-in receiver supports PAL/NTSC and can be switched automatically. The monitor is suitable for aerial enthusiasts and professional photographers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Monitor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features attractive IPS panels with 1280 x 800 resolution, 178&deg; wide viewing angle, and high brightness/contrast that provide a better viewing experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supports 32 channels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Included dual antennas can receive two different video signal channels and overlay the video signals on one monitor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multiple Picture-in-Picture (PiP) modes can be selected</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Integrated timer function supports up to 4-hour countdown, and it will alert when 1 minute left</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in 2600mAh battery supports up to 3 to 4 hours working time and provides battery level indicator</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wireless signal sensitivity indicator is convenient for users to monitor the video signal status of a UAV</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Receiver</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in 5.8 GHz wireless AV receiver</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supports PAL / NTSC switch automatically</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Simulation of composite video AV inputs, aerial camera connection</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No blue screen problem when the signal gets weak, from 100 to 2000m wireless distance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display</li>\r\n	<li>Panel 7&quot; IPS, LED backlit</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution 1280 x 800</li>\r\n	<li>Aspect Ratio 16:9</li>\r\n	<li>Brightness 400 cd/m2</li>\r\n	<li>Contrast 800:1</li>\r\n	<li>Viewing Angle 178/178&deg; (H/V)</li>\r\n	<li>Input</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless Receiver Input 2</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI 1</li>\r\n	<li>AV 1</li>\r\n	<li>Output</li>\r\n	<li>AV 1</li>\r\n	<li>Audio</li>\r\n	<li>Speaker 1</li>\r\n	<li>Earphone 1</li>\r\n	<li>Power</li>\r\n	<li>Current 1300 mA</li>\r\n	<li>Input Voltage 7 to 24 VDC</li>\r\n	<li>Battery Built-in 2600 mAh battery</li>\r\n	<li>Power Consumption &le; 18 W</li>\r\n	<li>Environmental</li>\r\n	<li>Operating Temperature -4 to 140&deg;F (-20 to 60&deg;C)</li>\r\n	<li>Storage Temperature -22 to 158&deg;F (-30 to 70&deg;C)</li>\r\n	<li>Mechanical</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions (L x W x D) 7 x 5 x 1&quot; (185 x 126 x 30 mm)</li>\r\n	<li>Weight 13.5 oz (385 g)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1612201704575fda3e39a165a.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:04:57', 0, '2020-12-16 17:04:57'),
(163, '', 'จำหน่าย Lilliput Dual 7 นิ้ว 3U 3G-SDI Monitor Rackmount', 6, 19, '', 'จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput RM-7028S</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The RM-7028S is Lilliput&#39;s rack mounted dual SDI monitor unit, featuring 2 IPS panels with 3G SDI connectivity. Perfect for live events and rack environments where space is a premium but quality is a necessity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The perfect unit for live events and shows. Featuring 2 IPS panels and 3G SDI connectivity and mountable in a 3U rack system or events managers board</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2 x 7 inch monitor with wide screen aspect ratio</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The RM-7028S features 2 x high definition IPS screens for amazing picture quality at an affordable price</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>178 degree viewing angle</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wide angle viewing allows the operator to see both monitors from one position, and opens up the rest of the technical team chance to see the show too</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>400 cd/m brightness</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High brightness panels let you view the screens comfortably in daylight. Perfect for gigs in the open air such as festivals</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>800:1 Contrast Ratio</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Crisp deep colours are possible with high contrast ratio monitors, letting you see accurately what is happening on your colour</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SDI and HDMI connection</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Multiple connectivity options</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check out the specification for the up to date information on the range of input options available on the product</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>SPECIFICATIONS&nbsp;</strong><strong>RM-7028S</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen size (diagonal)</li>\r\n	<li>2 x 7&quot; IPS monitors</li>\r\n	<li>Aspect ratio</li>\r\n	<li>16:9</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution (pixels)</li>\r\n	<li>1280&times;800 (native</li>\r\n	<li>Viewing angle (degrees)</li>\r\n	<li>178&ordm; x, 178&ordm; y</li>\r\n	<li>Brightness (cd/m&sup2;)</li>\r\n	<li>400</li>\r\n	<li>Contrast ratio</li>\r\n	<li>800:1</li>\r\n	<li>LCD backlight</li>\r\n	<li>LED</li>\r\n	<li>Video inputs</li>\r\n	<li>2 x 3G-SDI, 2 x HDMI, 2 x YPbPr, 2 x Composite, 2 x Tally Connection, 1 x USB Mini</li>\r\n	<li>Video outputs</li>\r\n	<li>2 x 3G-SDI, 2 x HDMI, 2 x YPbPr, 2 x Composite</li>\r\n	<li>Audio inputs</li>\r\n	<li>L+R</li>\r\n	<li>Touch screen inputs</li>\r\n	<li>None</li>\r\n	<li>Input power source</li>\r\n	<li>DC 12V</li>\r\n	<li>Operating temperature</li>\r\n	<li>-20&ordm;C to 60&ordm;C</li>\r\n	<li>Mount type</li>\r\n	<li>3U Rackmount panel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1612201706165fda3e8868486.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:06:16', 0, '2020-12-16 17:06:16'),
(164, '', 'จำหน่าย Lilliput RM-7024-VD Dual 7 นิ้ว Rackmount Monitors', 6, 19, '', 'จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput RM-7024-VD Dual 7&quot; Rackmount Monitors&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2x 7&quot; 800x480 LED LCD Displays</li>\r\n	<li>Composite, VGA, and DVI Inputs</li>\r\n	<li>140/120&deg; (H/V) Viewing Angle</li>\r\n	<li>3 RU Mounting</li>\r\n	<li>Independent Monitor Controls</li>\r\n	<li>Includes Remote Control</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Outfit your production setup with the RM-7024-VD Dual 7&quot; Rackmount</strong>&nbsp;Monitor from Lilliput for added monitoring options in a small space. The 3 RU chassis contains two 7&quot; monitors that can be driven by Component, VGA, or DVI inputs found on the rear panel. Each monitor is independent of the other and has its own control set and power switch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The LDC panels featured on this model are 800x480 in resolution, and able to display most common formats including 16:9 and 4:3 with minimal negative space. Because of its compact size and panel features, this monitor will fit well in broadcast workflows, studio production, surveillance, and A/V integration setups. A power supply and remote control are included for easy setup and operation right out of the box.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Two 7&quot; LED-backlit IPS monitors with 800 x 480 resolution</p>\r\n\r\n<p>400 cd/m&sup2; brightness and 500:1 contrast ratio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>140&deg; / 120&deg; (H/V) viewing angle</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aspect ratio settings among 15:9 (full screen), 16:9, and 4:3</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual VGA, Composite, and DVI inputs and loop through outputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multi-format compatibility</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Image flip (up / down / left / right)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Easy-to-navigate on-screen menus with 5-button control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Adjustable color temperature in VGA &amp; DVI mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Firm 