(167, '', 'จำหน่าย Lilliput TM-1018/O/P 10.1 นิ้ว Touchscreen LED Backlit Camera Monitor', 6, 19, '', 'จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput TM-1018/O/P 10.1&quot; Touchscreen LED Backlit Camera Monitor</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The TM-1018/O/P 10.1&rdquo; Touchscreen LED Backlit Camera Monitor</strong>&nbsp;from Lilliput is a field monitor with HDMI input &amp; output, designed for use with DSLR and higher standard cameras. With a high-quality panel, the monitor features a capacitive touchscreen function to access and operate the internal settings functions. The monitor also features a 3G-SDI connection for professional broadcasting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The monitor&rsquo;s integrated waveform, vectorscope, video analyzer, luminance/color/RGB histograms, luminance/RGB parade/YCbCr parade waveforms, and other waveform modes and measurement modes such as peaking, exposure, and audio level meter. These assist users to accurately monitor when shooting, making, and playing movies/videos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Level meter, histogram, waveform, and vectorscope can be displayed horizontally at the same time, while professional waveform measurement and color control helps the user realize and record natural color. Composite and component through BNC connectors and HDMI inputs cover all the bases for common broadcast applications. Also included is an HDMI output, avoiding the need of HDMI splitters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Histogram</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>RGB histogram shows the red, green, and blue channels in overlay&nbsp;<strong>histogram</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Color histogram shows histograms for each of the red, green, and blue channels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Luminance histogram shows the distribution of brightness in an image as a graph of luminance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Waveform</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Waveform monitoring consists of Luminance, YCbCr parade &amp; RGB parade Waveforms, which are used for measuring the brightness, luminance or chroma values from a video input signal</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It not only can warn the user for out-of-range conditions such as overexposure errors, but also assist with color correction &amp; camera white and black balance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vector</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vector scope shows how saturated the image is and where the pixels in the image land on the color spectrum</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It can also be displayed in various sizes &amp; positions, that allow users to monitor color gamut range in real time</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio Level Meter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Audio Level meters provide numerical indicators and headroom levels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They can generate accurate audio level displays to prevent errors during monitoring</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Widescreen Panel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 16:9 widescreen aspect ratio makes the TM-1018/S ideal for a variety of audio/video applications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It can be used in TV broadcast rooms, audio-visual installations, and as a preview monitor with professional camera crews for both on-camera and Video Village installations</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IPS LED Screen</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The TM-1018/S Monitor uses IPS screen panels that allow for high pixel pitch, which gives wide viewing angles and base resolutions of 1280 x 800, allowing upscaling to a full 1080p HD signal</p>\r\n\r\n<p>800:1 Contrast Ratio for Crisp Sharp Colors</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The TM-1018/s Monitor boasts a rich clear and sharp picture, thanks to a high contrast ratio and LED backlight</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The onboard matt LCD display means that all colors are well represented, and that there are no reflections evident on the screen</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The LED technology brings great benefits in terms of low power consumption, &quot;instant-on&quot; backlighting, and consistent brightness over years and years of use</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Made for DSLR Cameras</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The TM-1018/S Monitor has a large range of compatibility, with all major DSLR camera types supported using HDMI input</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It allows for convenient shot-taking, letting you to see the shot clearly before taking</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Advanced Camera Functions on the Fly</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packed with advanced features such as Peaking, Histograms, False Color Filtering, Exposure, and many more</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI Pass-Through</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The TM-1018/S Monitor includes an HDMI output which allows the user to duplicate the video content onto a second monitor, without the need of HDMI splitters</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The second monitor can be any size and picture quality will not be affected</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Optional Battery Plates</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery plate options allow for battery compatibility with 90% of major battery types, including a choice of 2 from Sony, Panasonic, and 2 types of Canon, with an extra charge Anton Bauer, and V-Type plates</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio Monitoring on Device</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TM-1018/S Monitor features an on-screen volume level for monitoring any excessive background noise or volume peaks whilst filming video and connecting via HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display</li>\r\n	<li>Panel 10.1&quot; (25.6 cm) LED IPS</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution 1280 x 800, supports up to 1920 x 1080</li>\r\n	<li>Aspect Ratio 16:9</li>\r\n	<li>Brightness 350cd/m2</li>\r\n	<li>Contrast 800:1</li>\r\n	<li>Viewing Angle 170&deg;/170&deg;(H/V)</li>\r\n	<li>Backlight LED</li>\r\n	<li>Input</li>\r\n	<li>Video 1 x HDMI, 1 x VGA, 1 x Composite (RCA)</li>\r\n	<li>Output</li>\r\n	<li>Video 1 x HDMI, 1 x Composite (RCA)</li>\r\n	<li>Audio 3.5 mm jack output, 1 x built-in speaker (&lt; 1 W)</li>\r\n	<li>Power</li>\r\n	<li>Current 1200 mA</li>\r\n	<li>Input Voltage 7 to 24 VDC</li>\r\n	<li>Operating Temperature 32 to 122&deg;F (0 to 50&deg;C)</li>\r\n	<li>Storage Temperature -4 to 140&deg;F (-20 to 60&deg;C)</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions (L x W x D) 9.8 x 6.7 x 1.1&quot; (25.0 x 17.0 x 2.9 cm)</li>\r\n	<li>Weight 22.2 oz (630 g)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1612201708135fda3efdd3685.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:08:13', 0, '2020-12-16 17:08:13'),
(168, '', 'จำหน่าย Lilliput FA1014/S 10.1 นิ้ว IPS On-Camera 3G-SDI/HDMI Monitor', 6, 19, '', 'จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput FA1014/S 10.1 นิ้ว IPS On-Camera 3G-SDI/HDMI Monitor</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>10.1&quot; 1280 x 800 IPS LCD Display</li>\r\n	<li>Supports NTSC/PAL &amp; HD</li>\r\n	<li>3G-SDI &amp; HDMI Inputs</li>\r\n	<li>170&deg; L / R, Top / Bot</li>\r\n	<li>Supports Frame Rates from 23.98 to 60p</li>\r\n	<li>12 VDC Power and Tally</li>\r\n	<li>Integrated Dustproof Front Panel</li>\r\n	<li>Remote Control and Shoe Mount Included</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>This FA1014/S 10.1&quot; IPS On-Camera 3G-SDI/HDMI Monitor</strong>&nbsp;from LILLIPUT is a field monitor that supports 1920 x 1080p, NTSC, and PAL video signals. It features a native resolution of 1280 x 800 and scales your video signal to display on its screen. The monitor supports Full HD video at 60p, and will also display footage shot at 23.98 (23.976), making it suitable for use with any camera that outputs HD video at 23.98. Featuring both HDMI and SDI in and out, the monitor can easily fit into most workflows.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The monitor supports a 170&deg; viewing angle for good color and contrast even when viewed from extremely off center. The monitor is powered by 12 VDC via a mini 4-pin XLR input, which makes it suitable for use in the field. the included 4-pin to mini-4-pin cable features pigtails that allow you to add Tally info. The integrated dustproof front panel protects the monitor&#39;s LCD screen from dust, moisture droplets and fingerprints. An included remote control allows you to access the monitor&#39;s functions and an included shoe mount allows you to mount the monitor on your camera&#39;s accessory shoe if you wish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>24 and 23.98 Frame Rate Support</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The monitor supports Full HD frame rates up to 60p in both NTSC and PAL compatible frame rates. The monitor also supports HD video at 24 fps to allow you to see video shot at cinema frame rates. 23.98 is also supported, which is the video version of 24 fps. 23.98 is actually recorded at 23.976 fps, but referred to as 23.98. This allows you to use this monitor to view footage shot by cameras that record at cinema frame rates.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Basic Display Controls</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dial</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MENU</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FN</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Advanced Display Controls</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Brightness</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contrast, Saturation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tint</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sharpness</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Volume</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Color Temp</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Center Marker</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Safety Marker</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aspect Ratio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H/V delay</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check Field</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pixel-to-Pixel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Underscan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zoom</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Freeze Input</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Auto</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H-Position</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V-Position</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phase</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Clock</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Language</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Reset</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Backlight</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Auto Light</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Image Flip</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Upgrade</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Functionality</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check Field: provides a monochrome view of your image using only the red, green, blue signals, or a grayscale of your image.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aspect Ratio: Adjust the monitor&#39;s aspect ratio from full screen, 4:3, or 16:9</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pixel-to-Pixel: 1:1 pixel-to-pixel mapping allows you to look at sections of your image without any scaling, so you can see the actual detail and not be fooled by scaling artifacts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H/V delay: H/V delay allows you to check your video&#39;s vertical blanking interval. This monitor allows you to check the H/V delay, or select either the horizontal delay or vertical delay individually.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Underscan: Shrinks the video image so that the edges are visible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Language: English, Chinese</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LCD Size 10.1&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aspect Ratio 16:9</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Display Resolution Native: 1280 x 800 (DOT)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supports: 1920 x 1080</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Brightness 350 cd/m2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contrast Ratio 800:1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Viewing Angle 170 / 170&deg; (H / V)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supported Resolutions SMPTE-425M-A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080p: 60/59.95/50/30/29.97/25/24/23.976/24sf</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SMPTE-274M</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080p: 30/29.97/25/24/24Sf/23.976</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080i: 60/59.94/50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SMPTE-296M</p>\r\n\r\n<p>720p: 60/59.94/50/30/25</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SMPTE-125M</p>\r\n\r\n<p>480i: 60/59.94</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ITU-R BT.656</p>\r\n\r\n<p>576i: 50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input / Output Connectors Input</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SDI: 1 x BNC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI: 1 x HDMI Type A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A/V: 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>VGA: 1 x VGA (D-sub 15-pin)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SDI: 1 x BNC</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI: 1 x HDMI Type A</li>\r\n	<li>Video: 1 x&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Earphone: 1</li>\r\n	<li>Speaker: 1 (&le;1W)</li>\r\n	<li>Language English</li>\r\n	<li>Chinese</li>\r\n	<li>Operating Temperature 32 to 122&deg;F / 0 to 50&deg;C</li>\r\n	<li>Storage Temperature -4 to 140&deg;F / -20 to 60&deg;C</li>\r\n	<li>Power 7 to 24 VDC</li>\r\n	<li>&le;12 W</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions (WxHxD) 9.8 x 6.7 x 1.3&quot; / 250.0 x 170.0 x 32.3 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Weight 23.3 oz / 660.0 g</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1612201708345fda3f127bd5c.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:08:34', 0, '2020-12-16 17:08:34'),
(169, '', 'จำหน่าย Lilliput FA1013 10.1 นิ้ว Field Monitor', 6, 19, '', 'จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput FA1013 10.1 นิ้ว &nbsp;Field Monitor</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>10.1&quot; 1024 x 600 LED LCD Display</li>\r\n	<li>Supports SD and HD Resolutions</li>\r\n	<li>Composite, Component, and HDMI Inputs</li>\r\n	<li>140&deg;/110&deg; Viewing Angle H/V</li>\r\n	<li>Removable Table Stand</li>\r\n	<li>Versatile Mounting Options</li>\r\n	<li>Includes HDMI to Mini-HDMI Cable</li>\r\n	<li>Includes Power Supply</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Monitor Composite, Component, or HDMI sources with the Lilliput FA1013 10.1&quot; Field Monitor</strong>. Featuring a sharp and bright 1024 x 600 LED LCD display, the FA1013 can display digital or analog SD and HD video signals, leveraging the 16:9 aspect ratio to avoid letterboxing HD video. The Component and Composite analog inputs have loop outputs for daisy-chaining other video equipment. Because of it&#39;s compact and portable design, the FA1013 can be implemented into studio, CCTV, A/V, and field production workflows.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a field monitor, the FA1013 can be mounted in various ways for different purposes. The integrated stand allows for straightforward desk mounting, while 75mm VESA securing points open up more flexible installation options. Additionally, a 1/4&quot;-20 mouting point is available for securing the FA1013 to your camera rig with a separately available arm. Along with the monitor, you&#39;ll receive an HDMI to mini-HDMI cable for connecting most common DSLR cameras and a 12V power supply.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display</li>\r\n	<li>Panel 10.1&quot; (25.6 cm) LED backlit</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution 1024 x 600 (display), 1920 x 1080 (maximum input)</li>\r\n	<li>Aspect Ratio 16:9</li>\r\n	<li>Brightness 250 cd/m2</li>\r\n	<li>Contrast 500:1</li>\r\n	<li>Viewing Angle (H/V) 140&deg; / 110&deg; (H/V)</li>\r\n	<li>Backlight LED</li>\r\n	<li>I/O</li>\r\n	<li>Video 1 x YPbPr 3-BNC, 1 x HDMI, 1 x Composite BNC</li>\r\n	<li>Audio 1.2 W Speaker (built-in), 3.5 mm headphone out</li>\r\n	<li>Power</li>\r\n	<li>Current 500 mA</li>\r\n	<li>Input Voltage 6 to 24 VDC</li>\r\n	<li>Physical</li>\r\n	<li>Operating Temperature -4 to 140&deg;F / -20 to 60&deg;C</li>\r\n	<li>Storage Temperature -22 to 158&deg;F / -30 to 70&deg;C</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions (L x W x D) 10.2 x 6.7 x 1.4&quot; / 259 x 170 x 37 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Weight 2.5 lb / 1.1 kg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1612201709025fda3f2e51b92.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:09:02', 0, '2020-12-16 17:09:02'),
(170, '', 'จำหน่าย Lilliput RM-1730S 17.3 นิ้ว Full HD 3G-SDI/HDMI Pullout Rackmount Monitor (1 RU)', 6, 19, '', 'จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput RM-1730S 17.3&quot; Full HD 3G-SDI/HDMI Pullout Rackmount Monitor (1 RU)</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The LILLIPUT RM-1730S 17.3&quot; Full HD 3G-SDI/HDMI&nbsp;</strong>Pullout Rackmount Monitor features a 16:9 IPS panel and offers a maximum resolution of 1920 x 1080p60. It offers a brightness rating of 300 cd/m2, contrast ratio of 700:1, and viewing angles of 178&deg;. The monitor comes with a host of functions including cross conversion, timecode, pixel zoom, vectorscope, waveform, level meter, peaking, false color, histogram, exposure, check field, color bars, and Image flip. Its 1 RU design allows it to be easily integrated into a studio or post-production rackmount setup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Metal housing with pullout drawer for protection from shocks and drops</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Monitor powers off automatically when screen is down and pushed in</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Signal cross conversion from SDI to HDMI, and from HDMI to SDI out</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supports various methods of mounting for use in broadcast, on-site monitoring, and live broadcast vans</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 RU rackmount design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>LCD Size 17.3&quot; (43.9 cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Display Resolution 1920 x 1080 (RGB)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Active Area H x V: 15 x 8.45&quot; (381.89 x 214.81 mm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dot Pitch H x V: 0.1989 x 0.1989 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aspect Ratio 16:9</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Brightness 300 cd/m2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contrast 700:1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Light Source LED</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Surface Treatment Hard coating (3H)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High-resolution adaptable AG</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Response Time Rising: 14 ms (typical), 19 ms (maximum)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Falling: 11 ms (typical), 16 ms (maximum)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Formats Supported SDI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SMPTE-425M-AB: 1080p 60/59.94/50, 1080i 60/59.94/50, 720p 60/59.94/50/30/29.97/25/24/23.98</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SMPTE-372M: 1080p 60/59.94/50/30/29.97/25/24/23.98, 1080i 29.97/25/24/23.98, 720p 60/59.94/50&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SMPTE-296M: 720p 60/59.94/50/30/29/25/24/23.98</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SMPTE-292M: 1080p 30/29.97/25/24/24PsF/23.98/23.98PsF</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SMPTE-125M: 1080p 30/29.97/25/24/24PsF/23.98/23.98PsF, 1080i 60/59.94/50, 480i 59.94</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ITU-R BT.656: 576i 50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080p Full HD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>720p</p>\r\n\r\n<p>576p</p>\r\n\r\n<p>576i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>480p</p>\r\n\r\n<p>486i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Viewing Angle 178&deg;/178&deg; (H/V)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input and Output Connectors Inputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x 3G-SDI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 x Audio (L/R)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x TALLY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x DVI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x 3G-SDI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x Earphone jack</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio 2 x Speakers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x Earphone</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Requirements Current: 2.5 A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input Voltage: 15 VDC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Controls Basic</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power, SDI, HDMI, DVI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Menu, &lt; &gt; button, exit, user-definable buttons</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Advanced</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Brightness, contrast, saturation, tint, sharpness, color temp</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Markers (center/aspect/safety), marker color, marker mat</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thickness, scan, aspect, underscan, H/V delay, check field</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zoom, freeze, DSLR, waveform, peaking (color/level), false color</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Exposure, exposure level, histogram</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Volume, level meter, audio ch, language</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI-SDI convert, color bar, OSD time, back light, fan, reset</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Consumption &le;32 W</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Speaker 1 W, built-in</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Menu Language English/Chinese</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Temperature &amp; Humidity Operation: 32 to 122&deg;F (0 to 50&deg;C)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage: -4 to 140&deg;F (-20 to 60&deg;C)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Humidity: 80% RH</p>\r\n\r\n<p>240 hours of operation at high temperature/humidity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (L x W x D) 19 x 1.7 x 19.9&quot; (48.25 x 4.4 x 50.75 cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 18.95 lb (8.6 kg)</p>\r\n', '1612201709265fda3f4609e14.jpg', 45000, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:09:26', 0, '2020-12-16 17:09:26'),
(171, '', 'จำหน่าย Lilliput BM230-4K Carry-On 4K Monitor (V-Mount)', 6, 19, '', 'จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>จอมอนิเตอร์ &nbsp;Lilliput BM230-4K Carry-On 4K Monitor (V-Mount)</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>23&quot; 3840x2160 10-Bit IPS LCD</li>\r\n	<li>Supports NTSC/PAL, HD, and 4K UHD</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI, SDI, DVI, and VGA Inputs</li>\r\n	<li>H/V 178&deg; Viewing Angle</li>\r\n	<li>Built-In Monitoring Tools</li>\r\n	<li>On-Screen Markers and Focus Peaking</li>\r\n	<li>Built-In V-Mount Bracket</li>\r\n	<li>Hard Case Enclosure</li>\r\n	<li>XLR 4-Pin 12-24 VDC Power Input</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Built into a hard case, the Lilliput BM230-4K is a 23&quot; native UHD 4K monitor</strong>&nbsp;useful for both studio and field situations. The full capacity of the 3840x2160 UHD resolution 10-bit IPS panel can be driven at up to 30 fps by any of the three HDMI 1.4 inputs, or up to 60 fps by the single HDMI 2.0 input. Other inputs available on the back panel include SDI (with a loop output), DVI, and VGA. Video signals input via any of these ports will be properly scaled to fit the entire screen. Analog audio from the RCA inputs or embedded digital audio from video inputs can be heard using the monitor&#39;s built-in speakers or the 3.5mm headphone output.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For power, this monitor accepts a wide range of voltages ranging from 12 to 24 VDC. In the studio, the included power supply plugs the BM230-4K into the wall, and the 75/100mm VESA mount can be utilized for mounting on a stand. The included tally connector passes tally information through to the monitor when connected to a switcher. While in the field, the monitor will accept battery power via the built-in V-Mount plate. It can be stood up vertically using the rubber feet built into the monitor&#39;s hard case, and a sunshade is included for increased visibility outdoors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Monitoring Tools</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Peaking</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Blue-only</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Image rotation/flip</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Overscan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Underscan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Image freeze</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aspect ratio selection</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Screen markers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Color temperature adjustment</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Assignable Buttons</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Using the four assignable buttons on the front panel, you can quickly turn any four essential monitoring tools on and off without venturing into the monitor&#39;s menu system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Carry-On Enclosure</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The included hard case/enclosure improves the robustness of the monitor&#39;s metal chassis, useful when venturing outside controlled environments. A rear opening gives easy access to all the monitor&#39;s ports and accessory mounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Supports Wireless HDMI (WHDI) Technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a separately available WHDI receiver, the BM230-4K can accept wireless HDMI signals from up to 50&#39; away for a hassle-free cordless connection. With the WHDI system in place, one transmitter can broadcast to multiple receivers, so no splitter is required for multi-monitor viewing.</p>\r\n', '1612201709545fda3f62c094d.jpg', 39900, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:09:54', 0, '2020-12-16 17:09:54'),
(172, '', 'Lilliput PVM150S - Security Monitor for Full HD CCTV', 6, 19, '', 'จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย จอมอนิเตอร์ Lilliput PVM150S - Security Monitor for Full HD CCTV</strong><br />\r\nThe PVM150S is a purpose designed CCTV monitor for use with industry standard CCTV&nbsp; servers and video systems. The unit features and HDMI 1.4b&nbsp; video as well as an SDI bayonet type input which facilitates connection to a whole host of CCTV servers and splitters.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aspect Ratio 16:9</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Brightness 1000 cdm&sup2;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contrast Ratio 1000:1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Display Screen 15.6&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution 1920 x 1080px</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Viewing Angle 178&deg; / 178&deg; (H/V)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Monitor Specification</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video Inputs 3G-SDI x1 // HDMI 1.4 x 1 (support 4K@30Hz) // VGA x1 // A/V x1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video Outputs 1x SDI Loop</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio Outputs Speaker x 1 // Ear Jack x 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Size</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions 252mm x 157mm x 25mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 2.87kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Power</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Current &lt;=2A (12V)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input Voltage 10-24V</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Consumption &lt;=24W</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Environment</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Temperature -20&deg;c to 60&deg;c</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage Temperature -30&deg;c to 70&deg;c</p>\r\n', '1612201710305fda3f86cc2a5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:10:30', 0, '2020-12-16 17:10:30'),
(173, '', 'กล้องวีดีโอ Sony RX0 1.0\" กล้องจิ๋วรุ่นโปรใช้เซนเซอร์ 1 นิ้ว ราคา 23,300', 7, 22, '', 'Sony', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายกล้องวีดีโอ Sony RX0 กล้องจิ๋วรุ่นโปรใช้เซนเซอร์ 1 นิ้ว ราคา 25,900</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sony เปิดตัว RX0 กล้องจิ๋วรุ่นโปรใช้เซนเซอร์ 1 นิ้ว ราคา 25,900</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/ht/di/5y.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nในงาน IFA 2017 โซนี่เปิดตัวกล้อง RX0 กล้องจิ๋วที่ใช้เซนเซอร์ขนาด 1 นิ้วเท่ากับกล้องตระกูล RX10, RX100 แต่ออกแบบให้กันน้ำ กันกระแทก และตัวเล็กพอที่จะนำไปติดตั้งในงานที่ต้องการกล้องหลายๆ ตัว เช่นการถ่ายภาพ 360 องศา หรือใช้งานถ่ายภาพโมเดลรอบทิศ<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '1612201712195fda3ff348763.jpg', 23300, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:12:19', 0, '2020-12-16 17:12:19'),
(174, '', 'SONY DSC-RX0 II 4k (UHD 3840 x 2160)', 7, 22, '', 'Sony', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SONY DSC-RX0 II, DSC-RX0 II G</strong><br />\r\nRX0 II มีขนาดกะทัดรัดเป็นพิเศษพร้อมด้วยตัวกล้องที่แข็งแรงทนทาน อีกทั้งยังป้องกันน้ำ<br />\r\nกันกระแทก และกันการกดทับ จอภาพที่ปรับเอียงได้ 180&deg; ช่วยให้คุณปรับเฟรมภาพถ่ายตนเองและ Vlog ขณะผจญภัย เซนเซอร์ขนาด 1.0-type และโปรเซสเซอร์ภาพขั้นสูงรวมกันให้โทนสีผิวที่สวยงาม&nbsp;มีคุณสมบัติ Eye AF บันทึกภาพยนตร์ 4K 30p2 ภายในกล้องได้ พร้อมด้วยการป้องกันภาพสั่นไหว<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Hilight</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>เลนส์ ZEISS&reg; Tessar T* 24 มม.F4 มุมกว้าง</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ตัวกล้องทนทานและกันน้ำ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LCD ปรับเอียงได้ 180 องศา</p>\r\n\r\n<p>การบันทึกภาพยนตร์ 4K ภายในตัวกล้อง</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ซูเปอร์สโลว์โมชั่น15สูงสุด 960fps/1000fps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ประเภทเซนเซอร์</p>\r\n\r\n<p>เซนเซอร์ Exmor RS CMOS 1.0-type (13.2 มม. x 8.8 มม.) Exmor RS CMOS,<br />\r\nสัดส่วนภาพ 3:2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>จำนวนพิกเซล (ที่ใช้งานจริง)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ประมาณ 15.3 ล้านพิกเซล</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ป้องกันน้ำ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>มี (เทียบเท่า IPX8)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ป้องกันการกระแทก</p>\r\n\r\n<p>มี (200kgf/2000N/440lbf)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ความไวแสง ISO (ภาพนิ่ง)(RECOMMENDED EXPOSURE INDEX)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>อัตโนมัติ(ISO125-12800, เลือกขีดจำกัดบน / ล่างได้),125/160/200/250/320/400/500/640/800/1000/1250/1600/2000/2500/3200/4000/5000/6400/8000/10000/12800 (ขยายเป็น ISO80/100 ได้),NR หลายเฟรม:อัตโนมัติ(ISO200-25600), 200/400/800/1600/3200/6400/12800/25600&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '1612201713035fda401fcc9ea.jpg', 21990, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:13:03', 0, '2020-12-16 17:13:03'),
(175, '', 'กล้อง GOPRO HERO BLACK 6 ACTION CAMERA', 7, 23, '', 'Gopro', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp;กล้อง ACTION CAMERA GOPRO HERO BLACK 6<br />\r\nรายละเอียดสินค้า</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HERO6 Black</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>฿ 14,500.00</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GoPro ให้คุณควบคุมการใช้งานได้อย่างง่ายดาย ผ่านโทรศัพท์มือถือ และแชร์รูปภาพและวีดีโอได้อย่างง่ายดาย GoPro Application จะทำการเปลี่ยนโทรศัพท์มือถือของคุณให้กลายเป็นรีโมทในการสั่งงานต่าง ๆ และควบคุมการตั้งค่าของกล้องเช่นการถ่ายรูป หรือถ่ายวีดีโอได้ทั้งหมด รวมถึงสามารดูมุมมองกล้องผ่านทางหน้าจอของโทรศัพท์มือถือได้อีกด้วย อีกทั้งยังมีแอพพลิเคชั่นสำหรับตัดต่อวีดีโอได้ผ่านทางบนโทรศัพท์มือถือเช่น Quik และแชร์โดยตรงเข้าสู่ Social network รวมทั้ง Facebook และ Instagram<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GoPro HERO6 Black ราคาเปิดตัวที่ 14,500 บาท</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>GoPro ได้พัฒนาให้รุ่น HERO6 Black นี้เพิ่มขีดความสามารถในการใช้งานด้วยชิปเซ็ทGP1รุ่นใหม่ ที่ยกระดับประสิทธิภาพของรูปถ่ายทั้งสีและคุณภาพให้ดียิ่งขึ้น ทำให้ได้ความละเอียดของวิดีโอเพิ่มขึ้นถึง 2 เท่าตัว ในระดับ 4K ที่ 60Fps (Frames Per Second), มีระยะถ่ายที่ไกลและคมชัดมากขึ้น และพัฒนาระบบช่วยลดการสั่นไหวของวิดีโอขึ้นอย่างมาก ซึ่งจะสามารถเห็นข้อแตกต่างได้อย่างชัดเจนเมื่อเทียบกับรุ่นก่อนๆ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ด้วยความสามารถของชิปเซ็ท GP1 ประสิทธิภาพทั้งหมดจะถูกยกระดับขึ้นไปอีกขั้น ซึ่งจะทำให้ได้วิดีโอมีสีสันที่สวยงามขึ้น, ได้ภาพนิ่งที่สวยโดยไม่ต้องปรับให้ยุ่งยาก และยังช่วยยกระดับความสามารถของการแสดงผลในคอมพิวเตอร์ และมีระบบวิเคราะห์ช่วงเวลาที่ดีที่สุดในคลิปวิดีโอ เพื่อสนับสนุนระบบอัจฉริยะของ QuikStories อีกด้วย</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>และให้ชีวิตคุณง่ายขึ้นด้วยการเชื่อมต่อ Wifi 5 GHz ทำให้โอนไฟล์ภาพและวิดีโอเข้าคอมพิวเตอร์หรือสมาร์ทโฟนได้เร็วขึ้น 3 เท่า รวมถึงการอัพโหลดไปยังระบบคลาวด์โดยอัตโนมัติ ตัวกล้องเพิ่มความสะดวกและง่ายในการใช้งานด้วยการควบคุมด้วยเสียงจอภาพแบบสัมผัสและการออกแบบที่มีความทนทานกันน้ำได้ลึกถึง 10 เมตร โดยไม่ต้องใส่กรอบ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>ชิฟเซ็ทGP1 ใหม่ล่าสุดที่มีประสิทธิภาพดีที่สุด</li>\r\n	<li>วิดีโอ 4K60 และ 1080p240</li>\r\n	<li>ใช้ QuikStories และ GoPro App ได้</li>\r\n	<li>ความเสถียรของภาพสูงสุดในบรรดากล้อง GoPro HERO</li>\r\n	<li>การซูมจากหน้าจอแบบสัมผัสครั้งแรก</li>\r\n	<li>ดึงข้อมูลออกได้เร็วกว่าเดิม 3 เท่า ด้วย 5GHz Wi-Fi</li>\r\n	<li>กันน้ำได้ 33 ฟุต (10 เมตร)</li>\r\n	<li>ใช้ได้กับ Karma และขาตั้งกล้องGoPro</li>\r\n	<li>ประสิทธิภาพสูงสุดแม้ในสภาพที่มีการเคลื่อนไหวหรือแสงน้อย</li>\r\n	<li>ถ่ายได้ทั้ง RAW และ HDR</li>\r\n	<li>ควบคุมด้วยเสียงถึง 10 ภาษา</li>\r\n	<li>GPS, Accelerometerและ Gyroscope</li>\r\n	<li>เชื่อมต่อ WiFi และ Bluetooth</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1612201717355fda412f31e80.jpg', 14500, 0, 0, '2020-12-16 17:17:35', 0, '2020-12-16 17:17:35');
