, drone and Steadicam applications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Consistent size and weight across most of the focal lengths enables quick change of lenses when used on drones and gimbals</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ultra-smooth focus rotation allows use of small focus motors</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Allgemeines</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gewicht880 g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abmessungen83,7 mm L&auml;nge</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eigenschaften Objektiv</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Filterdurchmesser95 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Blende T 2.1 to T 22</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Brennweite85 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Naheinstellgrenze1.0 m</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bildwinkel24&deg; / 17&deg; (Kleinbild / Super35)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/fc/fw/8c.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '1712201824105fdba24a5e2fe.jpg', 200000, 0, 0, '2020-12-17 18:24:10', 0, '2020-12-17 18:24:10'),
(249, '', 'เลนส์ ZEISS CP.3-2.1/100XD', 2, 2, '', 'ZIESS XD', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>จำหน่ายเลนส์&nbsp; ZEISS CP.3-2.1/100XD</p>\r\n', '1712201824305fdba25e3d99a.jpg', 240000, 0, 0, '2020-12-17 18:24:30', 0, '2020-12-17 18:24:30');
