(314, '', 'ขาตั้งกล้องวีดีโอ Manfrotto 114MV Cine/Video Dolly', 4, 14, '', 'Manfrotto', '', '<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>For 3181/82/85/86/90/and 3193 Series</li>\r\n	<li>Replaces # 3068</li>\r\n	<li>132 lb Load Capacity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Manfrotto 114MV Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Manfrotto 114MV Cine/Video Dolly is designed for use with tripods with spiked feet. This dolly features individually braked 5&quot; wheels with cable guards and a unique leg-locking system. Doorway clearance needed for the fully assembled Dolly is only 44.1&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Replaces old part number 3068.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compatibility</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For 3181/3182, 3185/3186 &amp; 3190/3193 series<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Manfrotto 114MV Specs</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Construction</td>\r\n			<td>Aluminum alloy</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Load Capacity</td>\r\n			<td>132 lb (60 kg)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Doorway Width</td>\r\n			<td>44.1&quot;<em>&nbsp;112cm</em></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Folded Length</td>\r\n			<td>25.5&quot;<em>&nbsp;64.7cm</em></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Wheel Diameter</td>\r\n			<td>5.0&quot;<em>&nbsp;12.7cm</em></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Wheel Lock</td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Cable Guards</td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Weight</td>\r\n			<td>13.7 lbs<em>&nbsp;6.2kg</em></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th colspan=\"2\"><a id=\"shipping\" name=\"shipping\"></a>Packaging Info</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Package Weight</td>\r\n			<td>14.55 lb</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Box Dimensions (LxWxH)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>26.75 x 12.75 x 9.0&quot;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\