(318, '', 'ขาตั้งกล้องวีดีโอ Manfrotto BeFree Compact Travel Aluminum Alloy Tripod (Black)', 4, 14, '', 'Manfrotto', '', '<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Load Capacity: 8.8 lb</li>\r\n	<li>Maximum Height: 56.7&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>Min Height: 13.4&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>Folded Length: 15.75&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>Leg Sections: 4</li>\r\n	<li>Weight: 3 lb</li>\r\n	<li>Independent Leg Angle Selector</li>\r\n	<li>Quick Release Ball Head</li>\r\n	<li>QR Plate Included</li>\r\n	<li>Fitted Case</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The black Manfrotto BeFree Compact Travel Aluminum Alloy Tripod is a sturdy, compact tripod that extends to 56.7&quot;, supports 8.8 lb, and folds up to only 15.75&quot;. The tripod&#39;s legs can be spread independently, with two-position leg angle stops. The legs fold up and around the ball head, a feature that helps makes this tripod so compact.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ball head has a large ergonomic locking handle and a quick release with an included QR plate that has a 1/4&quot;-20 mounting screw and a durable carrying case for storage and transport.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th colspan=\"2\"><a id=\"46404\" name=\"46404\"></a>General</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Material</td>\r\n			<td>Aluminum Alloy</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Load Capacity</td>\r\n			<td>8.8 lb (4 kg)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Maximum Height</td>\r\n			<td>56.7&quot; (144 cm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Maximum Height w/o Column Extended</td>\r\n			<td>48.4&quot; (123 cm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Minimum Height</td>\r\n			<td>13.4&quot; (34 cm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Folded Length</td>\r\n			<td>15.75&quot; (40 cm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Weight</td>\r\n			<td>Tripod with head: 3 lb (1.4 kg)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th colspan=\"2\"><a id=\"48805\" n