(319, '', 'ขาตั้งกล้องวีดีโอ Manfrotto MVM500A Fluid Aluminum Video Monopod with 500 Series Head', 4, 14, '', 'Manfrotto', '', '<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Load Capacity: 11 lb</li>\r\n	<li>Max Height: 78.9&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>Closed Length: 30.3&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>Sections: 4</li>\r\n	<li>Weight: 6.2 lb</li>\r\n	<li>Long Sliding Plate</li>\r\n	<li>Side Lock System for Safety</li>\r\n	<li>3 Mini Legs at Base for Added Stability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Manfrotto MVM500A Overview&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This 4-section aluminum Manfrotto MVM500A Fluid Video Monopod with 500 Series Head rises to a height of 78.9&quot;, folds down 30.3&quot; and includes a compact, lightweight fluid head for smooth panning and tilting. The quick release head has a long sliding plate with both 1/4&quot;-20 and 3/8&quot;-16 camera screws. Three mini, retractable feet at the base offer additional stability. This monopod and head combination is an ideal match for cameras weighing up to 11 lb. The included head does not have a fluid pan movement and is not removable. The fluid pan movement is in the base of the monopod.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Manfrotto MVM500A Specs</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th colspan=\"2\"><a id=\"75016\" name=\"75016\"></a>Monopod</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Construction</td>\r\n			<td>Aluminum</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Maximum Height</td>\r\n			<td>78.94&quot; (200.5 cm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Minimum Height</td>\r\n			<td>30.31&quot; (77 cm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Leg Sections</td>\r\n			<td>4</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Load Capacity</td>\r\n			<td>11.02 lb (5 kg)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Leg Lock Type</td>\r\n			<td>Flip-lock</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Male Thread Size</td>\r\n			<td>3/8&quot; screw attachment type</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>