(325, '', 'ขาตั้งกล้อง Sachtler FSB 4 Fluid Head', 4, 67, '', 'Sachtler', '', '<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Capacity Up to 8.8 lbs (4kg)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 75mm Bowl Mount</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- For Lightweight Camcorders &amp; DSLRs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 5-step Counterbalance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Works with SOOM Tripod System</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With its 8.8 lb capacity and compact size, the Sachtler FSB 4 Fluid</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Head is ideal for supporting small handheld camcorders and video-enabled DSLRs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the only head in its class to feature Sachtler&#39;s Snap &amp; Go sideload mechanism,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>the FSB 4 boasts an exceptionally large sliding range of 120mm (4.7&quot;).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Along with a 5-step counterbalance, this ensures extremely quick and</p>\r\n\r\n<p>precise balancing. At the same time, no-compromise vibration damping</p>\r\n\r\n<p>allows for extremely subtle and finely graded movement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATION</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"height:1254px; width:630px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:274.444px\">\r\n			<p>Load Capacity</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:305.556px\">\r\n			<p>8.8 lbs (4kg)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:274.444px\">\r\n			<p>Diameter/Thread</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:305.556px\">\r\n			<p>75mm Bowl/Flat Base</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:274.444px\">\r\n			<p>Counter Balance System</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:305.556px\">\r\n			<p>5 Steps</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:274.444px\">\r\n			<p>Counter Balance Range</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:305.556px\">\r\n			<p>4.7&quot; (120mm)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:274.444px\">\r\n			<p>Quick Release/Wedge Plate</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:305.556px\">\r\n			<p>Yes</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"widt