(344, '', 'NewTek Control Surfaces Maximum Performance', 22, 71, '', 'Live Production Systems', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NewTek 4-Stripe Control Panel</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Definitive control for the most demanding IP production ecosystems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The pinnacle of control for large-scale interconnected production environments, the NewTek 4-Stripe Control Panel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>lets you command multi-source, multi-system, and multi-site productions with absolute confidence.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"NewTek IP Series 4-Stripe Control Panel\" src=\"https://233b1d13b450eb6b33b4-ac2a33202ef9b63045cbb3afca178df8.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/images/control-surface/4Stripe.jpg\" style=\"height:141px; width:522px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intuitive layout mapped to the Video Mix Engine user interface</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IP-based connectivity, with support for multi-engine control over the network</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Responsive, multi-bus operation with independently assignable control stripes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Practical lighting, variable T-Bar illumination, and dynamic LCD label displays</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Precision controls for expert handling of real-time video operations</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Premium craftsmanship for optimal performance, ergonomics, and style<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>NewTek 2-Stripe Control Panel</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Consummate control for IP production environments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The perfect blend of power and versatility, the NewTek IP Series 2-Stripe Control Panel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>is built to handle interconnected productions&mdash;and environments&mdash;of any scale.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"NewTek IP Series 2-Stripe Control Panel\" src=\"https://233b1d13b450eb6b33b4-ac2a33202ef9b63045cbb3afca178df8.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/images/control-surface/2Stripe.jpg\" style=\"height:107px; width:524px\" /></p>\r\n', '2412201632015fe4c281c7646.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:32:01', 0, '2020-12-24 16:32:01'),
(345, '', 'Newtek TriCaster 2 Elite', 22, 71, '', 'Live Production Systems', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Newtek TriCaster 2 Elite</strong><br />\r\nComplete Production</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Engineered with a purpose and built with a commitment to ensuring you have everything you need to create amazing productions, NewTek live production systems provide the most comprehensive set of tools and capabilities for modern workflows and the most value for your investment of any video solution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See why they are the most complete video production systems on the planet.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>WorkFrow</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/n6/6m/pj.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '2412201632245fe4c2985face.png', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:32:24', 0, '2020-12-24 16:32:24'),
(346, '', 'NewTek TalkShow VS 4000 Multi-channel video calling', 22, 72, '', 'Skype For Broadcast', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TalkShow&reg; VS 4000 Multi-channel video calling, with broadcast-quality production control.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nInstantly connect with multiple contacts around the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TalkShow VS 4000 is the professional, multi-channel video calling system designed to simultaneously connect you with up to 4 remote guests&mdash;regardless of location&mdash;in real time and deliver distraction-free, broadcast-quality HD content with complete production control.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reach 300 million monthly Skype users with:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 concurrent Skype video channels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4-in, 4-out HD-SDI connections</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Integrated NDI&reg; technology supporting input and output over IP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tally notification on all call channels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most complete audio and video capabilities</p>\r\n', '09022104282060220f64ca063.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:33:39', 0, '2021-02-09 04:28:20'),
(347, '', 'TalkShow® VS 100 Premium for professional-grade Skype calls.', 22, 72, '', 'Skype For Broadcast', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TalkShow&reg; VS 100 Premium for professional-grade Skype calls.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Control every call with complete confidence.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the most comprehensive set of integrated production capabilities available in any Skype TX single-caller video calling system, TalkShow VS 100 gives you total control of your video interviews before, during, and after the show.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reach 300 million monthly Skype users with:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1-in, 1-out HD-SDI connections</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Industry-standard XLR and SDI-embedded audio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Professional audio tools, auto color, and proc amp controls</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Space-saving 1RU rack mount</p>\r\n', '09022104280860220f5872ad6.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:33:57', 0, '2021-02-09 04:28:08'),
(348, '', 'NewTek Remote Storage', 22, 73, '', 'Network Recording', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NewTek Remote Storage</strong><br />\r\nShared storage solutions for modern production workflows.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From providing instant access to an expansive library of stored media assets, to enabling essential and extended recording sessions, to supporting hours upon hours of content for archive, on-demand, and post-production, shared remote storage is a principal requirement in today&rsquo;s live production environments. Equip your workflow to meet these high-capacity, high-performance demands with NewTek Remote Storage &ndash; Powered by SNS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Available in multiple form factors and expandable storage capacities for productions of all sizes</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Record multiple streams of NDI|HX directly to RAID protected shared storage</li>\r\n	<li>Rackmount and desktop form factors</li>\r\n	<li>Industry-standard SATA/SAS removable drive bays</li>\r\n	<li>Support for simultaneous multi-channel capture, ingest, editing, and playback</li>\r\n	<li>Instant availability of recorded media for post-production turnaround</li>\r\n	<li>Fully compatible with NewTek IP Series, TriCaster&reg; TC1, and 3Play&reg; 3P1</li>\r\n	<li>High-performance SAN and NAS subsystem</li>\r\n	<li>Tag, comment, search, preview, and organize recorded media and other stored assets with included ShareBrowser media asset management software</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\" \" src=\"https://233b1d13b450eb6b33b4-ac2a33202ef9b63045cbb3afca178df8.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/images/lps/sns/nrs-16-v2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '2412201634435fe4c323bca4f.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:34:43', 0, '2020-12-24 16:34:43'),
(349, '', 'NewTek IsoCorder™ Pro Multi-channel recording for any workflow.', 22, 73, '', 'Network Recording', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NewTek IsoCorder&trade; Pro Multi-channel recording for any workflow.</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Live recording of any source.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Infuse your production workflow with video capture capabilities equivalent to racks of expensive recording hardware with a single user-friendly application. With NewTek IsoCorder Pro, up to 16 simultaneous video signals can be captured from any combination of hundreds of compatible hardware, software, and IP sources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Capture everything.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Seamlessly capture signals and still images from the cameras, systems, and devices connected to your PC via capture card or to your network over IP, independently assigning file names and destinations to suit your workflow.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://233b1d13b450eb6b33b4-ac2a33202ef9b63045cbb3afca178df8.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/images/IsoCorderScreenShots.jpg\" style=\"height:293px; width:522px\" /></p>\r\n', '2412201635055fe4c3393a76c.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:35:05', 0, '2020-12-24 16:35:05'),
(350, '', 'NewTek NDI® PTZ Camera', 22, 74, '', 'Camera Solutions', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NewTek NDI&reg; PTZ Camera</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Introducing NewTek NDI&reg; PTZ Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>VIDEO, AUDIO, CONTROL, TALLY AND POWER&mdash;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ONE ETHERNET CABLE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Simply connect to any Ethernet port.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>THAT&rsquo;S IT.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your camera is now a source for all NDI compatible systems and software on your network.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Connect, capture, and control with a single network cable. No need for extra connections, cables, and messy setups.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CORPORATE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Turn any office or meeting room into a remote studio for executive communications, video conferencing, or online training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>EDUCATION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Streamline virtual classroom production, lecture capture, and distance learning for live and on-demand teaching.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ENTERTAINMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Expand event coverage in-venue and behind the scenes for live streaming, recording, and social video.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GAMING</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capture the action, emotion, and intensity of competitive gaming and esports from every angle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GOVERNMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inform and involve citizens with real-time access to live meetings and community programming.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PROFESSIONAL A/V</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Explore virtually endless video applications, from medical and security installations to weddings and graduations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPORTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enhance the fan experience with unique camera angles or outfit facilities for covering practices and club activities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Technical Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>NDI output over IP via Ethernet connection</li>\r\n	<li>3G-SDI or HDMI video output</li>\r\n	<li>Native support for HD resolutions up to 1080p 60</li>\r\n	<li>Support for tally via NDI</li>\r\n	<li>Remote control &amp; monitoring via Web-based interface</li>\r\n	<li>20x optical zoom</li>\r\n	<li>Power over Ethernet via POE+ (802.3at)</li>\r\n	<li>Mounting bracket included</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 6.9 x 7.2 x 7.2 in (175 x 183 x 183 mm)</li>\r\n	<li>Weight: 4.0 lbs (1.8 kg)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2412201635595fe4c36f7ec28.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:35:59', 0, '2020-12-24 16:35:59'),
(351, '', 'NDI®|HX Upgrade For Cameras', 22, 74, '', 'Camera Solutions', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NDI&reg;|HX Upgrade For Cameras</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Automatically detect your camera as an NDI&reg; source on the network</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Simply connect to any Ethernet port. THAT&rsquo;S IT.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your camera is now a source for all NDI&reg; compatible systems and software on your network.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With NDI|HX driver enabled, any and all cameras detected on your network become immediately available for use&mdash;with no complex configuration required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NDI|HX</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imagine the possibilities of a camera that can serve as a live video input for any NDI-compatible hardware or software&mdash;from anywhere on your network. Integrated and automatic tally support via NDI, motor-driven pan-tilt-zoom operation with preset positions, remote control over IP via Studio Monitor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Video, Audio, Control, Tally and Power*&mdash;one Ethernet Cable</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>NDI|HX presents unprecedented freedom for installation, integration, and production. NDI|HX connects over IP to any of the hundreds of systems, devices, and applications that support NDI, and requires only an Ethernet connection for setup and operation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/gw/sd/9u.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '2412201636235fe4c387e91de.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:36:23', 0, '2020-12-24 16:36:23'),
(352, '', 'NDI®|HX Camera For Mobile application', 22, 74, '', 'Camera Solutions', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NDI&reg;|HX Camera application</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Turn your mobile device camera into a NDI source</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Production-ready video in the palm of your hand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imagine adding a new video camera to your production with the affordability, convenience and ease of a mobile device app download. NDI&reg;|HX Camera application turns any iOS mobile device into an IP-ready live video source when connected to the same network as your NDI-compatible receiving device or production system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>New cameras. New perspectives. New possibilities.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>From introducing new camera angles and new vantage points to your coverage, to adding completely new dimensions to your live broadcasts, webcasts and presentations, NewTek NDI Camera application opens up a world of creative possibilities for your productions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best of all, you can shoot with the same mobile device camera you use to take snapshots and selfies, so there&rsquo;s no experience needed and no additional camera training required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Add new live video sources to your production instantly with NDI&reg;|HX Camera application</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Easy to use, with device output automatically recognized by NDI-compatible receiving devices on the same local network</li>\r\n	<li>Hi Bandwidth mode (720p) or standard (SD) mode</li>\r\n	<li>Front and rear camera selection for shooting video and interactive communication</li>\r\n	<li>Simple pinch zooming and optional grid overlay for ideal framing</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible camera focus options, including Auto Focus, AF Lock, and tap to focus</li>\r\n	<li>Configurable exposure control, with Auto Exposure, AE Lock, and manual exposure compensation</li>\r\n	<li>One-touch device light and audio mute control</li>\r\n	<li>On-screen connection notification and tally display for preview and on-air status</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2412201637045fe4c3b087e2c.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:36:44', 0, '2020-12-24 16:37:04'),
(353, '', 'AVer Media C875 Live Gamer Portable USB Capture / Streaming', 23, 83, '', 'Capture / Streaming', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVer Media C875 Live Gamer Portable USB Capture / Streaming</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LGP is a capture card that accompanies you to battles at home, or on the road. Never miss another opportunity to record and share your awesome road games, tournaments, or friendly matches.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1-Click Full HD Recording without a PC</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Live Gamer Portable (LGP) packs all the essentials a gamer needs in its sleek body. HDMI or component inputs for all mainstream consoles*, an SD card slot for capturing without a PC, and a hot button that activates 1080p recording with a single click.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* To record PlayStation&reg;4, upgrade your system software to version 1.7 or later. Click here for more information on how to disable HDCP on PS4.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1-Click Full HD Recording without a PC. I/O ports includes HDMI IN &amp; OUT, AV IN, and 3.5 mm Audio IN/OUT.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Playful, yet Powerful</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LGP simplifies live streaming so much you almost forgot how much trouble it used to be. You can even record and stream your gameplay simultaneously, with voice commentary. The H.264 hardware encoder ensures top quality video without overloading your CPU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2412201640515fe4c493a9370.jpg', 74008, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:40:51', 0, '2020-12-24 16:40:51'),
(354, '', 'AVERMEDIA GC553 LIVE GAMER ULTRA เครื่องแคสเกมส์ 4K', 23, 83, '', 'Capture / Streaming', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp;</strong><strong>AVERMEDIA GC553 LIVE GAMER ULTRA&nbsp; เครื่องแคสเกมส์ 4K&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LIVE GAMER ULTRA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GC553 Live Gamer ULTRA (LGU) คือเกมแคปเจอร์ generation ใหม่ ที่รองรับการบันทึกภาพระดับ 4K มาไว้บนโต๊ะคุณ ในขณะที่มันสามารถส่งผ่านสัญญาณ HDMI Pass-thourh ออกจอ 4K HDR ได้ถึง 60p ช่วยให้นักแคสเกมสามารถสัมผัสได้ถึงประสบการณ์ การเล่นเกมในระดับ 4K HDR ได้อย่างแท้จริง&nbsp; และหากคุณใช้ความละเอียด Full HD มันยังสามารถส่งผ่านสัญญาณ HDMI Pass-thourh ออกจอได้ถึง 240Hz เลยทีเดียว</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4K HIGH DYNAMIC RANGE PASS-THROUGH</p>\r\n\r\n<p>อย่าทิ้งเนื้อหา HDR 4K เพียงแค่เพื่อให้สามารถบันทึกการเล่นเกมของคุณได้&nbsp; ด้วยคุณสมบัติ 4Kp60 HDR video pass-through, ไม่มีอาการ lag 100%&nbsp; &nbsp;Live Gamer Ultra (GC553) จะช่วยให้คุณเพลิดเพลินกับการเล่นเกม 4K HDR อันน่าหลงใหลและบันทึกได้ที่ความละเอียดถึง 4Kp30</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HIGH FRAME RATE CAPTURE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ด้วยความสามารถในการบันทึกความละเอียด Full HD ที่รองรับได้ถึง 120 เฟรมต่อวินาที&nbsp; GC553 จึงคว้าตำแหน่ง เกมแคปเจอร์แบบติดตั้งภายนอกในตลาดตัวแรก ที่บันทึกได้อย่างราบรื่น</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FULL HD HIGH DYNAMIC RANGE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ด้วยคุณสมบัติพิเศษที่ไม่ซ้ำใคร&nbsp; GC553 สามารถบันทึกเนื้อหาแบบ HDR ในระดับ Full HD ได้ถึง 60 เฟรมต่อวินาที และ รองรับ 4K HDR pass-through</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>EASIEST SETUP EVER</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GC553 รองรับเทคโนโลยี UVC ซึ่งทำให้คุณไม่ต้องลงไดรเวอร์เพื่อติดตั้งอุปกรณ์ เพียงแค่เชื่อมต่อ GC553 กับพีซีของคุณ ก็พร้อมที่จะบันทึกและสตรีมได้ทันที</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RECENTRAL&mdash;POWERFUL STREAMING SOFTWARE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RECentral เป็นซอฟต์แวร์แคปเจอร์และแคสเกมอันดับแรก ที่สามารถบันทึกเนื้อหาแบบ HDR ได้, และไม่เพียงเท่านั้น RECentral ยังสามารถสตรีมไปหลายแพลตฟอร์มได้ด้วยเช่นกัน เช่น Youtube, Facebook, Twitch, Ustream, RTMP custom เป็นต้น</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RECENTRAL EXPRESS FOR MAC OS X</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ใหม่!&nbsp; RECentral Express สำหรับ Mac OS X High Sierra 10.13 ช่วยให้คุณสามารถบันทึกและสตรีม จาก Mac OS ได้ง่าย ๆ และมีประสิทธิภาพ (ไม่รองรับการบันทึก HDR)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CAPTURE, RECORD, EDIT 4K</p>\r\n\r\n<p>หากต้องการแก้ไขวิดิโอ 4K ของคุณ แต่ไม่ทราบจะเริ่มต้นอย่างไร เรามีโปรแกรม CyberLink PowerDirector 15 ที่รวมอยู่ในชุด เป็นโปรแกรมตัดต่อวิดิโอ 4K ที่ใช้ง่ายสำหรับผู้เริ่มต้น</p>\r\n', '2412201642315fe4c4f775b8d.jpg', 7590, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:42:31', 0, '2020-12-24 16:42:31'),
(355, '', 'AVer MEDIA Game Capture HD II - C285', 23, 83, '', 'Capture / Streaming', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/9v/j2/qg.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>เงื่อนไขอื่นๆ</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย AVer MEDIA Game Capture HD II - C285</strong><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dz.lnwfile.com/_/dz/_raw/9u/lo/ds.png\" /><br />\r\nGame Capture HD II is the stand-alone all-in-one solution to start your YouTube channel. It records 1080p video to its internal storage, without a PC.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Warning wording</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stand-Alone Console Capturing. C285 streams and captures without PC and provides 1080p high quality videos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stand-Alone Console Capturing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Game Capture HD II supports both HDMI and component inputs from all mainstream consoles. The HDMI pass-through allows playing and capturing right in your living room on the TV. There&#39;s no need to hook up additional PC to do the job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Power of Voice. Make commentaries directly with C285 by using headset or desktop microphone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Power of Voice</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even the most spectacular move would look dull without commentaries. Connect your headset to Game Capture HD II, and be your own commentator.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Edit from Your Couch. Built-in editor for direct footage clipping right on your TV</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Edit from Your Couch</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video editing does not necessarily require a PC. Game Capture HD II comes with its built-in editor for direct footage clipping right on your TV. Post- production has never been this easy!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Direct Upload to YouTube. Game Capture HD II links directly to your YouTube channel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Direct Upload to YouTube</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Want to share your videos? We&rsquo;ve got you covered. Game Capture HD II links directly to your YouTube channel, so you can share your gameplay straight away.</p>\r\n', '2412201642595fe4c51346521.jpg', 8400, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:42:59', 0, '2020-12-24 16:42:59'),
(356, '', 'AVer Media Live Gamer 4K - GC573', 23, 83, '', 'Capture / Streaming', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVer Media Live Gamer 4K - GC573&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Live Gamer 4K</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Live Gamer 4K (LG4K) is the embodiment of what next generation of game capture is all about. Mighty in every aspect, from capturing 4K HDR content to amazingly high frame capturing of up to 240 FPS, the LG4K is bringing the future of video capture to all gamers and content creators.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To see if LG4K is compatible with your computer, please download and run ourcompatibility test tool.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Capture Like No One Before</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>What can be better than capturing 4Kp60 video?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capturing4Kp60 HDR, period.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Smooth Gameplay Recording Just Got Smoother</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Forget about &ldquo;buttery smooth&rdquo; 60FPS. Supporting refresh rates of up to 240 Hz in Full HD, the LG4K brings smoother than buttery smooth gameplay recordings to your archives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GC553</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>RGB Lighting</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The LG4K brings more than just awesome performance to your PC setup. Adding RGB lighting to the mix (3 preset modes), the LG4K will give your set up one more reason to shine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>RECentral&mdash;Powerful Streaming Software</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>First in its class! RECentral is the first gaming capture software able to record HDR content. And it doesn&rsquo;t stop there, RECentral is also able to simultaneously stream to multiple platforms. For more information,clickhere</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GC553</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Customizable resolution utility</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you decided not to connect a display to the HDMI output (pass-through) of your LG4K we got you covered! With the &ldquo;AVerMedia Gaming Utility&rdquo; you can customize which resolutions and corresponding frame rates you are able to preview and record without the need to connect a passthrough monitor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GC553</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Capture, Record, Edit 4K</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you thinking about editing your 4K videos but don&rsquo;t know where to start? We&rsquo;ve got you covered. The bundled CyberLink&reg; PowerDirector&trade; 15 is a feature-packed, intuitive 4K video editor to kickstart your editing skills.</p>\r\n', '2412201643255fe4c52d2bfcc.png', 9900, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:43:25', 0, '2020-12-24 16:43:25'),
(357, '', 'AVer Media LIVE Gamer Portable 2 PLUS - GC513', 23, 83, '', 'Capture / Streaming', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVer Media LIVE Gamer Portable 2 PLUS - GC513</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dz.lnwfile.com/_/dz/_raw/qe/4k/1q.jpg\" style=\"height:181px; width:579px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ultra HD 4K Pass Through *</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t sacrifice the 4K experience just to record your game plays. Enjoy 100% lag-less 4Kp60 video with LGP2 Plus integrated pass through feature and still records amazing game plays at Full HD 60 fps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*HDR not supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PC Mode</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stream Right Away. We understand the frustration in having to go through setups and installations. You can forget about all that. LGP2 Plus works right out of the box.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PC-Free Mode</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Record on the Go.Touring the world with LGP2 Plus? A tap on the hot button initiates 1080p60 recording, keeping all your road games in the microSD card. No extra hardware is required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage Mode</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Access and Share Files Directly. Back home, switch LGP2 Plus to Storage Mode and it acts as a card reader. Never remove and risk losing memory cards again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Simple Plug and Play Technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>LGP2 Plus works right out of the box. Unlike other video capture solutions LGP2 Plus uses the latest UVC technology, this means all you need is already in your computer or Mac, simply plug it and you are ready to stream !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Live Commentary &amp; Party Chat</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Adding commentaries to your streams or capturing your party chats has never been as easy as plug and go. Put on your headset, grab your controller, and let LGP2 Plus handle the rest.</p>\r\n', '2412201643445fe4c540d97c6.png', 6490, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:43:44', 0, '2020-12-24 16:43:44'),
(358, '', 'EVC130 Point to Point Video Conferencing', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Key Features<br />\r\nPerfectly suited for small meeting rooms, the EVC130&#39;s 88&deg; FOV ensures everyone in attendance is in focus and onscreen<br />\r\nWide compatibility with all major legacy video conferencing brands, including Polycom, Tandberg, and Lifesize, and with cloud services through their H.323 bridges<br />\r\nSimply pick up the remote and dial into your meeting immediately<br />\r\nAchieve video excellence through smooth audio and video streaming even under the most erratic network conditions with AVer&#39;s High Efficiency Lost Pack Recovery (HELPeR&trade;) technology<br />\r\nSecure conferencing since data doesn&#39;t need to go through 3rd party cloud server<br />\r\nBuilt-in recording at no extra charge<br />\r\nExtremely cost effective</p>\r\n', '2412201644565fe4c58818e73.jpg', 69000, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:44:56', 0, '2020-12-24 16:44:56'),
(359, '', 'EVC150 Point-to-point, New eCam Focus with 18X Total Zoom', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVER MEDIA EVC150 Point-to-point, New eCam Focus with 18X Total Zoom</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The EVC150 is video conferencing&rsquo;s price-to-performance leader, offering small to medium-scale organizations a uniquely cost-effective full HD video conferencing solution. The EVC150 features real-time full HD video streaming and HD 720p content sharing along with a PTZ camera, an microphone array, a sleek UI and a compact system design. In addition to its impressive hardware, the EVC150 comes with a 3-year standard warranty and remarkably low total cost of ownership, translating into an astounding return on investment. Whether for point-to-point conferencing, cloud-based video collaboration or hardware system integration, the standards-based EVC150 is the system of choice for savvy VC users.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Full HD video &amp; HD content sharing\" src=\"http://communication.aver.com/Upload/Model/1417/featureimg_1.png\" style=\"height:317px; width:479px\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Full HD video &amp; HD content sharing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience natural, real-time video communication on one monitor at HD 1080p 30fps, while sharing presentation files, animation, visualizer images and more on another at HD 720p 30fps, creating a smooth, interactive video conferencing experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt=\"One-touch recording\" src=\"http://communication.aver.com/Upload/Model/1417/featureimg_2.png\" style=\"height:319px; width:482px\" /></p>\r\n', '2412201645175fe4c59d18fa8.png', 89000, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:45:17', 0, '2020-12-24 16:45:17'),
(360, '', 'AVER MEDIA EVC170 Full HD Endpoint with a Built-In Meeting Server', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Main system unit (codec)<br />\r\neCam PTZ IV camera<br />\r\nEVC microphone array<br />\r\nIR remote control with batteries<br />\r\nPower supply<br />\r\nCables<br />\r\nWarranty card<br />\r\nQuick guide</p>\r\n', '2412201645435fe4c5b7c8163.png', 119000, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:45:43', 0, '2020-12-24 16:45:43'),
(361, '', 'EVC350 4-site Embedded MCU License Upgrade to 6, 8 and 10 Points', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVER MEDIA EVC350 4-site Embedded MCU License Upgrade to 6, 8 and 10 Points</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Perfect for any budget, the EVC350 is AVer&rsquo;s affordable, 4-site, high performance MCU video conferencing system. This all-in-one video conferencing solution allows organizations to start conferencing immediately, with no installation fees or costly upgrades. Our patented, intelligent microphones can be linked together to form a daisy chain so you can enjoy great audio reception in any size of conference room. All your important meetings can be recorded directly to a USB flash drive, even when you are offline. Moreover, you can use the EVC350 with AVer&rsquo;s EZDraw collaborative annotation app to access to an impressive array of interactive tools. Users can also connect to the EVC350 from PCs, laptops, tablets and smart phones via AVer&rsquo;s EZMeetup software. All these great features make the EVC350 the perfect communication solution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Break Your Communication Barriers with Simultaneous Skype for Business, H.323, and SIP Support<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prepare your video conferencing experience for Tri-Protocol Integration for the AVer EVC Series! Get exclusive Multipoint connections between three protocols and expand your global communication capabilities. (License upgrade required)</p>\r\n', '2412201646055fe4c5cdcfcf8.png', 169000, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:46:05', 0, '2020-12-24 16:46:05'),
(362, '', 'VC520+ Professional Camera for Video Collaboration in Conference Rooms', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVER MEDIA VC520+ Professional Camera for Video Collaboration in Conference Rooms</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>VC520+ เป็นเครื่องมือที่จำเป็นสำหรับการทำธุรกิจที่ใช้การประชุมผ่านเว็บหรือระบบคลาวด์เหมาะสำหรับห้องประชุมทุกขนาดตั้งแต่ห้องเล็กจนถึงห้องประชุมขนาดใหญ่ VC520+ มีกล้องขนาดกะทัดรัดและลำโพงสปีกเกอร์โฟนที่ทรงพลังให้ภาพรายละเอียดสูงและมีคุณภาพเสียงที่สดใส เหมาะอย่างยิ่งกับแล็ปท็อปเพียงแค่เสียบและเล่น VC520+ ผ่านการเชื่อมต่อ USB เท่านั้น</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Perfectly Designed for Medium to Large Rooms and 360&deg; Audio Pick-up</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>VC520+ เป็นกล้องที่สมบูรณ์แบบสำหรับห้องประชุมขนาดกลางถึงขนาดใหญ่ สามารถมองเห็นทุกคนพอดีกับหน้าจอ ชุดสปีกเกอร์โฟนมีไมโครโฟนแบบ 3 ทิศทางที่ให้เสียง 360 &deg;ในช่วง 9 เมตร</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PTZ Camera with 18X Total Zoom</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ด้วยการซูมแบบ (PTZ) และสามารถซูมได้ 18X VC520+ จะตอบสนองความต้องการในการทำงานร่วมกันของวิดีโอในห้องประชุมขนาดใหญ่หรือเล็ก โดยไม่คำนึงว่าคุณต้องการมุมมองที่ละเอียดของวัตถุขนาดเล็กหรือมุมมองกว้างของผู้เข้าร่วมทั้งหมด นอกจากนี้เลนส์โฟกัสอัตโนมัติที่รวดเร็วช่วยให้มั่นใจถึงประสบการณ์การประชุมที่ราบรื่นและสมจริง</p>\r\n', '2412201646295fe4c5e51895a.png', 42900, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:46:29', 0, '2020-12-24 16:46:29'),
(363, '', 'AVer VB342 USB Conference Camera with 4K Video and Lifelike Sound', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>จำหน่าย AVer VB342 USB Conference Camera with 4K Video and Lifelike Sound</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVer VB342 USB Conference Camera with 4K Video and Lifelike Sound</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Video Soundbar</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The VB342 easily puts all participants in clear focus with its 4K PTZ camera&rsquo;s extraordinary video quality and its professional-grade speakers and microphones. Perfectly suited for huddle rooms.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A Vibrant Face to Face Experience with 4K &amp; Pan Tilt Zoom</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the VB342, there&rsquo;s no need to leave your office for face-to-face meetings- just click a button and everyone is there. The VB342&rsquo;s 4K camera provides superb resolution, color balance, and detail so you can catch all participants&rsquo; expressions with no distortion. Ultra-sharp clarity is maintained even when you pan, tilt and zoom.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Professional audio optimized for meetings</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The VB342 brings an optimized audio experience unlike any experienced in a meeting space. Its two uni-directional microphones cover a 4m range, ample for any huddle room. Its stereo speaker offers 5W full range. No matter how far away everyone is, it will sound like they are in the same room.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Easy to install and setup</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The VB342 is designed for ease of access and the maximum user experience. It is easy to install, and integrates seamlessly with your existing systems, offering multiple connectivity and expansion options and bringing together the ultimate VC experience in a unified, accessible platform.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Contents</p>\r\n\r\n<p>VB342 unit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remote control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.8m USB cable to PC (USB 3.0 type C to PC)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB type-A to type-C adapter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power supply</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quick-start guide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wall mount bracket</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mounting screws</p>\r\n', '2412201647225fe4c61a2d9f2.png', 57000, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:47:22', 0, '2020-12-24 16:47:22'),
(364, '', 'AVER MEDIA VC322 Market Leading 4K PTZ USB Video Conferencing', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVER MEDIA VC322 Market Leading 4K PTZ USB Video Conferencing</strong><br />\r\nDesigned for Huddle Rooms</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A 4K PTZ USB camera provides vivid lifelike video quality; accompanied by a high quality speakerphone that picks up crystal clear audio in the meeting room with no cable clutter, this is the AVer VC322 and it is the USB camera your meeting room is looking for. With its large FOV, everyone at the table is clearly visible. All you need is to plug in the camera and start a video collaboration with any video conferencing software or cloud service you&rsquo;re familiar with. No more bulky systems; the VC322 is compactly designed to perfectly fit your meeting space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Perfect Choice for Huddle Rooms</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With outstanding video quality in 4K and large 85&deg; field of view, the VC322 easily puts all participants in clear focus. Furthermore, its sharp and compactly designed speakerphone makes sure everyone can hear and be heard. The VC322 is your best choice for your meetings of up to 6 people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A Real Face to Face Experience with the 4K PTZ Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>VC322 breaks the expectations of what a USB camera can do. With the VC322 there is no need to tolerate bad video quality anymore. Its 4K video provides superb resolution, color balance, and detail. It delivers ultra-sharp clarity with a lens that allows you to pan, tilt and zoom precisely without losing focus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Powerful Speakerphone with 360&deg; Pickup</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>One is enough. No more daisy-chaining speakerphones, the VC322 makes your table tidy again with a powerful speakerphone that removes the necessity of squeezing in with colleagues in order to be heard. Two uni-directional microphones ensure everyone sounds as good as they look and with an audio pickup range of 6m in diameter it completely optimizes your meeting experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Large Field of View for Meeting Spaces</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The VC322&rsquo;s 85&deg; FOV easily puts everyone at the table into frame. No more frustration over camera controls or seating arrangements. Just focus on the meeting and let the camera do all the work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Just Plug-and-Play</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The VC322 provides a simple, easy to use experience. Just plug and play, no more waiting for technicians to work on complicated settings. Plug in the camera and within seconds you&rsquo;re ready to experience video collaboration with any video conferencing application and cloud service you&rsquo;re familiar with.</p>\r\n', '2412201647435fe4c62fd59a9.png', 22900, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:47:43', 0, '2020-12-24 16:47:43'),
(365, '', 'CAM340 Industry Leading Professional Ultra HD 4K Huddle Room Collaboration USB Cameras', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVER MEDIA CAM340 Industry Leading Professional Ultra HD 4K Huddle Room Collaboration USB Cameras</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Meet the CAM340 - the next generation of intelligent camera that gives you the freedom to express yourself and collaborate anywhere. Unbox, unfold, and connect to your computer and instantly start a next generation video communication experience for huddle and small conference rooms. The CAM340 is compatible with all of your favorite applications; connecting to virtually any desktop or laptop, via a single USB cable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cutting Edge 4K Ultra HD</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAM340 uses a Sony&trade; high quality sensor and multi-lens glass to provide you the sharpest video you can find. The CAM340&rsquo;s advanced image processing engine allows for natural, vividly colored details to be displayed even under challenging lighting conditions and very low latency.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>94&deg; Wide Angle, No Distortion!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fit everyone into frame! The high quality multi-glass lens with deep focus, fast-F stop, and super high resolution allow for everyone at the table and whiteboard to be in perfect focus all at the same time, with minimal distortion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pan, Tilt, and Zoom Like 4X Optical Zoom Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With our Ultra 4K CAM340 you can zoom in up to 4X* as if it was a traditional optical camera. Zoom in and move around, no moving parts, and no quality lost as with typical digital zoom, because this is 4K.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*not available in 4K or 60 fps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tricky Light Conditions, No Worry!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>No matter if you are in low or bright light, natural or fluorescent, or have multiple types of lighting AVer&rsquo;s CAM340 white balance and exposure will provide you with accurate color to its fullest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Easy Plug-and-Play For Any App</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just plug in the USB cable and go, no drivers to install, no power cable needed. Have the freedom to use the tools of your trade and as long as you have a USB3.0 port, you&rsquo;re good to go!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Package contents</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB3.0 4K camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power adapter (for USB 2.0 usage)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB3.0 type-C to type-A (6ft) cable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB3.0 type-A to type-C adapter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quick guide</p>\r\n', '2412201648135fe4c64d70294.png', 21900, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:48:13', 0, '2020-12-24 16:48:13'),
(366, '', 'AVer Media CAM520 Camera for All Kinds of Businesses', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVer Media CAM520 The USB Plug-and-Play and Professional Unified Communications Camera for All Kinds of Businesses</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AVer CAM520 is designed to meet the unified communications and collaboration needs of a variety of businesses. Widely compatible and ideal for numerous applications and integration with other equipment, its full HD 1080p 60fps capability ensure high-quality real-time communication whether in conference rooms or industrial environments. Moreover, CAM520 provides a USB connection, perfect for software- or cloud-based video collaboration and other applications that require very high quality video.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Full HD 1080p 60fps Resolution</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD 1080p 60fps has never felt more lifelike! Even in poor lighting you can enjoy detailed, crystal-clear views of people and objects at the far site, and motion blur is nonexistent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PTZ Camera with 18X Total Zoom</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Boasting pan-tilt-zoom (PTZ) and 18X zoom, the CAM520 will meet your needs for any kind of collaboration. Their quick auto-focus, fast lens, large aperture, subtle movement steps, and wide angle ensure an unbeatably smooth and lifelike video experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Up to 10 Camera Presets</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>No need to waste time panning and zooming manually during meetings &ndash; simply preset up to 10 locations ahead of time on the remote control, and you can shift the camera from a wide view of the room to a close-up of an object with just the press of a button.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Simply Plug and Play</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Simply plug the CAM520&#39;s USB connector into a desktop or laptop, and you&rsquo;re ready to go! With no need for device drivers, the CAM520 are able to provide top-quality video images at any time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Package contents</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remote control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5m USB cable to PC (USB2.0 mini B to PC)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power supply</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quick-start guide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tabletop/wall/ceiling mount</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.35mm tripod mounting screw</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Velcro</p>\r\n', '2412201648355fe4c6638edce.png', 35900, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:48:35', 0, '2020-12-24 16:48:35'),
(367, '', 'AVer Media CAM530 Camera for All Kinds of Businesses', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVer Media CAM530 The USB Plug-and-Play, HDMI, and Professional Unified Communications Camera for All Kinds of Businesses</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AVer CAM530 is designed to meet the unified communications and collaboration needs of a variety of businesses. Widely compatible and ideal for numerous applications and integration with other equipment, its full HD 1080p 60fps capability ensure high-quality real-time communication whether in conference rooms or industrial environments. Moreover, CAM530 provides both a USB and HDMI connection, perfect for software- or cloud-based video collaboration and other applications that require very high quality video.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PTZ Camera with 18X Total Zoom</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Boasting pan-tilt-zoom (PTZ) and 18X zoom, the CAM530 will meet your needs for any kind of collaboration. Their quick auto-focus, fast lens, large aperture, subtle movement steps, and wide angle ensure an unbeatably smooth and lifelike video experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Full HD 1080p 60fps Resolution</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD 1080p 60fps has never felt more lifelike! Even in poor lighting you can enjoy detailed, crystal-clear views of people and objects at the far site, and motion blur is nonexistent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Up to 10 Camera Presets</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>No need to waste time panning and zooming manually during meetings &ndash; simply preset up to 10 locations ahead of time on the remote control, and you can shift the camera from a wide view of the room to a close-up of an object with just the press of a button.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Simply Plug and Play</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Simply plug the CAM530&rsquo;s USB connector into a desktop or laptop, or CAM530&rsquo;s HDMI connector into a display, and you&rsquo;re ready to go! With no need for device drivers, the Cam530 are able to provide top-quality video images at any time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package contents</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remote control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5m USB cable to PC (USB2.0 mini B to PC)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power supply</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quick-start guide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tabletop/wall/ceiling mount</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.35mm tripod mounting screw</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Velcro</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3m HDMI cable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RS232 adapter</p>\r\n', '2412201648555fe4c677b4d46.png', 42900, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:48:55', 0, '2020-12-24 16:48:55'),
(368, '', 'AVer CAM540 Bring Superior 4K Quality to Your Meeting', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVer CAM540 Bring Superior 4K Quality to Your Meeting</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4K Conference Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAM540 brings AVer&rsquo;s new SmartFrame auto-framing technology to 4K high definition video conferencing. With a wide field of view, the CAM540 is guaranteed to provide an incredible communication experience in your meeting room.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVer SmartFrame Gets Your Meeting Started Fast</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAM540 delivers AVer&rsquo;s latest camera technology to your meeting room with AVer SmartFrame.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SmartFrame maximizes the viewable field with a one click auto-framing solution that effortlessly puts everyone in your meeting into frame fast and with no hassle. No more complex settings or time wasting controls simply click a single button and find the most comfortable distance for your meeting with the CAM540 and SmartFrame.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4K Ultra HD</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAM540 supports a high-end Sony 4K CMOS that allows for 4K video to be captured at 30 frames per second, providing users with an unbelievably lifelike meeting experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>High Detail 16X Total Zoom</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAM540 is built with cutting edge 16X total zoom capability. Bringing an unseen level of clarity to video conferencing, the CAM540 maximizes your team&rsquo;s collaboration with simple, easy, and efficient video communication.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Make an Impression with the CAM540&rsquo;s Stylish New Design</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAM540 offers a new sleek and fluid design for conferencing rooms. Compared to traditional designs, the CAM540 is elegant and compact to save you space. The CAM540 easily fits your modern meeting room and provides an experience that both novices and experts can enjoy in style.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Just Plug-and-Play</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAM540 provides a simple, easy to use experience. With a USB3.1 Gen1 Type-C cable, the CAM540 allows for simple plug-and-play functionality that means no more complicated settings. Plug in the camera and within seconds you&rsquo;re ready to experience video collaboration with any video conferencing application and cloud service you&rsquo;re familiar with.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reliable Video and Outstanding Quality</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AVer&#39;s quality manufacturing process ensures that the CAM540 is always ready for use. Designed for durability, the CAM540 camera is built to be durable and reliable. With AVer&rsquo;s industry leading 3+2 years warranty program, we make sure that AVer is always there with the support you deserve.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ultra-crystal clear image supports up to 4K</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Frame rate: 4K, 1080p , 720p , 640x480, 320x240</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AutoFraming for smart macro shooting people for an appropriate composition</p>\r\n\r\n<p>16X Zoom</p>\r\n\r\n<p>86&deg; field of view</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quick auto focus: minimum working distance 1 meter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Back light compensation and 2D noise reduction technology for optimizing light balance in different conditions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Standard tripod thread</p>\r\n', '2412201652085fe4c738dd1b2.png', 65000, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:52:08', 0, '2020-12-24 16:52:08');
