(369, '', 'AVer FONE520 USB Conference Phone', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AVer FONE520 USB Conference Phone</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FONE520 USB Conference Phone</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy crystal-clear conference calls with the AVer FONE520 speakerphone. Connect via USB and start talking in seconds.FONE520&rsquo;s stylish design makes it easy for you to take your conference room anywhere with this portable speakerphone. The AVer FONE520 speakerphone works right out of the box with leading UC platforms; and yes &ndash; it can also play your favorite music!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Crystal Clear Audio Quality</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy crystal-clear calls with the FONE520 which can filter out background noise. Your conversations will sound vibrant and natural anywhere with the well designed FONE520 in the executive&rsquo;s office, small meeting rooms, or conference halls.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Automatic Echo Cancellation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The FONE520 adopts advanced noise and echo cancellation technologies it brings you hassle-free conferencing and full-duplex audio experience. In addition, the FONE520 detects voices and ensures everyone is heard no matter if the conversation is unidirectional or bidirectional.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Noise Suppression Technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Feeling irritated by background keyboard typing and paper shuffling noises while you are on a conference call? With FONE520&rsquo;s noise suppression technology, you will never have to listen to those annoying sounds again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Full Duplex Microphone Array with 360&deg; Room Coverage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The FONE520 is equipped with a fine-tuned speaker and three unidirectional microphones to provide a full 360-degree coverage to capture audio from up to 9m away the system can also be connected with up to 4 delegate microphone stations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>USB Plug-and-Play</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Connect to any device and be ready to talk in seconds. The FONE520 can be easily connected to your PC, tablet, or smartphone via a USB cable. Audio conferencing has never been this easy!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Full Compatibility with UC systems</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Seamless integration with most UC systems such as Skype&trade;, Skype for Business, Google Hangouts&trade;, FaceTime&reg;, Cisco Webex&reg;, GoToMeeting&reg;, Adobe&reg; Connect&trade;, BlueJeans, Zoom, Vidyo&reg;, Fuze, WebRTC, V-Cube, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Package contents</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>FONE520 main unit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power adaptor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>16&#39; USB cable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3&#39; phone-in cable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quick guide</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n', '2412201653005fe4c76c077cc.png', 22900, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:53:00', 0, '2020-12-24 16:53:00'),
(370, '', 'AVer VC520 USB Video Conferencing Camera', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย AVer VC520 USB Video Conferencing Camera</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Professional conferencing system for mid-to-large rooms</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The VC520 Pro is equipped with a 12X optical zoom and daisy-chain speakerphone that deliver a lifelike audiovisual experience. With 1080p HD quality, Sony True WDR, and IP-based management features, the VC520 Pro is the professional conferencing system your enterprise needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Perfect Audio for Professional Conferencing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience lifelike audio in various sizes of meeting rooms with the VC520 Pro. The speakerphone&rsquo;s pickup range is up to 15 ft., or you can daisy-chain two additional speakerphones and reach up to 45 ft. Touch controls make it easy to adjust or mute the volume, and echo cancellation ensures a steady audio experience. You can also connect extra microphones for ultra-clear voice pickup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"VC520 pro\" src=\"https://communication.aver.com/Upload/Model/2354/visualimg_2s.png\" /></p>\r\n', '2412201653195fe4c77f7baa6.jpg', 66000, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:53:19', 0, '2020-12-24 16:53:19'),
(371, '', 'Aver Media Cam520 pro', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>บริษัท 99aplus มีจำหน่าย Aver media Cam520 pro. The CAM520 Pro is equipped with a high-class 18X total zoom that displays every detail in crystal-clear quality. Also, on-trend technology such as AVer SmartFrame, Sony True WDR, and IP video streaming provide enterprises with a professional meeting experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sony super-low-light 2M pixel sensor, clear and natural imaging in low-light conditions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution: (16:9) 1920 x 1080, 1600 x 900, 1280 x 720, 960 x 540, 848 x 480, 800 x 448, 640 x 360, 424 x 240, 320 x 180; (4:3) 800 x 600, 640 x 480, 480 x 360, 320 x 240 at 60, 30, 15fps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SmartFrame for automatic FOV adjustment to fit all participants</p>\r\n\r\n<p>True WDR up to 120db: Superb backlight compensation technology for optimizing light balance in high-contrast conditions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zoom: 18X total zoom (12X optical zoom)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wide field of view (DFOV): 82&deg;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lens focal length: 3.9 mm (wide) ~ 47.3 mm (tele)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lens F#: 1.8 (wide) ~ 2.8 (tele)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mirror, flip, AE, white balance: auto/manual override via PTZApp</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Minimum focus distance: 1.5 m</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Standard tripod screw holes and Kensington slot</p>\r\n', '2412201653405fe4c79410cdc.jpg', 59000, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:53:40', 0, '2020-12-24 16:53:40'),
(372, '', 'Aver Media Cam520 Pro(POE)', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>บริษัท 99aplus มีจำหน่าย Aver Media Cam520 Pro(POE). The CAM520 Pro is equipped with a high-class 18X total zoom that displays every detail in crystal-clear quality. Also, on-trend technology such as AVer SmartFrame, Sony True WDR, and IP video streaming provide enterprises with a professional meeting experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sony super-low-light 2M pixel sensor, clear and natural imaging in low-light conditions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution: (16:9) 1920 x 1080, 1600 x 900, 1280 x 720, 960 x 540, 848 x 480, 800 x 448, 640 x 360, 424 x 240, 320 x 180; (4:3) 800 x 600, 640 x 480, 480 x 360, 320 x 240 at 60, 30, 15fps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SmartFrame for automatic FOV adjustment to fit all participants</p>\r\n\r\n<p>True WDR up to 120db: Superb backlight compensation technology for optimizing light balance in high-contrast conditions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zoom: 18X total zoom (12X optical zoom)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wide field of view (DFOV): 82&deg;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lens focal length: 3.9 mm (wide) ~ 47.3 mm (tele)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lens F#: 1.8 (wide) ~ 2.8 (tele)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mirror, flip, AE, white balance: auto/manual override via PTZApp</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Minimum focus distance: 1.5 m</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Standard tripod screw holes and Kensington slot</p>\r\n', '2412201654005fe4c7a8c51b0.jpg', 70000, 0, 0, '2020-12-24 16:54:00', 0, '2020-12-24 16:54:00'),
(373, '', 'Aver Media speaker for vc520pro', 23, 82, '', 'Video Conference', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>บริษัท 99 aplus มีจำหน่าย The AVer VC520 PRO Expansion Speakerphone is designed to expand the VC520 PRO Video Conferencing System&#39;s microphone pickup range and maximize audio coverage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The AVer VC520 PRO Expansion Speakerphone is designed to expand the VC520 PRO Video Conferencing System&#39;s microphone pickup range and maximize audio coverage. This full-duplex speakerphone is equipped with a powerful speaker and a mic that picks up voice within 360&deg; at up to 15&#39;, giving you configuration flexibility regardless of your room</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For VC520 PRO Video Conferencing System</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Increase Voice Pickup Range up to 30&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximize Audio Coverage, 6W Speaker</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full Speakerphone Controls Available</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connectors</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1 x RJ45 to VC520 PRO Speakerphone</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1 x RJ45 to Other Expansion Speakerphone</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Microphone</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Dual-Microphone Array</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;360&deg; Pickup Pattern</p>\r\n\r\n<p>15&#39; / 4.6 m Radius</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Frequency Response: