(388, '', 'Panasonic AG-MC200G Super-Directional Camera Mountable Shotgun Microphone', 11, 89, '', 'ไมค์โครโฟนติดหัวกล้อง', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายไมค์ติดหัวกล้อง&nbsp;</strong><strong>Panasonic AG-MC200G Super-Directional Camera<br />\r\nMountable Shotgun Microphone</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic AG-MC200G</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AG-MC200G Super-Directional Electret Microphone from Panasonic is a camera mounted condenser microphone with superior directional characteristics than that of standard unidirectional microphones. The focused pickup of the AG-MC200G eliminates audio at the sides of the microphone, greatly reducing ambiance and potential feedback problems. The AG-MC200G uses +48V phantom power and feature a standard XLR output. The microphone is ideal for camera use, as well as portable recording devices and field mixers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Super-directional Pick Up</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The super-directional characteristic of the AG-MC200G rivals standard unidirectional microphones. The AG-MC200G is ideal for isolating signal in high noise environments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Balanced Output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The balanced 3-pin XLR output provides high signal gain and low noise floor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stabilized Power Supply Circuit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AG-MC200G uses standard +48V phantom power.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic AG-MC200G Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Analog Performance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Transducer Electret Condenser</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Frequency Range 160 Hz to 20 kHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Signal to Noise Ratio 69 dB&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum SPL 127 dB SPL</p>\r\n\r\n<p>THD 1%</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Impedance 100 Ohms &plusmn; 30% @ 1 kHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sensitivity -40 dB at 1 kHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output Connectors 1 x 3-Pin XLR</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Current Consumption 2.0 mA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Voltage 48 V</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Length 6.38&quot; / 162 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Diameter 0.83&quot; / 21 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 3.81 oz / 108 g</p>\r\n', '3012200903015fec4245efd14.jpg', 14000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:03:01', 0, '2020-12-30 09:03:01'),
(389, '', 'Panasonic AJ-MC700 - Microphone and Holder Kit for AJ-D700 DVC PRO', 11, 89, '', 'ไมค์โครโฟนติดหัวกล้อง', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายไมค์ติดหัวกล้อง Panasonic AJ-MC700 - Microphone and Holder Kit for AJ-D700 DVC PRO Camcorder&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic AJ-MC700 Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Panasonic AJ-MC700 is a microphone kit for DVCPRO camcorders AJ-D700 and AJ-SDX900. The kit includes a shotgun mic, windscreen and a mic holder that screw-mounts to the top of the camera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic AJ-MC700 Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 0.54 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 12.5 x 3.2 x 2.2&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200903245fec425c9b942.jpg', 39000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:03:24', 0, '2020-12-30 09:03:24'),
(390, '', 'Panasonic SHAN-TM700 Quick-Release Tripod Adapter - for AJ-D700 DVC PRO Camcorder', 11, 89, '', 'ไมค์โครโฟนติดหัวกล้อง', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic SHAN-TM700 Quick-Release Tripod Adapter - for AJ-D700 DVC PRO Camcorder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic SHAN-TM700 Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Panasonic SHAN-TM700 is a quick-release camera mounting plate for The AJ-D700 camcorder. This plate allows the camcorder to release from the support and be used handheld in a very easy and fast fashion. It is reattached to the tripod just as fast and easy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic SHAN-TM700 Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 1.8 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 11.4 x 4.0 x 1.9&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200903475fec4273816a3.jpg', 9700, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:03:47', 0, '2020-12-30 09:03:47'),
(391, '', 'Sony ECM-XM1 (ECMXM1) Shotgun Monaural Microphone', 11, 89, '', 'ไมค์โครโฟนติดหัวกล้อง', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายไมค์ติดหัวกล้อง Sony ECM-XM1 (ECMXM1) Shotgun Monaural Microphone</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Sony ECM-XM1 short microphone is supplied as part of the HVR-Z5, HVR-Z7, HVR-S270 and HXR-NX5 professional camcorders.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sensitivity (at 1KHz)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;-20dB &plusmn; 3.5dB*7&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Signal-to-noise ratio&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>78dB, typical&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Frequency Response&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>50~20,000Hz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum Input sound pressure level*8&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>127dB SPL</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dynamic Range&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>111dB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*7 0dB = 1V/Pa at 1kHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*8 0dB SPL = 20 &mu;Pa</p>\r\n', '3012200904065fec42865b36d.jpg', 135000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:04:06', 0, '2020-12-30 09:04:06'),
(392, '', 'Panasonic AG-MC200 Camera Mountable Shotgun Microphone', 11, 89, '', 'ไมค์โครโฟนติดหัวกล้อง', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายไมค์โครโฟนติดหัวกล้อง Panasonic ag-mc200&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Panasonic AG-MC200G Super-Directional Camera Mountable Shotgun Microphone</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic AG-MC200G Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AG-MC200G Super-Directional Electret Microphone from Panasonic is a camera mounted condenser microphone with superior directional characteristics than that of standard unidirectional microphones. The focused pickup of the AG-MC200G eliminates audio at the sides of the microphone, greatly reducing ambiance and potential feedback problems. The AG-MC200G uses +48V phantom power and feature a standard XLR output. The microphone is ideal for camera use, as well as portable recording devices and field mixers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Super-directional Pick Up</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The super-directional characteristic of the AG-MC200G rivals standard unidirectional microphones. The AG-MC200G is ideal for isolating signal in high noise environments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Balanced Output</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The balanced 3-pin XLR output provides high signal gain and low noise floor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stabilized Power Supply Circuit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AG-MC200G uses standard +48V phantom power.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Panasonic AG-MC200G Specs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Analog Performance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Transducer Electret Condenser</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Frequency Range 160 Hz to 20 kHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Signal to Noise Ratio 69 dB&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum SPL 127 dB SPL</p>\r\n\r\n<p>THD 1%</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Impedance 100 Ohms &plusmn; 30% @ 1 kHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sensitivity -40 dB at 1 kHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output Connectors 1 x 3-Pin XLR</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Current Consumption 2.0 mA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Voltage 48 V</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Length 6.38&quot; / 162 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Diameter 0.83&quot; / 21 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 3.81 oz / 108 g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 0.6 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 9.685 x 4.646 x 2.835&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200904235fec4297174d2.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:04:23', 0, '2020-12-30 09:04:23'),
(393, '', 'Sony BP-U90 Lithium-Ion Battery Pack (14.4V, 85Wh)', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแบตเตอรี่ Sony BP-U90 Lithium-Ion Battery Pack (14.4V, 85Wh)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Sony BP-U90</strong>&nbsp;is a 14.4V, 85Wh lithium-ion battery for XDCAM EX camcorders. It features an INFO function that communicates battery status to the camcorder, which in turn displays the exact battery life on LCD and viewfinder. Even when the camcorder is powered off, the camcorder LCD will continue to display battery life, and the battery itself has LED displays that indicate remaining battery life at the push of a button.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Voltage Nominal: 14.4 VDC&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum: 16.4 VDC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity 85 Wh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Charging Time Using the BC-U1 charger: approx. 220 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Temperature -4 to 113&deg;F (-20 to 45&deg;C)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions 1.8 x 4.9 x 2.8&quot; (4 x 12 x 7 cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 1.4 lb (630 g)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 1.4 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 5.2 x 3.0 x 2.4&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200905565fec42f4407cb.jpg', 25000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:05:56', 0, '2020-12-30 09:05:56');
