(394, '', 'Sony BP-U60T Lithium-Ion Battery with 4-Pin Power Output', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแบตเตอรี่ Sony BP-U60T Lithium-Ion Battery with 4-Pin Power Output</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Sony BP-U60T</strong>&nbsp;Lithium-Ion Battery with 4-Pin Power Output is a 57Wh battery compatible with XDCAM camcorders and decks such as the PMW-200, PMW-150, PMW-100, and PMW-50. It features a 4-pin XLR output that allows you to provide 2A of power supply to additional devices. It provides on average about two hours of power to most of the compatible camcorders.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The battery features an INFO function that communicates capacity, charge time, and charge cycle data to camcorders and chargers supporting the INFO function.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chemistry Lithium-ion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output Voltage 14.4 V DC, 2 A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity 57 Wh, 39 mAh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Output Connector 4-pin Hirose</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions 1.7 x 3.3 x 2.8&quot; (4.2 x 8.3 x 7 cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 0.77 lb (350 g)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 1.15 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 4.409 x 3.228 x 2.598&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200906165fec4308f0ac9.jpg', 16800, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:06:16', 0, '2020-12-30 09:06:16'),
(395, '', 'Sony BP-U30 Lithium-Ion Battery - for PMW-EX1 Camcorder, INFO Function, 23 Wh', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแบตเตอรี่ Sony BP-U30 Lithium-Ion Battery - for PMW-EX1 Camcorder, INFO Function, 23 Wh</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Sony BP-U30</strong>&nbsp;is a lithium-ion battery designed for professional video shooting in both the field and the studio. This battery is equipped with the INFO function that communicates battery status data to the PMW-EX1 camcorder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chemistry Li-Ion, Lithium-Ion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output Voltage 16.4 VDC/14.4 VDC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Connection Specific to PMW-EX1 Camcorder</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity 23 Wh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 8 oz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>220 g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (WxHxD) 1 11/16 x 1 13/16 x 2 3/4&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.15 x 4.51 x 6.97 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 0.65 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 3.6 x 3.1 x 1.9&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200906355fec431b577f2.jpg', 8900, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:06:35', 0, '2020-12-30 09:06:35'),
(396, '', 'Sony BP-U60 Lithium-Ion Battery - for PMW-EX1 Camcorder, INFO Function, 56 Wh', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแบตเตอรี่ สำหรับกล้องวีดีโอ Sony BP-U60 Lithium-Ion Battery for PXW-FS7</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony BP-U60</strong>&nbsp;Lithium-Ion Battery - for PMW-EX1 Camcorder, INFO Function, 56 Wh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Sony BP-U60</strong>&nbsp;is a lithium-ion battery designed for professional video shooting in both the field and the studio. This battery is equipped with the INFO function that communicates battery status data to the PMW-EX1 camcorder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chemistry Li-Ion, Lithium-Ion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output Voltage 16.4 VDC/14.4 VDC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Connection Specific to PMW-EX1 Camcorder</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity 56 Wh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 15 oz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>350 g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (WxHxD) 1 11/16 x 3 1/4 x 2 3/4&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.15 x 8.25 x 6.97 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 1.05 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 3.6 x 3.0 x 2.2&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200906525fec432c81716.jpg', 16800, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:06:52', 0, '2020-12-30 09:06:52'),
(397, '', 'Sony NP-F970 L-Series Info-Lithium Battery Pack (6300mAh)', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแบตเตอรี่ Sony NP-F970 L-Series Info-Lithium Battery Pack (6300mAh)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nแบตเตอรี่สำหรับ SONY PXW-Z150,HXR-NX100</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony NP-F970 Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Small and lightweight, Sony&#39;s NP-F970 Info-Lithium Battery Pack (6300mAh) provides the advantages of lithium-ion, meaning it can be charged or discharged at anytime without developing memory effect. This means the battery never loses its ability to hold a full charge. The NP-F970 displays remaining battery time on the LCD as well as in the viewfinder by continuously communicating with the camcorder. The battery lasts for up to 12 hours on a single full charge. Sony&#39;s Info-Lithium battery packs have a built-in micro processor that accurately calculates remaining battery life in minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony NP-F970 Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mount / Series Type Sony L-Series</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chemistry Lithium-Ion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity (Wh) Not specified by manufacturer</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amp-Hours 6300.00 mAh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output Voltage 7.2 VDC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (W x H x D) 2.2 x 2.9 x 1.5&quot; / 57.0 x 73.0 x 38.0 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 12.30 oz / 350 g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 0.8 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 8.3 x 3.4 x 2.4&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200907105fec433e6ad5b.jpg', 6990, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:07:10', 0, '2020-12-30 09:07:10'),
(398, '', 'Sony NP-FV100A Rechargeable Battery Pack (3410mAh, 6.8-8.4V)', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแบตเตอรี่ Sony NP-FV100A Rechargeable Battery Pack (3410mAh, 6.8-8.4V)&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony NP-FV100A Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Sony NP-FV100A is a part of Sony&#39;s InfoLITHIUM V Series of batteries, designed with the capability to exchange data with compatible equipment. It communicates battery consumption data and remaining time in minutes, useful for long shoots. The NP-FV100A is compatible with all Handycam camcorders.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>รุ่นความจุสูงสุดของแบตเตอรี่แพคแบบชาร์จได้ InfoLITHIUM&trade; V ซีรีส์ กำลังแสดงตัวบอกปริมาณพลังงานคงเหลือที่แม่นยำใน Handycam&reg; พลังที่แข็งแกร่งขึ้นเมื่อเทียบกับรุ่นก่อนหน้า NP-FV100 ชาร์จอย่างรวดเร็วด้วยอุปกรณ์ชาร์จเสริม BC-QM1/AC-VQV10</p>\r\n\r\n<p>แรงดันไฟฟ้าเอาต์พุตเฉลี่ย: 7.4V</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ความจุ: 25Wh (3410mAh)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ขนาด (ประมาณ): กว้าง 31.8 มม. X สูง 55.5 มม. X ลึก 45.1 มม. (1 5/16 นิ้ว X 2 1/4 นิ้ว X 1 13/16 นิ้ว)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>น้ำหนัก (ประมาณ): 145 ก. (5.2 ออนซ์)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony NP-FV100A Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amp-Hours 3410.00 mAh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum Output Voltage 8.4 VDC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chemistry Lithium-Ion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (W x H x D) 1.3 x 2.2 x 1.8&quot; / 3.3 x 5.6 x 4.5 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 7 oz / 200 g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 0.45 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 5.4 x 3.5 x 2.5&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200908485fec43a06ed2e.jpg', 6990, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:08:48', 0, '2020-12-30 09:08:48'),
(399, '', 'Sony AC Adapter AC-VQ1050D and Twin Charger For L-Series Batteries', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแท่นชาร์ตแบตเตอรี่ Sony AC Adapter and Twin Charger For L-Series Batteries</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony AC-VQ1050D (Sony Battery Charger)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>แท่นชาร์จ InfoLITHIUM&trade; สำหรับแบตเตอรี่ InfoLITHIUM&trade; L-Series ที่ให้อัตราชาร์จอันรวดเร็วทำให้คุณสามารถชาร์จแบตเตอรี่ได้อย่างรวดเร็วแม้ระหว่างเร่งรีบ พร้อมจอแสดงผล LCD แสดงสถานะแบตเตอรี่บนตัวแท่น และขั้วต่อ DC Adaptor สำหรับการใช้งานในรถ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>แท่นชาร์จแบบชาร์จเร็ว</p>\r\n\r\n<p>จอแสดงผล LCD แสดงสถานะแบตเตอรี่บนตัวแท่น</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ระบบ Relay charging สำหรับการชาร์จแบตเตอรี่พร้อมกันหลายก้อน</p>\r\n\r\n<p>สายชาร์จ DCC-VQ1 ทำให้สามารถใช้งานในรถยนต์ได้อย่างสะดวกสบาย</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Switches from AC Adapter to Charger</li>\r\n	<li>LCD Displays Charge Status</li>\r\n	<li>345 Min Approx. Dual Battery Charge Time</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony AC-VQ1051D Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Sony AC Adapter and Twin Charger For L-Series Batteries is a power adapter that at the flip of a switch turns into a two-battery charger for Sony&#39;s L-series batteries. Four power cords come included.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LCD display indicates: battery life, charging time, total charging time, last use year and month, and total number of charging cycles</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony AC-VQ1051D Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output Voltage DC 8.4 V / 1.8 A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Requirements 100-240 V, 50/60 Hz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions Approx. 4.8 x 2.1 x 5.3&quot; (12.2 x 5.3 x 13.5 cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight .9 lb (400 g)</p>\r\n', '3012200909065fec43b2e4e34.jpg', 8990, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:09:06', 0, '2020-12-30 09:09:06'),
(400, '', 'Sony AC-VQV10 AC Adaptor/Charger', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแท่นชาร์ตแบตเตอรี่ Sony AC-VQV10 AC Adaptor/Charger</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The dual slot Sony AC-VQV10 AC Adaptor/Charger quickly charges Sony V, H, and P Series InfoLITHIUM batteries. The AC-VQV10&#39;s consecutive charging feature automatically starts charging the second battery after the first has completed its cycle. This Adaptor/Charger also gives you the option of seeing the remaining battery life on the built-in LCD.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dual battery slot for consecutive charging 1</li>\r\n	<li>Selectable viewing of remaining battery life on LCD</li>\r\n	<li>Compatible with Sony V, H, and P InfoLITHIUM batteries</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery Type V/H/P InfoLITHIUM Series</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Requirements 100-240V, 50/60Hz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Output 8.4VDC, 2.2A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions 4 x 2.6 x 4.4&quot; (100 x 67 x 111mm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 11.7 oz (330g)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 1.45 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 7.2 x 6.0 x 3.4&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200909245fec43c4965d3.jpg', 5000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:09:24', 0, '2020-12-30 09:09:24'),
(401, '', 'Sony ACCL1BP Power supply & fast dual charger for L series batteries', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแท่นชาร์ตแบตเตอรี่ Sony ACCL1BP Power supply &amp; fast dual charger for L series batteries</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power supply &amp; fast dual charger for HDV and NXCAM camcorders using L series batteries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ACCL1BP kit includes one Sony NPF970 high capacity L-series Li-Ion battery pack (6600mAH) and one ACVQ1051D dual slot Fast Charger/AC Adaptor. The NPF970 battery provides the longest running time of all L series batteries. Incorporates Sony InfoLithium technology which enables compatible camcorders to accurately report the charge remaining. The ACVQ1051D is a dual slot fast charger for L series InfoLITHIUM&trade; batteries. Quick charging of up to two batteries. LCD displays battery charge status.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Highlights:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Includes one Sony NPF970 high capacity L-series Li-Ion battery pack (6600mAH) and one ACVQ1051D dual slot Fast Charger/AC Adaptor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The NPF970 battery provides the longest running time of all L series batteries. Incorporates Sony InfoLithium technology which enables compatible camcorders to accurately report the charge remaining.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ACVQ1051D is a dual slot fast charger for L series InfoLITHIUM&trade; batteries. Quick charging of up to two batteries. LCD displays battery charge status.</p>\r\n', '3012200909425fec43d626491.jpg', 13000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:09:42', 0, '2020-12-30 09:09:42'),
(402, '', 'จำหน่ายแท่นชาร์ตแบตเตอรี่ Sony SONY ACC-V1BP dual charger/AC adaptor', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแท่นชาร์ตแบตเตอรี่ Sony SONY ACC-V1BP dual charger/AC adaptor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>แท่นชาร์จแบตเตอรี่กล้อง SONY ACC-V1BP</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make sure your camcorder is always ready to shoot with the ACC-V1BP dual charger/AC adaptor and InfoLITHIUM&reg; rechargeable battery kit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sony&#39;s ACC-V1BP</strong>&nbsp;accessory kit includes the AC-VQV10 dual charger / AC adaptor and an NP-FV100 high capacity InfoLITHIUM&reg; battery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This accessory kit offers real flexibility for professionals, giving longer battery life and faster re-charging than ever before.<strong>&nbsp;The AC-VQV10</strong>&nbsp;can provide AC power to your camcorder or quickly charge two InfoLITHIUM batteries in sequence. It is fully compatible with InfoLITHIUM V, H &amp; P series batteries. The NP-FV100 high capacity, long-lasting battery powers your camcorder longer than any other battery in the V-series, and has a 15% capacity increase over the NP-FH100. And because it&#39;s InfoLITHIUM you&#39;ll be able to see the remaining battery life displayed on your camcorder&#39;s screen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '3012200910005fec43e8e52e3.jpg', 13000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:10:00', 0, '2020-12-30 09:10:00'),
(403, '', 'Sony BP-U35', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>บริษัท99 aplus มีจำหน่าย แบตเตอรี่ ฺbattery Sony BP-U35<br />\r\nThe BP-U35 is a 35 Wh capacity lithium ion battery optimised for professional video shooting. Its compact size and low weight make the BP-U35 ideal for high-mobility applications such as gimbal mounting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BP-U35 is a 35 Wh capacity lithium ion battery optimised for professional video shooting. Its compact size and low weight make the BP-U35 ideal for high-mobility applications such as gimbal mounting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery status data is continuously communicated to the camera. Remaining capacity is displayed on the camera&rsquo;s LCD monitor and viewfinder, allowing operators to monitor battery status easily and accurately while shooting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BP-U35 offers higher capacity and faster charging time than the previous generation BP-U30.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>GENERAL</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (W x H x D)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;41.5 x 46.1 x 69.7 mm (1 11/16 x 1 7/8 x 2 3/4 inches)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MassApprox.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;235 g (8.3 oz)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum/nominal voltage&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;16.4 V DC/14.4 V DC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;35 Wh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Charging time (using the BC-U1A/U2A)Approx.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;90 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating temperature (when discharging / charging)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-20&deg;C to + 45&deg;C (-4&deg;F to + 113&deg;F) / 0&deg;C to 40&deg;C&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(32&deg;F to 104&deg;F)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remaining capacity display&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Four LED (20, 40, 60, and 80%)</p>\r\n', '3012200910565fec4420458bf.jpg', 9250, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:10:56', 0, '2020-12-30 09:10:56'),
(404, '', 'Sony BP-U70', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>บริษัท 99aplus มีจำหน่าย Sony BP-U70. The BP-U70 is a 72 Wh capacity lithium ion battery that offers an ideal balance of capacity and weight for many professional video applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BP-U70 is a 72 Wh capacity lithium ion battery that offers an ideal balance of capacity and weight for many professional video applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery status data is continuously communicated to the camera. Remaining capacity is displayed on the camera&rsquo;s LCD monitor and viewfinder, allowing operators to monitor battery status easily and accurately while shooting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BP-U70 offers significantly higher capacity while having the same charging time than the previous generation BP-U60.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;(W x H x D)41.5 x 84.5 x 69.7 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;(1 11/16 x 3 3/8 x 2 3/4 inches)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MassApprox.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;450 g (15.9 oz)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum/nominal voltage&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;16.4 V DC/14.4 V DC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;72 Wh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Charging time (using the BC-U1A/U2A)Approx.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;150 min.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating temperature (when discharging / charging)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-20&deg;C to + 45&deg;C (-4&deg;F to + 113&deg;F) / 0&deg;C to 40&deg;C (32&deg;F&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;to 104&deg;F)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remaining capacity display&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Four LED (20, 40, 60, and 80%)</p>\r\n', '3012200911215fec4439ac52e.jpg', 16700, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:11:21', 0, '2020-12-30 09:11:21'),
(405, '', 'Sony BP-U100', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>บริษัท 99 aplus มีจำหน่าย Sony BP-U100<br />\r\nThe BP-U100 is a high performance 97 Wh capacity lithium ion battery optimised for professional video shooting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BP-U100 is a high performance 97 Wh capacity lithium ion battery optimised for professional video shooting. Its high capacity makes the BP-U100 ideal for extended shooting times in the field or in the studio, with the camera either shoulder- or tripod-mounted.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery status data is continuously communicated to the camera. Remaining capacity is displayed on the camera&rsquo;s LCD monitor and viewfinder, allowing operators to monitor battery status easily and accurately while shooting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BP-U100 offers significantly higher capacity than the previous generation BP-U90</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (W x H x D)41.5 x 122.8 x 69.7 mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MassApprox. 645 g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum/nominal voltage16.4 V DC / 14.4 V DC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity97 Wh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Charging time (using the BC-U1A/U2A)Approx. 210 min.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating temperature (when discharging / charging)-20 to +45 &deg;C (-4 to +113 &deg;F) / 0&deg;C to 40&deg;C (32&deg;F to 104&deg;F)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remaining capacity displayFour LED (20, 40, 60, and 80%)</p>\r\n', '3012200911415fec444d7ecdc.jpg', 24200, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:11:41', 0, '2020-12-30 09:11:41'),
(406, '', 'Sony BC-U2A', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>บริษัท 99 aplus มีจำหน่าย Sony BC-U2A<br />\r\nCharges two BP-U90/U60/U60T/U30 batteries<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe BC-U2A battery charger can simultaneously charge two compact BP-U90, BP-U60 / 60T or BP-U30 Lithium-ion batteries at high speed</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Charges two BP-U90/U60/U60T/U30 batteries</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BC-U2A battery charger can simultaneously charge two compact BP-U90, BP-U60 / 60T or BP-U30 Lithium-ion batteries at high speed</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in AC adaptor provides 12 V DC power output while charging one battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BC-U2A also has 12 V DC power output cable to power a camcorder directly, while charging one battery simultaneously.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portable design for ease of use</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BC-U2A has a mass of 620 g (1 lb 6 oz) and dimensions (W x H x D) of 177 x 53.2 x 137 mm (7 x 8 1/8 x 5 1/2 inches).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NOTE: BC-U2A is compliant with safety standard IEC62368-1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power RequirementsAC100V～240V 50/60Hz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power consumption89W</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DC supply[36W] 12V / 3.0A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Charging Voltage16.4V</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (W x H x D)177x53.2x137 (mm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mass620 (g) +DC out cable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Temperature[DC supply]-5&nbsp;℃～+45℃</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Charge] 0℃～+45℃</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Approximate charge times</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BP-U90190 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BP-U60 / 60T150 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BP-U30130 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supplied Accessories</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supplied AccessoriesInstruction manual</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Warranty Paper</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DC out cable</p>\r\n', '3012200912045fec4464a55d4.jpg', 18500, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:12:04', 0, '2020-12-30 09:12:04'),
(407, '', 'Sony BC-U1A', 11, 90, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ SONY', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>บริษัท 99 aplus มีจำหน่าย Sony BC-U1A<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCharges one BP-U90/U60/U60T/U30 battery<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe BC-U1A battery charger charges one compact BP-U90, BP-U60/U60T, BP-U30 Lithium-ion battery at high speed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Charges one BP-U90/U60/U60T/U30 battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BC-U1A battery charger charges one compact BP-U90, BP-U60/U60T, BP-U30 Lithium-ion battery at high speed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in AC adaptor provides 12 V DC power output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BC-U1A also has 12 V DC power output cable to power a camcorder directly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compact design for ease of use</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BC-U1A has a mass of only 340 g (12 oz) and dimensions (W x H x D) of 128 x 45 x 98 mm (5 1/8 x 1 13/16 x 3 7/8 inches).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NOTE: BC-U1A is compliant with safety standard IEC62368-1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power RequirementsAC100V～240V 50/60Hz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power consumption46W</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DC supply[36W] 12V / 3.0A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Charging Voltage16.4V</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (W x H x D)128x45x98 (mm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mass340 (g)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Temperature[DC supply]-5&nbsp;℃～+45℃</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Charge] 0℃～+45℃</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Approximate charge times</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BP-U90190 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BP-U60150 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BP-U30130 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supplied Accessories</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supplied AccessoriesInstruction manual</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Warranty Paper</p>\r\n', '3012200912235fec44772b378.jpg', 9250, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:12:23', 0, '2020-12-30 09:12:23'),
(408, '', 'Panasonic VW-VBG6 Lithium-Ion Battery Pack (7.2V, 5400mAh)', 11, 91, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ PANASONIC', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ ag-px270 vw-vbg6 ราคาพิเศษ&nbsp;<br />\r\nลิเที่ยมแบตเตอรี่สำหรับกล้องวีดีโอ ag-px270</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic VW-VBG6 Lithium-Ion Battery Pack (7.2V, 5400mAh)</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- For Select Panasonic Camcorders</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Compatible with VW-VH04 Battery Holder</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Panasonic VW-VBG6 Lithium-Ion Battery Pack is a 7.2V, 5400mAh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>battery for select Panasonic camcorders. It can also be used with many</p>\r\n\r\n<p>other cameras via an optional Panasonic VW-VH04 Battery Pack Holder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATION PANASONIC VW-VBG6</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Voltage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.2 V</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5400 mAh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight</p>\r\n\r\n<p>0.75 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.5 x 3.7 x 2.6&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200913585fec44d6758a8.jpg', 6000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:13:58', 0, '2020-12-30 09:13:58'),
(409, '', 'Panasonic CGA-D54 Lithium-Ion Battery Pack', 11, 91, '', 'แบตเตอรี่กล้องวีดีโอ PANASONIC', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายแบตเตอรี่ Panasonic CGA-D54 Lithium-Ion Battery Pack</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Select Panasonic Mini DV Camcorders</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic CGA-D54 Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Panasonic&#39;s CGA-D54 is a battery designed to work with select Panasonic MiniDV digital Palmcorders. Its lithium-ion technology can power your camera for up to 9 hours. This battery is immune from &quot;memory&quot; effect; so you can fully recharge it any time you like and there&#39;s no need to wait for it to drain completely.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Panasonic CGA-D54 Specs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mount / Series Type Panasonic CGA-D Series</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chemistry Lithium-Ion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity (Wh) Not specified by manufacturer</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amp-Hours 5400.00 mAh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Output Voltage 7.2 VDC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (W x H x D) Not specified by manufacturer</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight Not specified by manufacturer</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 0.7 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 5.1 x 3.2 x 1.8&quot;</p>\r\n', '3012200914165fec44e86a1fe.jpg', 5500, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:14:16', 0, '2020-12-30 09:14:16'),
