(423, '', 'Panasonic AJ-P2M064AG 64GB microP2 UHS-II Memory Card', 11, 93, '', 'เมมโมรี่การ์ด Panasonic', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายเมมโมรี่การ์ด Panasonic AJ-P2M064AG 64GB microP2 UHS-II Memory Card&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 64GB Capacity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- UHS-II Complaint</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Max. Read Speed: 2Gb/s</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Max. Write Speed: 200Mb/s</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Proof 7 Protection from Environment</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Safety Fuse</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- RAID-Type Error Correction System</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- CPS Password Protection</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>The 64GB microP2 UHS-II Memory Card</strong>&nbsp;from Panasonic is an SDXC UHS-II compliant flash card with the same form factor as a full-size SD card. It features a maximum read speed of 2Gb/s and a maximum write speed of 200Mb/s using the AVC-Intra200 recording format (excluding 1080/60p/ 50p). A member of Panasonic&#39;s Proof 7 collection, the card can withstand water and dust, shock and vibration, magnetic fields, X-rays, extreme temperatures and static electricity, and also contains a safety fuse to protect against overheating. Additionally, the card is equipped with a RAID-like error correction system to protect data and CPS password protection. A QR code enables scanning and identification and a Lifetime Counter notifies you when the card approaches the end of its life cycle, which is up to 5 years. A convenient memo area lets you add a note or label. The card includes a storage case. The optional AJ-P2AD1G microP2 Memory Card Adapter enables you to use the microP2 card in the full-size P2 card slots in camcorders.</p>\r\n', '3012200923225fec470a1e2a2.jpg', 17000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:23:22', 0, '2020-12-30 09:23:22'),
(424, '', 'Panasonic AJ-P2M032AG 32GB microP2 UHS-II Memory Card', 11, 93, '', 'เมมโมรี่การ์ด Panasonic', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายเมมโมรี่การ์ด Panasonic AJ-P2M032AG 32GB microP2 UHS-II Memory Card</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>32GB Capacity</li>\r\n	<li>UHS-II Complaint</li>\r\n	<li>Max. Read Speed: 2Gb/s</li>\r\n	<li>Max. Write Speed: 200Mb/s</li>\r\n	<li>Proof 7 Protection from Environment</li>\r\n	<li>Safety Fuse</li>\r\n	<li>RAID-Type Error Correction System</li>\r\n	<li>CPS Password Protection</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The 32GB microP2 UHS-II Memory Card from Panasonic</strong>&nbsp;is an SDHC UHS-II compliant flash card with the same form factor as a full-size SD card. It features a maximum read speed of 2Gb/s and a maximum write speed of 200Mb/s using the AVC-Intra200 recording format (excluding 1080/60p/ 50p). A member of Panasonic&#39;s Proof 7 collection, the card can withstand water and dust, shock and vibration, magnetic fields, X-rays, extreme temperatures and static electricity, and also contains a safety fuse to protect against overheating. Additionally, the card is equipped with a RAID-like error correction system to protect data and CPS password protection. A QR code enables scanning and identification and a Lifetime Counter notifies you when the card approaches the end of its life cycle, which is up to 5 years. A convenient memo area lets you add a note or label. The card includes a storage case. The optional AJ-P2AD1G microP2 Memory Card Adapter enables you to use the microP2 card in the full-size P2 card slots in camcorders.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card Type microP2</li>\r\n	<li>Capacity 32 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Bus Interface Speed UHS-II</li>\r\n	<li>Read Speed Maximum: 2.0 Gb/s</li>\r\n	<li>Write Speed Maximum: 200 Mb/s</li>\r\n	<li>Error Correction RAID-type system</li>\r\n	<li>Data Protection CPS password protection</li>\r\n	<li>Durability Depth rating: 3.28&#39; (1 m) for 30 min (IPX7)</li>\r\n	<li>Shockproof:</li>\r\n	<li>Bending load resistance - Minimum: 20 N</li>\r\n	<li>Twisting torque resistance - Minimum: 0.3 N&bull;m</li>\r\n	<li>X-ray proof: ISO 7816-1 compliant</li>\r\n	<li>Magnetism: Resistant to 1000-gauss DC magnetic field for approx. 1 min</li>\r\n	<li>Electrostatic force-proof: ICE 61000-4-2 compliant</li>\r\n	<li>Protection against excess current / heat: built-in safety fuse</li>\r\n	<li>Insertion / removal cycles: 10,000</li>\r\n	<li>Operating Temperature -13 to 185&deg;F (-25 to 85&deg;C)</li>\r\n	<li>Packaging Info</li>\r\n	<li>Package Weight 0.2 lb</li>\r\n	<li>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 4.5 x 3.25 x 1.5&quot;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '3012200923445fec4720ea1ca.jpg', 9000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:23:44', 0, '2020-12-30 09:23:44'),
(425, '', 'Panasonic AJ-MPD1G microP2 Drive USB 3.0 Card Reader', 11, 93, '', 'เมมโมรี่การ์ด Panasonic', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายการ์ดรีดเดอร์&nbsp; Panasonic AJ-MPD1G microP2 Drive USB 3.0 Card Reader&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Supports Panasonic&#39;s MicroP2 Media</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- USB 3.0 / USB 2.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Bus Powered</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Two Media Card Slots</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Supports Spanned Clips</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Compliant with UHS-II SD Memory Cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Supports up to 2.0GB/S Reading</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Supports SDHC/SDXC Media up to 128GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Plug &amp; Play with Mac &amp; Windows</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>The Panasonic AJ-MPD1G</strong>&nbsp;microP2 Drive USB 3.0 Card Reader supports Panasonic&#39;s MicroP2 card format. microP2 cards are the same size as SD cards, but they feature RAID technology, increased bending and twisting strength over SD cards and an end of life notification function. The microP2 reader allows you to transfer video files from Panasonic&#39;s microP2 data cards to a computer using a USB 3.0 or USB 2.0 port. The unit is powered by the USB connection and it features two data card slots.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>The microP2</strong>&nbsp;Drive supports offloading of spanned clips using its two media card slots, and is compliant with UHS-II SD memory card standard, which allows it to read data at up to 2.0 Gb/s. The microP2 Drive will also read data from SDHC/SDXC cards between 4 and 128GB in size, although not all cards work with the microP2 system. The reader is Plug &amp; Play with both Mac and Windows.</p>\r\n', '3012200924135fec473d0667b.jpg', 18000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:24:13', 0, '2020-12-30 09:24:13'),
(426, '', 'Panasonic AJ-P2AD1G microP2 Memory Card Adapter', 11, 93, '', 'เมมโมรี่การ์ด Panasonic', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายอะแดปเตอร์การ์ด Panasonic AJ-P2AD1G microP2 Memory Card Adapter</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Max. Read Speed: 1Gb/s</li>\r\n	<li>Max. Write Speed: 100Mb/s</li>\r\n	<li>CPS Password Protection</li>\r\n	<li>Also Works with Class 10 SDHC/SDXC Cards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The AJ-P2AD1G microP2 Memory Card Adapter</strong>&nbsp;from Panasonic enables you to use microP2 cards in the full-size P2 card slots in camcorders. Since these are the same size as SD memory cards, you can also use many 4-128GB Class 10 SDHC/SDXC cards in this adapter, with interval rec, one-shot rec, loop rec, and one-clip rec disabled (some cards may not be usable). The AJ-P2AD1G features maximum read speeds of 1Gb/s and can write at up to 100Mb/s using the AVC-intra100 recording format (excluding 60p/50p), available when using microP2 cards only. When using SDHC/SDXC cards, you have access to DV, DVCPRO, DVCPRO50, and AVC-Intra50 formats, the last two of which allow for 50Mb/s maximum write speeds. Additionally, the adapter has CPS password protection. It requires a firmware upgrade of current P2 hardware.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Read Speed Maximum: 1.0 Gb/s</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Write Speed Maximum:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>microP2 cards: 100 Mb/s, excluding 60p/50p (AVC-intra100)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.0-128 GB Class 10 SDHC/SDXC cards: 50 Mb/s (DVCPRO50 / AVC-Intra50)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compatibility AG-HPX250, AG-HPX255, AG-HPX600 camcorders, AG-HPD24 deck, and AJ-PCD20, AJ-PCD35, AJ-PCD30, AJ-PCD2 drives, AJ-HPX3100 camcorder, AG-HPX370 camcorder and AG-HPG20 recorder, AJ-HPX2000 camcorder, and AJ-HPM200 and AJ-HPD2500 recorders</p>\r\n', '3012200924595fec476b70177.jpg', 10000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 09:24:59', 0, '2020-12-30 09:24:59')