(529, '', 'กล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic HC-MDH2 AVCHD Shoulder Mount Camcorder', 1, 65, '', 'FULL HD CAMCORDER', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>(สินค้าตกรุ่นแล้ว) จำหน่ายกล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic HC-MDH2 AVCHD Shoulder Mount Camcorder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>คุณสมบัติและจุดเด่นของกล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic HC-MDH2 Video Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>บันทึก Video Full HD</li>\r\n	<li>บันทึกภาพนิ่งความละเอียด 20.4 megapixel (16:9)</li>\r\n	<li>Optical Zoom 21x (28-729.6mm (16:9), 436.2-893mm 4:3) 35mm equiv.)</li>\r\n	<li>รูรับแสง f/1.8-3.5</li>\r\n	<li>ระบบลดการสั่นไหว HYBRID O.I.S.</li>\r\n	<li>SD Card Slot x 2 รองรับ SD/SDHC/SDXC Memory Card</li>\r\n	<li>หน้าเลนส์ขนาด 49 มม.</li>\r\n	<li>microphone : 2ch Stereo, zoom microphone</li>\r\n	<li>หน้าจอขนาด 3 นิ้ว ความละเอียด 460,800 pixel</li>\r\n	<li>Electronic Viewfinder 0.24 นิ้ว</li>\r\n	<li>ขนาด 205 x 217 x 479 มม.</li>\r\n	<li>น้ำหนัก 2270 กรัม ; ไม่รวม Battery และ memory card</li>\r\n	<li>มีช่องต่อหูฟังและไมโครโฟน</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '3012201033145fec576ae481f.jpg', 29900, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:33:14', 0, '2020-12-30 10:33:14'),
(530, '', 'กล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic AJ-PX5000G 2/3\" 2.2MP MOS Image Sensor Full-HD Camcorder', 1, 65, '', 'P2 Camera', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายกล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic AJ-PX5000G 2/3&quot; 2.2MP MOS Image Sensor Full-HD Camcorder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2/3&quot; 2.2MP MOS Image Sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Full-HD Resolution of 1920 x 1080</li>\r\n	<li>Built-In P2, microP2 &amp; SD Card Slots</li>\r\n	<li>NTSC &amp; PAL Compatible Frame Rates</li>\r\n	<li>Flip Out 3.45&quot; LCD Screen</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-Recording &amp; Loop Recording</li>\r\n	<li>AVC-ULTRA Recording/Dual Codec Recording</li>\r\n	<li>Image Control &amp; Camera Tools</li>\r\n	<li>3G-SDI Input/Output &amp;Wireless Slot</li>\r\n	<li>Wired LAN Remote Connector &amp; USB 3 Port</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A High-End ENG Camera Recorder Featuring AVC-ULTRA*1 Codecs,</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>microP2 Card Slots and Network Support for</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Automatic FTP Transmission and On-Air Streaming.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://pro-av.panasonic.net/en/sales_o/p2/aj-px5000g/img/img_network.jpg\" style=\"height:281px; width:699px\" /></p>\r\n', '3012201033425fec578625b6f.jpg', 980000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:33:42', 0, '2020-12-30 10:33:42'),
(531, '', 'กล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic AJ-HPX3100G P2 HD Camcorder', 1, 65, '', 'P2 Camera', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายกล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic AJ-HPX3100G P2 HD Camcorder&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2/3&quot; 2.2MP 3CCDs</li>\r\n	<li>Full Raster 1920 x 1080</li>\r\n	<li>AVC-Intra, DVCPRO HD/DV, DVCPRO50</li>\r\n	<li>1080 24p, 25p, 30p, 50i and 60i</li>\r\n	<li>4:2:2 10-bit Sampling</li>\r\n	<li>24-bit Audio in AVC-Intra 100/50</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless Metadata Input</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced Gamma Settings</li>\r\n	<li>Film-like Shutter Controls</li>\r\n	<li>HD/SD-SDI</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic AJ-HPX3100 Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic&#39;s AJ-HPX3100GJ P2 HD Camcorder</strong>&nbsp;is a compact 2/3&quot; ENG camera capable of recording full-raster 1920 x 1080 video in a variety of formats and frame rates. From AVC-Intra 100 down to standard-definition DV, the AJ-HPX3100GJ lets you capture stunning master-quality footage using 4:2:2 10-bit sampling and up to 24-bit audio. Whether you&#39;re shooting news, documentaries, TV series, commercials, or digital cinema, the camera&#39;s quiver of professional features gives you the control, convenience and portability you need.</p>\r\n', '3012201034065fec579e93e76.jpg', 887000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:34:06', 0, '2020-12-30 10:34:06'),
