(543, '', 'Panasonic AW-RP120 G Remote Camera Controller (ตัวควบคุมกล้องระยะไกล)', 1, 65, '', 'PTZ Camara', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายตัวควบคุมกล้องระยะไกล Remote Camera Controller | AW-RP120 G ที่ใช้ในการควบคุมทิศทางของกล้อง รุ่นที่ใช้ในการควบคุม เช่น Panasonic AW-HE-130 KEJ&nbsp; , Panasonic เป็นต้น</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remote PTZ Camera System Controller with IP and Serial Connectivity<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Key Features</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Full size; precision joystick for smooth control of camera moves</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Preset Groups for easy; rapid scene changes (4 groups of up to 10 cameras)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Separate Speed Shift Dials for Pan-Tilt/Zoom/Focus</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Direct panel controls for R/B Gain/Ped; Master Pedestal; Gain; Detail</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; SD Card Storage for backup and recall of settings</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Tracing Memory for complex camera moves (includes SD card storage with IP cameras)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 10 Camera Direct Panel Selection Buttons</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &bull; 5 cameras via RS422</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &bull; Up to 100 cameras via IP (10 groups of 10)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; SW-Link via IP with HS50 switcher; plus external control of RP120 via serial - for simpler workflow</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '3012201040035fec59035f804.jpg', 189000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:40:03', 0, '2020-12-30 10:40:03'),
(544, '', 'Panasonic Remote Camera Controller AW-RP50', 1, 65, '', 'PTZ Camara', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายรีโมทสำหรับควบคุมกล้อง Panasonic Remote Camera Controller AW-RP50</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Uses IP and Serial Control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Supports up to 5 Panasonic Cameras</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Offers Automatic IP Setup</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Controls Camera Functions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Simple to Connect and Operate</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ergonomically Designed</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Controls up to 100 AW-HE50S/H Cameras</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Panasonic Remote Camera Controller uses serial and IP control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>to support Panasonic pan/tilt heads, integrated, and box cameras.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Simple to set up and operate, the controller offers automatic IP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>setup and can be configured via your PC.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '3012201041375fec5961a07a3.jpg', 75000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:41:37', 0, '2020-12-30 10:41:37'),
(545, '', 'Panasonic AW-HS50E รีโมทสำหรับควบคุมกล้องวงจรปิด', 1, 65, '', 'PTZ Camara', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายPanasonic AW-HS50E รีโมทสำหรับควบคุมกล้องวงจรปิด</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is a half-rack size digital video switcher. In spite of its compact size, it features four SDI inputs, one DVI-D input, two SDI outputs, and one DVI-D output. A MultiViewer Display function lets you split the screen in eight different ways, and a Frame Synchronizer ensures easy, high-quality switching. By combining the AW-HS50 with the AW-HE50S HD Integrated Camera and AW-RP50 Remote Camera Controller, a space-saving, low-cost HD image production system can be configured for business use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD 1080/59.94i,50i,24PsF,23.98PsF,720/59.94p,50p</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SD 480/59.94i, 576/50i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* AV-HS04M1, M2, M3, M4, M5, M6, M7, M7D, and M8 cards do not support 1080/24PsF or 1080/23.98PsF.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Five Inputs/Three Outputs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Five inputs : Four SDI inputs and one DVI-D input come standard.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Three outputs : Two SDI outputs and one DVI-D output come standard.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HD/SD Multi-Format</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AW-HS50 supports a variety of HD/SD formats, including 1080/24PsF, as standard. System frequency is 59.94 Hz/50 Hz/24 Hz switchable. This makes it ideal for digital cinema production and worldwide operation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Frame Synchronizers on All Inputs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A Frame Synchronizer is embedded in all inputs. This enables asynchronous video signals to be switched without glitches.</p>\r\n', '3012201041575fec5975a2c11.jpg', 164000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:41:57', 0, '2020-12-30 10:41:57'),
(546, '', 'Panasonic AW-RM50G Wireless Remote Control รีโมทคอนโทรลไร้สาย', 1, 65, '', 'PTZ Camara', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายรีโมทคอนโทรลไร้สาย Panasonic AW-RM50G Wireless Remote Control&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;ของ Panasonic ที่ได้รับการออกแบบเพื่อให้สามารถใช้งานและควบคุมกล้อง HE50 ได้ถึงห้าชุด ควบคุมการแพนเอียงและซูมด้วยความเร็วสูงและต่ำและสามารถเลือกโฟกัสอัตโนมัติและโหมดม่านตาได้จากระยะไกล การควบคุมอื่น ๆ ได้แก่ การโฟกัสแบบแมนนวลม่านตาและการรับสัญญาณรวมถึงการเขียนโปรแกรมและการเรียกคืนค่าที่ตั้งไว้ล่วงหน้าของกล้อง พารามิเตอร์อื่น ๆ อีกมากมายสามารถปรับได้ผ่านการเข้าถึงเมนูเมนูบนหน้าจอจากระยะไกล</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Quick Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Panasonic AWRM50G (AW-RM50G) Wireless Remote. The AWRM50G handheld wireless infrared remote control provides selection, operation and control of up to five HE50 series cameras. The AWRM50G can control pan, tilt, and zoom at both high and low speeds. The RM50G also enables remote selection of auto focus and iris modes, controls manual focus, iris, and gain, as well as programming and recall of camera presets. Access to on-screen menus is provided for adjustment of many other parameters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/ah/m0/nv.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '3012201042235fec598f48eff.jpg', 5500, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:42:23', 0, '2020-12-30 10:42:23'),
(547, '', 'กล้องวงจรปิด Panasonic AW-HE2E HD Integrated Camera', 1, 65, '', 'PTZ Camara', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายกล้องวงจรปิด Panasonic AW-HE2E HD Integrated Camera Compact remote camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ราคาพิเศษ 32,900 บาท มีบริการติดตั้งให้พร้อมรับออกแบบ โซลูชั่นในการติดตั้งให้ฟรี</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT&nbsp; HILIGHT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 1 / 2.33 type Full-HD MOS (1920 x 1080 pixels)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 850 TV Lines horizontal resolution</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- HDMI Output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- IP control supported, IR remote control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AW-HE2 is a small and very flexible HD Integrated Camera, offering a bright</p>\r\n\r\n<p>and new range of applications. Using in TV Conferences, Animal Observations,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Medical Distance Diagnosis or Education, to mention just some of the applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AW-HE2 combines a new concept of</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remote Cameras: &ldquo;Affordable + IP + Full HD&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AW-HE2 is&nbsp; Panasonic&rsquo;s Professional Image Creation Technology,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>like the Full HD MOS System, iA zoom with super resolution technology up to supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multi &ndash; format (1080p). Including Professional Features like Tally, Presets, integrated</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stereo microphone or &ldquo;Self P in P&rdquo;, providing an easy and simple operation with this</p>\r\n\r\n<p>super compact camera. Major key topic and aspect will be the IP Network capability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Easy setup and System Expandability, controlling of up to 100 cameras and IP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Monitoring shows the strength of this Camera.</p>\r\n', '3012201042495fec59a926990.jpg', 32900, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:42:49', 0, '2020-12-30 10:42:49'),
(548, '', 'กล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic HC-MDH3 AVCHD Shoulder Mount Camcorder', 1, 65, '', 'FULL HD CAMCORDER', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายกล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic HC-MDH3 AVCHD Shoulder Mount Camcorder with LCD Touchscreen &amp; LED Light</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HC-MDH3</strong>&nbsp;เป็นกล้องวีดีโอรุ่นใหม่ล่าสุดจากทางค่าย Panasonic ที่กำลังจะเข้ามาขายในประเทศไทยเร็ว ๆ นี้ ราคาต่างประเทศจะอยู่ที่&nbsp; $1,399.99 ดอลล่าห์ ส่วนราคาเมื่อเข้ามาถึงประเทศไทยทางเราจะแจ้งให้ทราบโดยเร็วครับ คาดการณ์ว่าราคาจะอยู่ที่ ราว ๆ&nbsp; 48,000 บาทโดยประมาณ&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic HC-MDH3 AVCHD Shoulder Mount Camcorder</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Panasonic HC-MDH3</strong>&nbsp;กล้องวีดีโอรุ่นใหม่ล่าสุดจากทางค่าย พานาโซนิค เป็นกล้องวีดีโอชนิดแบกบ่าที่พัฒนามาจากรุ่นก่อนหน้านี้คือ HC-MDH2 ครับ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ซึ่งกล้องวีดีโอ HC-MDH3 นี้มีการพัฒนาในหลายด้าน ไม่ว่าจะเป็น เซ็นเซอร์รับภาพ ,ระบบ Picture Tone ,ไฟหัวกล้อง, การบันทึก Relay recording -Hot swap เป็นต้น<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/s8/w7/3t.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '3012201043155fec59c3adb9c.jpg', 39900, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:43:15', 0, '2020-12-30 10:43:15'),
(549, '', 'กล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic AG-CX350 4K 1\" MOS Sensor Camcorder', 1, 65, '', '4K Camera', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp;กล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic AG-CX350 4K 1&quot; MOS Sensor Camcorder</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>กล้องวีดีโอรุ่นใหม่จากค่าย PANASONIC รุ่น AG-CX350 รองรับ NDI</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Highlights</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1&quot; MOS Sensor</li>\r\n	<li>20x Optical, 32x Intelligent Zoom</li>\r\n	<li>UHD 4K, 1080p, Variable Frame Rate</li>\r\n	<li>2 x Media Card Slot, HLG Recording</li>\r\n	<li>3.2&quot; LCD Screen, OLED Viewfinder</li>\r\n	<li>Individual Zoom, Focus, Iris Rings</li>\r\n	<li>Front-Mounted Mic with Front Audio Level</li>\r\n	<li>TC In/Out, 3G-SDI, HDMI Out</li>\r\n	<li>USB 3.0, USB 2.0 Host, LAN Port</li>\r\n	<li>Optional Wireless File Transmission</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '3012201044065fec59f632524.jpg', 129000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:44:06', 0, '2020-12-30 10:44:06'),
(550, '', 'AW-HE42 Full-HD Professional PTZ Camera with 3G-SDI', 1, 65, '', 'PTZ Camara', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>PRODUCT DETAILS<br />\r\nOutstanding video output in full HD. Take advantage of 3G-SDI and IP outputs to get you a reliable live video production workflow. An ideal addition for your PRO PTZ arsenal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AW-HE42 Full-HD Professional PTZ Camera with 3G-SDI</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT DETAILS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Outstanding video output in full HD. Take advantage of 3G-SDI and IP outputs to get you a reliable live video production workflow. An ideal addition for your PRO PTZ arsenal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1/2.3&quot; MOS Sensor with 20x Optical Zoom (extendable by iA zoom)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Excellent HD video via 3G-SDI, HDMI, USB &amp; LAN</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High Dynamic Range function (HDR), suitable for backlit condition</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A Single Cable Solution for Remote Video and Audio Capture (NDI|HX option available)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supports PoE+ (Power over Ethernet+) for lower installation costs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A PTZ Camera for When Quality Matters</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AW-HE42 camera is designed to produce great results in a variety of applications that require high-quality video and precise control&mdash;such as conference video, event capture, staging, distance learning and houses-of-worship. Thanks to their precision 20X optical zoom lenses, wide field of view, smooth PTZ functions and exceptional image quality, HE42 cameras are ideal for demanding remote production and IMAG use. With IP-Preview transmission and control, and support for PoE+ (which allows power to be supplied via a LAN cable), the HE42 also offers the flexibility needed for easy installation and management.</p>\r\n', '3012201044245fec5a0817951.png', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:44:24', 0, '2020-12-30 10:44:24'),
(551, '', 'Panasonic AW-UE150 PTZ Camera 4k 60p/50p 12G-SDI Supported', 1, 65, '', 'PTZ Camara', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>KEY FEATURES<br />\r\nFirst UHD/4K 59.94p Integrated PTZ Camera<br />\r\n75.1&deg; horizontal viewing angle (widest in its class)<br />\r\nVarious 4K interfaces (12G-SDI, HDMI, Optical Fiber, IP)<br />\r\nOptical 20x Zoom + iZoom<br />\r\n4K/HD Simultaneous Output</p>\r\n', '3012201044455fec5a1d29dab.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:44:45', 0, '2020-12-30 10:44:45'),
(552, '', 'Panasonic AW-RP150 Remote camera control', 1, 65, '', 'PTZ Camara', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Key Features<br />\r\nLarge touchscreen for easy usability<br />\r\nNew joystick for one-handed operation<br />\r\nSimplified PTZ camera presets and tracing memory<br />\r\nIntuitive design elements based on direct feedback from everyday robotic camera operators<br />\r\n3G-SDI Active Through Output, 5 x RS-422, LAN PoE+, 2 x GPIOs</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic AW-RP150 Remote camera control</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the latest remote camera control unit, the AW-RP150 is a perfect complement to Panasonic&#39;s professional PTZ camera systems. Essentially identical to the AW-RP120 and AW-RP50, however, it features significant improvements over these models, such as the new one-hand joystick (for PTZ or focus control) and a large LCD touch screen monitor and menu settings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A toggle lever on the joystick supports the pan/tilt function with precise zoom and focus control for intuitive one-handed operation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The integrated touch display allows quick and easy operation of all major camera functions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Large touch screen for easy operation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>New joystick for one-handed operation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Simplified Preset/Tracing Memory Functions for PTZ Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intuitive design elements based on direct practical experience in robot camera operation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3G-SDI Active Through Output, 5 x RS-422, LAN PoE+, 2 x GPIOs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specifications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (W x H x D) 13-19/32 inches x 7-3/32 inches x 10-1/16 inches</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Footnote ** Specifications are subject to change without notice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Related links to &quot;Panasonic AW-RP150&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Do you have any questions concerning this product?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Further products by Panasonic<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AW-RP150 will be the newest remote camera controller to compliment Panasonic&#39;s comprehensive professional PTZ camera lineup. It has the same great functionality of the AW-RP120 and AW-RP50, and joins the lineup with significant improvements over those models, including a new one-hand operation joystick (controlling PTZ or Focus) and a large touch-panel LCD screen for monitoring and menu setting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A seesaw lever mounted on the joystick manages pan and tilt operations for zoom and focus control and intuitive single-handed operation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The built-in touch display allows for easy and quick operation of all essential camera functions.</p>\r\n', '3012201045085fec5a34b7bfb.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:45:08', 0, '2020-12-30 10:45:08'),
(553, '', 'กล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic AG-AC30 Full HD Camcorder Built-In LED Light', 1, 65, '', 'P2 Camera', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>HD Camcorder with Built-In LED Light<br />\r\n1/3.1&quot; BSI MOS Sensor<br />\r\n1920 x 1080 up to 59,94p<br />\r\n20x Optical Zoom Lens</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>กล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic AG-AC30 Full HD Camcorder with Touch Panel LCD Screen &amp; Built-In LED Light</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>HD Camcorder with Built-In LED Light</li>\r\n	<li>1/3.1&quot; BSI MOS Sensor</li>\r\n	<li>1920 x 1080 up to 59,94p</li>\r\n	<li>20x Optical Zoom Lens</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '3012201045335fec5a4da9080.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:45:33', 0, '2020-12-30 10:45:33'),
(554, '', 'กล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic AW-UE4 Wide Angle 4K PTZ Camera with IP Streaming', 1, 65, '', 'PTZ Camara', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>กล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic AW-UE4 Wide Angle 4K PTZ Camera with IP Streaming</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT DETAILS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compact 4K PTZ camera with high-quality video output that excels in live production. The AW-UE4 is ideal for spaces both large and small, with a wide-angle of view perfect for huddle spaces or e-sports production.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ultra wide-angle lens with 111&deg; field of view</li>\r\n	<li>Supports 4K/30p video output</li>\r\n	<li>Video output via 3 interfaces, including HDMI, LAN &amp; USB</li>\r\n	<li>Supports PoE or USB power options</li>\r\n	<li>AW-UE4K (black) / AW-UE4W (white) 4K Professional PTZ Remote Camera</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '3012201046255fec5a8195770.png', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:46:25', 0, '2020-12-30 10:46:25'),
(555, '', 'Panasonic AG-CX10 4K Professional Camera Camcorder', 1, 65, '', '4K Camera', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Panasonic AG-CX10 4K Professional Camera Camcorder</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nกล้องวีดีโอ รุ่นใหม่ล่าสุดจากทางค่าย PANASONIC ที่สามารถถ่าย 4k ได้ถึง 60fps<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Up to UHD 4K60 Video, 3G-SDI, HDMI Out</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NDI/HX for Streaming and IP Control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1/2.5&quot; 8.29M MOS Sensor, Venus Engine</p>\r\n\r\n<p>24x Optical Zoom, 48x Digital iZoom<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Smallest, Lightest 4K 60p Camcorder</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The industry&#39;s smallest, and lightest* 4K 60p director&#39;s camera capable of being carried anywhere for instant, precise shooting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* For a camcorder with an integrated lens capable of 4K 60p recording (as of January 6th, 2020. Panasonic research).</p>\r\n', '3012201046465fec5a9697119.jpg', 85000, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:46:46', 0, '2020-12-30 10:46:46'),
(556, '', 'Panasonic HC-X2000 UHD 4K 3G-SDI/HDMI Professional Camcorder', 1, 65, '', '4K Camera', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายกล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic HC-X2000 UHD 4K 3G-SDI/HDMI Professional Camcorder with 24x Zoom</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Up to UHD 4K60 Video, 3G-SDI &amp; HDMI Out</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1/2.5&quot; 8.29M MOS Sensor, Venus Engine</p>\r\n\r\n<p>24x Optical Zoom, 48x Digital iZoom</p>\r\n\r\n<p>120 fps Slow Motion, Live RTP Streaming<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Industry&#39;s Smallest and Lightest 4K/60p Camcorder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Professional shooting everywhere: HC-X2000 packs advanced functions in a well-balanced body to excel both in functionality and mobility. A new ultrathin fan disperses the heat to allow the construction of the industry&#39;s smallest and lightest 4K/60p-camcorder and a very low power consumption.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Industry\'s Smallest and Lightest 4K/60p Camcorder\" src=\"https://www.panasonic.com/uk/pim-panels/feature-section/20/c4/20c422e4540c0c6e54984f07d06a93889c4e7414/_jcr_content/content/globalfeatureslide/image1component/image.img.png/1577104802214.png\" style=\"height:451px; width:527px\" /></p>\r\n', '3012201047095fec5aadf1d33.jpg', 68990, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:47:09', 0, '2020-12-30 10:47:09'),
(557, '', 'Panasonic HC-X1500 4k Professional Camcorder', 1, 65, '', '4K Camera', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายกล้องวีดีโอ Panasonic HC-X1500 4k Professional Camcorder</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Record up to UHD 4K60 Video, HDMI Out</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1/2.5&quot; 8.29M MOS Sensor, Venus Engine</p>\r\n\r\n<p>24x Optical Zoom, 48x Digital iZoom</p>\r\n\r\n<p>120 fps Slow Motion, Live RTP Streaming</p>\r\n', '3012201047315fec5ac35bddd.jpg', 56500, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:47:31', 0, '2020-12-30 10:47:31'),
(558, '', 'Zhiyun Smooth Q2 ไม้กันสั่นสำหรับมือถือ Smart Phone', 24, 115, '', 'ZHIYUN GIMBAL', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Zhiyun Smooth Q2 ไม้กันสั่นสำหรับมือถือ Smart Phone</strong><br />\r\nออกแบบมาให้สำหรับสาย Mobile</p>\r\n\r\n<p>แบตเตอรี่ใช้งานได้สูงสุด 16 ชั่วโมง&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>สามารถที่จะถ่ายวิดีโอแบบ Sport ได้</p>\r\n\r\n<p>เหมาะกับคนที่ถ่ายวิดีโอด้วยมือเดียว</p>\r\n\r\n<p>สามารถทำงานร่วมกับสมาร์ทโฟนทั้ง iOS และ Android&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>เหมาะกับคนที่เน้นถ่ายด้วยมือถือ Smart Phone</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Truly Pocket-Size Smartphone Gimbal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ZHIYUN has come a long way in exploring the ultimate compact form factor without any compromise in functionality. We turned our eye of precision and dedication into every detail, to deliver a beauty of pure simplicity to filmmakers of all levels. Introducing SMOOTH-Q2, the engaging gimbal ready to work without any fuss, the ultimate smartphone gimbal redefining the concept of compactness.</p>\r\n', '3012201049115fec5b276e7cc.jpg', 4300, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:49:11', 0, '2020-12-30 10:49:11'),
(559, '', 'Zhiyun Crane-M2 สำหรับกล้อง Mirrorless , Compact และ Smartphone', 24, 115, '', 'ZHIYUN GIMBAL', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Zhiyun Crane-M2 สำหรับกล้อง Mirrorless , Compact และ Smartphone</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/37/ex/zw.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '3012201049345fec5b3e54877.jpg', 8500, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:49:34', 0, '2020-12-30 10:49:34'),
(560, '', 'ZHIYUN CRANE 2 DSLR and Mirrorless Camera Stabilizer Gimbal', 24, 115, '', 'ZHIYUN GIMBAL', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย ZHIYUN CRANE 2 DSLR and Mirrorless Camera Stabilizer Gimbal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/7s/y7/vk.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Both Digital &amp; Mechanical Follow Focus</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Integrated with an unprecedented follow focus wheel and attached Servo Follow Focus, Crane 2 allows &plusmn;0.02&deg; real time follow focus for brands like Canon, Sony, Panasonic and Nikon etc. You can always keep your subject in focus while moving, setting free your camera for more dedicated tasks and achieving dolly zoom for lots of cameras.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Crane 2 Package Upgrade, Servo Follow Focus Included, From May 10, 2018</p>\r\n', '3012201050145fec5b66234cd.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:50:14', 0, '2020-12-30 10:50:14'),
(561, '', 'ZHIYUN SMOOTH X กิมบอลรุ่นใหม่ล่าสุดสำหรับมือถือ', 24, 115, '', 'ZHIYUN GIMBAL', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย ZHIYUN SMOOTH X กิมบอลรุ่นใหม่ล่าสุดสำหรับมือถือ</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/nk/41/qq.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Explore your Xtra Life</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The rotatable structure in palm size that allows you to toss in a backpack conveniently, an extendable grip made for exploring bigger vision, and a handy App - ZY Cami, for making videos rock everybody! Meet Smooth X and explore your EXTRA life!</p>\r\n', '3012201050355fec5b7b9bd27.jpg', 1990, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:50:35', 0, '2020-12-30 10:50:35'),
(562, '', 'ZHIYUN CRANE 3S GIMBAL FOR CINEMA CAMERA รองรับน้ำหนัก 6.5 กิโลกรัม', 24, 115, '', 'ZHIYUN GIMBAL', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย ZHIYUN CRANE 3S GIMBAL FOR CINEMA CAMERA รองรับน้ำหนัก 6.5 กิโลกรัม</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CRANE 3S Mission Delivered</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>From intense chasing shoot to studio filming, different types of shooting environment require both high capacity and flexibility of shooting equipment. Bearing filmmakers in mind, ZHIYUN felt the Crane series can be even better to adapt to strict and unpredictable filming environment. Now introducing the new CRANE 3S, the legendary gimbal built on a heritage of innovation with magnificent motors and brand new modular design, which aims for wider application and intuitive control.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reengineered for More Ambitious Camera Setups</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is not simply an upgrade but reconstruction. CRANE 3S is constructed with brand new SUPER motors which allow for Max. 6.5kg payload for a wide range of camera setups.<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/ts/y7/47.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '3012201050595fec5b9304fbd.jpg', 25899, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:50:59', 0, '2020-12-30 10:50:59'),
(563, '', 'ZHIYUN SMOOOTH 4 FOR MOBILE FILMMAKERS', 24, 115, '', 'ZHIYUN GIMBAL', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย ZHIYUN SMOOOTH 4 FOR MOBILE FILMMAKERS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/3u/ir/lp.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Born for Mobile Filmmakers</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zhiyun Smooth 4 turns your mobile phone into a professional filmmaking camera, helping you create stable and smooth footage with just your phone. The design of integrated control panel can reduce the need to touch the screen, and help users control both the stabilizer and mobile camera directly with hot-key buttons. Get one now to create your own Hollywood movies with just phones!</p>\r\n', '3012201051395fec5bbbef20e.jpg', 3400, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:51:39', 0, '2020-12-30 10:51:39'),
(564, '', 'ZHIYUN WEEBILL-S handles mainstream mirrorless and DSLR camera', 24, 115, '', 'ZHIYUN GIMBAL', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย ZHIYUN WEEBILL-S handles mainstream mirrorless and DSLR camera</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tiny Giant&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>WEEBILL-S easily handles mainstream mirrorless and DSLR camera &amp; lens combos. Thanks to its neat lightweight body and a unique Sling mode, WEEBILL-S brings an effortless shooting experience like never before. Featuring an upgraded algorithm and stronger motors, an intelligent ViaTouch 2.0 system as well as an ultra-low latency HD image transmission module, WEEBILL-S pushes the limit of filmmaking even further. Unleash boundless possibilities with WEEBILL-S!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Supreme Power, Superior Compatibility</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>WEEBILL-S comes with new motor units and an upgraded high-precision algorithm. Combos like Sony A7Ⅲ+FE 24-70mm F2.8 and Canon 5D4+EF 24-70mm F2.8 can be perfectly balanced and stabilized on WEEBILL-S for smooth cinematic shots under different scenarios. Simply mount your camera onto WEEBILL-S and WEEBILL-S can auto tune its power to best adapt to your devices. Be limitless with WEEBILL-S and enjoy creation full heartedly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsive and Flexible than EVER</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The upgraded 8th Instune algorithm provides high responsiveness and eliminates jittery in fast movement in any environment. Not only that, you can quickly adjust the speed and various parameters of each axis directly through the dial on the handle itself, giving you responsive and flexible control than ever!<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/6c/1c/by.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '3012201052015fec5bd19e98b.jpg', 12900, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:52:01', 0, '2020-12-30 10:52:01'),
(565, '', 'ZHIYUN WEEBILL LAB Wireless Image Transmission', 24, 115, '', 'ZHIYUN GIMBAL', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย ZHIYUN WEEBILL LAB Wireless Image Transmission</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/pq/86/o0.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '3012201052245fec5be89ffe4.jpg', 10600, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:52:24', 0, '2020-12-30 10:52:24'),
(566, '', 'ZHIYUN CRANE 3 LAB REDEFINE STABILIZER', 24, 115, '', 'ZHIYUN GIMBAL', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย ZHIYUN CRANE 3 LAB REDEFINE STABILIZER&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/2d/1k/h9.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '3012201052425fec5bfa47302.jpg', 31500, 0, 0, '2020-12-30 10:52:42', 0, '2020-12-30 10:52:42');
