(593, '', 'Kiloview N30 12G-SDI/Full NDI Encoder/Decoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview N30 12G-SDI/Full NDI Encoder/Decoder&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kiloview N30 for NDI supports up to 12G-SDI video input (Encoder) or 12G-SDI video output (Decoder).&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is small and compact enough to put in your pocket with the overall size of 100*80*28mm. It featured with an 12G-SDI input and 12G-SDI loop for view on the monitor while NDI streaming, or 12G-SDI output while decoding.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A tally system with a big tally light is built-in for indicating which camera is in program or preview. It also has the 3.5mm&nbsp; audio input/output.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kiloivew N30 for 12G-SDI has a wide DC input range from 5V to 18V, so it can be easily powered by USB, power bank or camera battery. It can also be powered over Ethernet (PoE).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A threaded screw camera mount is provided for your mounting on a camera. PTZ control is available by USB to Serial adaptor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>can be easily realized</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>● Rack-mounted design to support install on the camera easily</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● Plug and play, SDI to NDI&reg;, or NDI&reg; to 12G-SDI to screen</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● SDI input/output supported to monitor during NDI streaming</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Highlight</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tally Light</li>\r\n	<li>Wide DC power input range from 5V-18V&nbsp; to make it easy powered by USB, power bank, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm audio Input/output and Intercom supported (Kiloview Software required)</li>\r\n	<li>Threaded screw camera mount</li>\r\n	<li>Optional control cable supported which can control PTZ over Visca / Visca over IP / Pelco etc. (Customize available for other unlisted PTZ protocols)</li>\r\n	<li>Compatible with Kiloview IMS software for device and source management.</li>\r\n	<li>Support resolution up to 12G-SDI when encoding and&nbsp; decoding and compatible with SD / HD / VESA&nbsp; &nbsp;resolution and others.</li>\r\n	<li>YCbCr 4: 2: 2 NDI encoding ensures excellent picture quality, lossless audio encoding ensures high-fidelity sound quality.</li>\r\n	<li>Through accurate clock and intelligent algorithm, ensure video frame synchronization, as well as&nbsp; accurate picture and audio synchronization.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '0401211616035ff33f4300649.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:16:03', 0, '2021-01-04 16:16:03'),
(594, '', 'Kiloview N3 3G-SDI/Full NDI Encoder/Decoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview N3 3G-SDI/NDI Bi-directional Converter</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kiloview N3 for NDI supports up to 3G-SDI video input (Encoder) or 3G-SDI video output (Decoder). A tally system with a big tally light is built-in for indicating which camera is in program or preview. It also has the 3.5mm audio input/output. It is small and compact enough to put in your pocket with the overall size of 100*80*28mm. It featured with an 3G-SDI input and 3G-SDI loop for view on the monitor while NDI streaming, or 3G-SDI output while decoding.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x 3G-SDI input, 1 x 3G-SDI loop-through or decoding output;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1x RJ45 + PoE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Threaded screw camera mount</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tally Light</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.5mm Audio Input/Output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intercom supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PTZ Control via USB/Ethernet</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DC 5V-18V power supply</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compact design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All NewTek NDI enabled encoding or streaming sotware supported;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Newtek NDI, OBS, Xsplit, vMix VidBlaster, Wirecast MimoLive, Streamstar</p>\r\n', '0401211616285ff33f5cf374a.png', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:16:28', 0, '2021-01-04 16:16:28'),
(595, '', 'Kiloview N40 4Kp60 HDMI/NDI Bi-directional Converter', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview N4 4Kp60 HDMI/NDI Bi-directional Converter</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kiloview N4 for NDI supports up to 4Kp60 video input (Encoder) or 4Kp60 video output (Decoder). This converter is small and compact enough to put in your pocket with the overall size of 100*80*24mm. It features an HDMI2.0 input and HDMI2.0 loop through for view on the monitor while NDI streaming, or HDMI 2.0 output while decoding. A tally system with a big tally light is built-in for indicating which camera is in program or preview. It also has the 3.5mm audio input/output which supports intercom</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI input, 1 x HDMI loop-through or decoding output;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1x RJ45 + PoE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Threaded screw camera mount</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tally Light</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.5mm Audio Input/Output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intercom supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PTZ Control via USB/Ethernet</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DC 5V-18V power supply</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compact design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All NewTek NDI enabled encoding or streaming sotware supported;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Newtek NDI, OBS, Xsplit, vMix VidBlaster, Wirecast MimoLive, Streamstar</p>\r\n', '0401211616505ff33f72ecdf8.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:16:50', 0, '2021-01-04 16:16:50'),
(596, '', 'Kiloview N4 1080p60 HDMI/NDI Bi-directional Converter', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview N4 1080p60 HDMI/NDI Bi-directional Converter</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kiloview N4 for NDI supports up to 1080p60 video input (Encoder) or 1080p60 video output (Decoder). This converter is small and compact enough to put in your pocket with the overall size of 100*80*24mm. It features an HDMI2.0 input and HDMI2.0 loop through for view on the monitor while NDI streaming, or HDMI 2.0 output while decoding. A tally system with a big tally light is built-in for indicating which camera is in program or preview. It also has the 3.5mm audio input/output which supports intercom</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x HDMI input, 1 x HDMI loop-through or decoding output;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1x RJ45 + PoE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Threaded screw camera mount</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tally Light</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.5mm Audio Input/Output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intercom supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PTZ Control via USB/Ethernet</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DC 5V-18V power supply</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compact design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All NewTek NDI enabled encoding or streaming sotware supported;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Newtek NDI, OBS, Xsplit, vMix VidBlaster, Wirecast MimoLive, Streamstar</p>\r\n', '0401211617215ff33f914065b.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:17:21', 0, '2021-01-04 16:17:21'),
(597, '', 'Kiloview N1 NDI – Wireless SDI to NDI Video Encoder with battery', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview N1 NDI &ndash; Wireless SDI to NDI Video Encoder with battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>NDI has become a more convenient and reliable video transmission technology which is widely applied in the video production process. The Kiloview N1 video encoder can directly convert a SDI video signal into NDI, and realize ultra-low-latency transmission through WIFI (or wired Ethernet) to various other NDI compatible devices or software like vMix on the same network.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Authorized by NewTek, compatible with other NDI hardware and software products</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portable design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in 5G enhanced WIFI module</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual stream output (also through RTMP) and Local recording</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in battery (3-4 hours fully charged)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipped with hot shoe</p>\r\n', '0401211617395ff33fa318141.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:17:39', 0, '2021-01-04 16:17:39'),
(598, '', 'Kiloview N2 NDI – Wireless HDMI to NDI Video Encoder with battery', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview N2 NDI &ndash; Wireless HDMI to NDI Video Encoder with battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>NDI has become a more convenient and reliable video transmission technology which is widely applied in the video production process. The Kiloview N2 video encoder can directly convert a HDMI video signal into NDI, and realize ultra-low-latency transmission through WIFI (or wired Ethernet) to various other NDI compatible devices or software like vMix on the same network.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Authorized by NewTek, compatible with other NDI hardware and software products</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portable design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in 5G enhanced WIFI module</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual stream output (also through RTMP) and Local recording</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in battery (3-4 hours fully charged)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipped with hot shoe</p>\r\n', '0401211620355ff34053f3c40.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:20:35', 0, '2021-01-04 16:20:35'),
(599, '', 'Kiloview E1 NDI HX 3G-SDI H.264 SRT Video Encoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview E1 NDI HX 3G-SDI H.264 SRT Video Encoder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>TheKiloview E1 NDI|HX HD/3G-SDI H.264 Video Encoder delivers any digital video source to the network in full HD, with high-efficiency NDI&reg; output via NDI|HX and native support for resolutions up to 1080p. It supports RTP/RTSP/RTMP/RTMPS/HLS/TS streaming media protocols for live broadcast on Facebook, YouTube, Ustream, Twitch, Wowza etc</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H.264 video encoding</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SRT</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NDI|HX output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD Live streaming</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual streams output supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low bandwith (1Mbps@720p, 1.5Mbps@1080p)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low latency( &le; 67)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SDI Loop-through for live monitoring</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low power consumption (&lt;4w)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Manage with Android app or via web app</p>\r\n', '0401211620575ff340690b2fa.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:20:57', 0, '2021-01-04 16:20:57'),
(600, '', 'Kiloview E2 NDI HX HDMI H.264 SRT Video Encoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview E2 NDI HX HDMI H.264 SRT Video Encoder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Kiloview E2 NDI|HX HDMI H.264 Video Encoder delivers any digital video source to the network in full HD, with high-efficiency NDI&reg; output via NDI|HX and native support for resolutions up to 1080p. It supports RTP/RTSP/RTMP/RTMPS/HLS/TS streaming media protocols for live broadcast on Facebook, YouTube, Ustream, Twitch, Wowza etc</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H.264 video encoding</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SRT</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NDI|HX output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD Live streaming</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual streams output supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low bandwith (1Mbps@720p, 1.5Mbps@1080p)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low latency( &le; 67)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI Loop-through for live monitoring</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low power consumption (&lt;4w)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Manage with Android app or via web app</p>\r\n', '0401211621175ff3407dc5f27.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:21:17', 0, '2021-01-04 16:21:17'),
(601, '', 'Kiloview P1 – Wireless 4G-LTE SDI H.264 SRT Encoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview P1 &ndash; Wireless 4G-LTE SDI H.264 SRT Encoder with Battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Kiloview P1 is the ideal solution for broadcasting events, seminars, conferences, church services etc. in environments with poor bandwidth connection. The P1 brings you flexibility offering different ways to built up a reliable network connection through Wifi, Ethernet, 4G-LTE simcards or by bonding these together to realize high quality streaming. Furthermore the built battery that last up to 3 hours and gives you the freedom to place the P1 with the hotshoe mount to any movable camera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H.264 video encoding</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SRT support</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080p60</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4G-LTE bonding*</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wifi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in lithium battery (up to 3 hours)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in cooling fan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Removable hot shoe bracket</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low bandwidth transmission</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Live Broadcasting to YouTube, Facebook Live, Vimeo, DaCast etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Standard 1 simcard supported, bonding of 2 simcards and more with Omnistream bonding service.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '0401211621425ff34096ef0e0.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:21:42', 0, '2021-01-04 16:21:42'),
(602, '', 'Kiloview P2 – Wireless 4G-LTE HDMI H.264 Encoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview P2 &ndash; Wireless 4G-LTE SDI H.264 Encoder with Battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Kiloview P2 is the ideal solution for broadcasting events, seminars, conferences, church services etc. in environments with poor bandwidth connection. The P2 brings you flexibility offering different ways to built up a reliable network connection through Wifi, Ethernet, 4G-LTE simcards or by bonding these together to realize high quality streaming. Furthermore the built battery that last up to 3 hours and gives you the freedom to place the P2 with the hotshoe mount to any movable camera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H.264 video encoding</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1080p60</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4G-LTE bonding*</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wifi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in lithium battery (up to 3 hours)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in cooling fan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Removable hot shoe bracket</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low bandwidth transmission</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Live Broadcasting to YouTube, Facebook Live, Vimeo, DaCast etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Standard 1 simcard supported, bonding of 2 simcards and more with Omnistream bonding service.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '0401211622065ff340ae2ae43.png', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:22:06', 0, '2021-01-04 16:22:06'),
(603, '', 'Kiloview G1 HD/3G-SDI H.264 4G/Wifi Video Encoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview G1 HD/3G-SDI H.264 4G/Wifi Video Encoder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Kiloview wireless video encoder can convert the full 1080P HD/3G-SDI video source to IP signal without loss and push to internet streaming broadcast platforms through Ethernet. It has a built-in Wifi or 4g network to realize video transmission, which makes live broadcasting available at anytime and anywhere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H.264 video encoding</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD Live streaming</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Support wifi/4g/Ethernet</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual streams output supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low bandwith (1Mbps@720p, 1.5Mbps@1080p)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low latency( &le; 67</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SDI Loop-through for live monitoring</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low power consumption (&lt;4w)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Manage with Android app or via web app</p>\r\n', '0401211622585ff340e23c8d7.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:22:58', 0, '2021-01-04 16:22:58'),
(604, '', 'Kiloview G2 HDMI H.264 4G/Wifi Video Encoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview G2 HDMI H.264 4G/Wifi Video Encoder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Kiloview wireless video encoder can convert the full 1080P HDMI video source to IP signal without loss and push to internet streaming broadcast platforms through Ethernet. It has a built-in Wifi or 4g network to realize video transmission, which makes live broadcasting available at anytime and anywhere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H.264 video encoding</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full HD Live streaming</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Support wifi/4g/Ethernet</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual streams output supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low bandwith (1Mbps@720p, 1.5Mbps@1080p)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low latency( &le; 67</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI Loop-through for live monitoring</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Low power consumption (&lt;4w)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Manage with Android app or via web app</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '0401211623255ff340fd6ba8b.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:23:25', 0, '2021-01-04 16:23:25'),
(605, '', 'KILOVIEW M2 H.264 HDMI VGA IP RTSP/RTMP/HLS VIDEO ENCORDER', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย KILOVIEW M2 H.264 HDMI VGA IP RTSP/RTMP/HLS VIDEO ENCORDER</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>KILOVIEW&reg; M2 professional HD/3G-HDMI วิดีโอ H.264 encoder. ขนาดเล็กและ ultra - low เชื้อเพลิง! M2 เข้ากันได้กับ HDMI 1.3/HDCP 1.3 สนับสนุนวิดีโออินพุตและการเข้ารหัสสูงสุด 1080p60; อินเทอร์เฟซ VGA สนับสนุนวิดีโอความละเอียดที่สอดคล้องกับมาตรฐาน VESA VGA ถึง WUXGA, สูงสุดถึง 1920x1200 @ 60 เฮิร์ต.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>M2 รองรับ unbind จากสัญญาณ HDMI, นอกจากนี้ยังมีอินพุตเสียง Analog Line - in สำหรับ AAC (MPEG4-Audio) สเตอริโอการเข้ารหัสเสียงหรือ G.711 การเข้ารหัสเสียง.</p>\r\n', '0401211625055ff3416101240.png', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:25:05', 0, '2021-01-04 16:25:05');
