(606, '', 'Kiloview D300 IP/SRT to 4K UHD HDMI/SDI Video Decoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview D300 IP/SRT to 4K UHD HDMI/SDI Video Decoder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The D300-4K UHD Video decoder is a professional hardware decoding device that can decode multiple video streams without relying on a computer It outputs SDI signal and HDMI signal video, supports 4K UHD resolution, and supports multi-channels video stream split screen to the display wall and dynamic switching.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you need to decode and split the multi-channel 4K UHD network video stream, even if you need to switch the multi-channel network stream to the wall, you only need to connect the D300 4K UHD decoder to</p>\r\n\r\n<p>the network and the large screen interface. Various web videos can be presented in real time on a large screen according to your needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Support H.265, H.264 decoding,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Support 16 channels 1080p30, or 4 channels 4k HD video simultaneous decoding output.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI and SDI dual interface output, support HDMI (up to 3840&times;2160@60Hz) and SDI (up to 1920&times;1080@60Hz) same or different content output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The input supports mainstream network video protocols such as RTMP/SRT/HLS/TS over UDP/RTP/RTSP, and supports protocols such as SIP and VOCP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Less than 200ms decoding delay</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Support HDMI/SDI embedded audio output and analog audio output</p>\r\n', '0401211625285ff341784152d.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:25:28', 0, '2021-01-04 16:25:28'),
(607, '', 'Kiloview DC230 SRT & IP to SDI/HDMI/DVI Video Decoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview DC230 SRT &amp; IP to SDI/HDMI/DVI Video Decoder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Kiloview KV-DC230 is a network (IP) HD video decoder with high performance. It is able to decode IP-Cameras from network and any streaming device or encoders based on RTSP, RTP unicast or multicast. The KV-DC230 supports up to 3G-SDI and HDMI/VGA/DVI video and audio outputs through self-adaptive decoding. Supported SDI signals are SD-SDI(270M), HD-SDI (1.485G) standard and 3G-SDI (2.97G) at 720p, 1080i and 1080p (maximum 60Hz); HDMI output supporting up to 1080p60Hz HD video signal; VGA supporting maximum UXGA output.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The KV-DC230 can decode simultaneously 2 channels HD video up to 1080p60, with functions of self-adaptive decoding and smart control on network delay. Under typical network environment, it can control decoding delay lower or equal to 200ms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H.264 video decoding</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Up to 2CH 1080p60 (H.264) video decoding simultaneously</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supports SRT/ RTMP/ HLS/ TS over UDP, RTSP / SIP/ VOCP and IP cameras.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Outputs of SDI/ HDMI can be up to 1080p60, 1080p/1080i 59.9</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multi streams decoding</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7*24 Working mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Image scaling/ frame rate conversion</p>\r\n', '0401211625545ff3419254c22.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:25:54', 0, '2021-01-04 16:25:54'),
(608, '', 'Kiloview DC220 IP Network Video Decoder', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview DC220 RTSP/HLS to SDI/HDMI/DVI IP Network Video Decoder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>About Kiloview DC220</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kiloview DC220 HD video decoder is a professional hardware decoding device. It is capable of independently decoding incoming streams from IP Camera, stream media server or any encoder (based on RTSP, RTMP, RTP, unicast and multicast). The output interface can be SDI and DVI-I (HDMI/VGA). This device decodes IP video from encoders via Ethernet. DC220 video decoder has approved by CE, FCC, ISO, HDMI, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; H.264 video decoding</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; High Compatibility</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 7x24 Working mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; SDK provided</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Dual output SDI &amp; DVI (HDMI/ VGA compatible)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Support 1080p</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Strong decoding ability, strong error-resistance, low latency</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; With Kiloview unique image enhancement and fault-tolerant technology, it has powerful error resistance for video encoded at low bitrate with up to 10% packet loss, excellent image output can be obtained</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Decoding latency can be less than 200 ms under a typical network environment with Kiloview intelligent latency control technology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Decoding of H.264 encoded video and AAC/G.711 encoded audio at bitrate of 40Mbps supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High compatibility, SDI + DVI dual output, wide application</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; It supports RTMP/ SRT/ HLS/ TS over UDP, RTSP protocols as well as SIP/ VOCP, it can also be connected with different kinds of encoding device, streaming media servers and IP cameras</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; With dual output SDI &amp; DVI ( HDMI/ VGA compatible ) and the resolution can be self-defined</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Outputs of SDI/ HDMI can be up to 1080p60 and VGA up to UXGA solution; 1080p/1080i 59.94 is also compatible</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Analog audio and embedded SDI/ HDMI audio can be output simultaneously</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Audio mixing, tally and column loudspeaker indicating design supported</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portable size, low power consumption, multifunctional, 24h continuous operation available</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Power consumption less than 5W</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; With image scaling function, the output video can be scaled as well as frame rate conversion, in order to adapt different output video formats</p>\r\n', '0401211636115ff343fbbe856.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:36:11', 0, '2021-01-04 16:36:11'),
(609, '', 'Kiloview CV180 Broadcast Grade SDI to HDMI/VGA/AV Video Converter', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย Kiloview CV180 Broadcast Grade SDI to HDMI/VGA/AV Video&nbsp; Converter</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kiloview KV-CV180 is a broadcast level multifunctional video converter which can convert SDI to HDMI, VGA and AV(CVBS) with functions of frame conversion, resolution conversion, image scale up/ down, color conditioning, image enhancement and adjustment, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dz.lnwfile.com/_/dz/_raw/d2/z2/y2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Application</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kiloview CV180 video converter is suitable for the applications that need to convert&nbsp; SDI to&nbsp; (HDMI/ VGA/ AV (CVBS)/ independent audio, etc.)&nbsp; such as broadcast, video teaching and training, HD video information release, HD video long-distance transmission, video conferencing, multimedia advertising and video security monitoring etc..</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Main features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>SD/ HD /3G SDI to HDMI/ VGA /AV( CVBS)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High compatibility</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Frame/ resolution conversion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remote control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web configuration management</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7*24h continuous working</p>\r\n', '0401211636335ff3441157f0d.jpg', 0, 0, 0, '2021-01-04 16:36:33', 0, '2021-01-04 16:36:33'),
(610, '', 'Kiloview KV-CV190 HDMI&VGA&AV to SD/HD/3G-SDI Converter', 25, 116, '', 'KILOVIEW (NDI Encoder/Decoder)', '', '<h2>รายละเอียดสินค้า</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่าย KV-CV190 HDMI&amp;VGA&amp;AV to SDI Video Converter</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>KV-CV190 HDMI&amp;VGA&amp;AV to SDI&nbsp; converter is a professional converter which is applied for single HDMI or VGA or AV(CVBS) interface to high definition SDI interface. The KV-CV190 be integrated SDI&#39;s transmitter and HDMI&#39;s receiver, HDMI can be easily convert to SDI, separate and convert the audio then embed to SDI to achieve audio and video transmit simultaneously, or embed the external audio of VGA,AV(CVBS) to SDI to achieve audio and video transmit simultaneously, the user can designated the SDI output format compulsively to adapt to different enviorment.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>KV-CV190 is applied for HDMI system of the subway platform, HDMI system of the train platform, long-distance HD video signal transmit of military maneuver, long-distance HD video signal transmit of security monitoring, long-distance HD video signal transmit of Large-scale performances, also suitable for various HD video applications etc..</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Support HDMI output format:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>480i,576i,480p,576p,720p50/59.94/60,1080p24/25/29.97/30,1080i 50/59.94/60,1080p 50/59.94/60, be compatible up to 1920x1080@60Hz VGA format resolution</p>\r\n\r\n<p>support VGA resolution format up to 1920x1080@60Hz, be compatible to various standard VESA SD resolution and normal no-VESA SD resolution</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SDI support SMPTE 425M(A lever and B lever) output , SMPTE424M, SMPTE292M,SMPTE259M-C</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With dual SDI signal output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Support HDMI DDC function and HDCP digital content protection</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Support all format dissymmetric conversion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Automatically embed SDI audio signal to HDMI signal</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SDI output can