(639, '', 'Sennheiser EW100 G4 HSP Essential Wireless System', 8, 77, '', 'Sennheiser', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย Sennheiser EW100 G4 HSP Essential Wireless System</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ew 100 G4-HSP Essential Wireless Bodypack System with HSP Essential Omnidirectional Neckworn Microphone&nbsp; from Sennheiser is the latest addition to their evolution family of wireless microphones that is fully compatible with all previous series. This kit includes an EM100 G4 UHF diversity rackmount receiver, an SK 100 G4 bodypack transmitter with HSP Essential Omnidirectional Neckworn Microphone, a GA3 rackmount kit, It can be used to capture audio in indoor environments for hands-free speech and interview applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Both transmitter and receiver synchronize channel and frequency at the touch of a button. The bodypack transmitter allows you to charge the (optional) rechargeable battery pack while installed. The receiver&rsquo;s high-contrast LCD display allows for easy operation under dimly-lit conditions and its user-friendly menu makes operation quick and easy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ew 100 G4-HSP Essential Wireless Bodypack System with HSP Essential Omnidirectional Neckworn Microphone is at home in theaters, clubs, town halls, houses of worship, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Robust bodypack transmitter for daily use on stage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Easy and flexible wireless synchronization between transmitter and receiver via infrared.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fast frequency allocation for up to 12 receivers via updated linking functionality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Up to 20 compatible channels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Up to 42 MHz bandwidth with 1680 selectable frequencies, fully tunable in a stable UHF range.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Transmission Range: up to 100 meters / 300&prime;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High RF output power (up to 30 mW) depending on country regulations.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>SK 100 G4 Wireless Bodypack Transmitter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Modulation Wideband FM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Frequency Range A: (516 to 558 MHz)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Transmission Frequencies Maximum 1680 receiving frequencies, adjustable in 25 kHz steps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>20 frequency banks, each with up to 12 factory-preset channels, no intermodulation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 frequency bank with up to 12 programmable channels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Switching Bandwidth Up to 42 MHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nominal/Peak Deviation &plusmn;24 kHz / &plusmn;48 kHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Frequency Stability &le; &plusmn;15 ppm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RF Output Power Maximum 30 mW at 50 Ohms</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pilot Tone Squelch Can be switched off</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compander<br />\r\nSennheiser HDX</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AF Frequency Response<br />\r\nMic: 80 Hz to 18 kHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Line: 25 Hz to 18 kHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Signal to Noise Ratio<br />\r\n&ge; 110 dBA (1 mV, peak deviation)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Total Harmonic Distortion<br />\r\n(THD) &le; 0.9%</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum Input Voltage<br />\r\nMicrophone/Line: 3 V eff</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input Impedance<br />\r\nMicrophone/Line: 40 kOhms, unbalanced / 1 MOhms</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input Capacitance<br />\r\nSwitchable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input Sensitivity Range<br />\r\n60 dB, adjustable in 3 dB steps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Temperature Range<br />\r\n14 to 131&deg;F (-10 to 55&deg;C)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power Supply<br />\r\n2 x AA batteries, 1.5 V or BA 2015 accupack</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nominal Voltage 3 V battery / 2.4 V rechargeable battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Current Consumption At Nominal Voltage: Approximately 180 mA&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With Transmitter Switched Off: &le; 25 &micro;A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating Time Typically 8 hours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions (W x L x H)<br />\r\n3.2 x 2.5 x 0.6&Prime; (82 x 64 x 24 mm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight<br />\r\n5.6 oz (160 g)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>EM 100 G4 Wireless UHF True Diversity Rackmount Receiver</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Receiver</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fr