(696, '', 'CLEAN VIDEO HDS-9106 6 CH HD Video Switcher', 5, 112, '', 'Clean Video', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย CLEAN VIDEO HDS-9106 6 CH HD Video Switcher</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT DETAILS:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>6 CH HD Video Switcher</p>\r\n\r\n<p>15.6 inch screen:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;One-piece design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PIP/POP:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Picture effects</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PGM/PVW:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Multi-screen output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Six channels:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;hidden&quot; interface</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>15.6&quot; HD LCD Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HD 1080p Screen, All Input Sources, Preview,The Screen And</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Main Output Screen Are Included In The Screen For Easy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Monitoring</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>◆ Signal Input:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4-Channel SDI And Two HDMI Inputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>◆ Audio Output:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3.5mm Analog Audio Input And Output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1 Set Of Lotus Seat Audio Input And Output</p>\r\n\r\n<p>◆ PGM Output:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2-Way SDI And 1-Channel HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>◆ Multi-Picture Output:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1 Way HDMI And 1 Way SD<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/ja/l4/rw.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '080221173635602176a36844a.jpg', 29500, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:36:35', 0, '2021-02-08 17:36:35'),
(697, '', 'Saramonic Wireless 4-Channel VHF Lavalier Omnidirectional Microphone System', 8, 78, '', 'ไมค์โครโฟนไวเลส Saramonic', '', '<p><strong>สินค้าตัวนี้ราคารวม VAT แล้ว&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Saramonic SR-WM4C Wireless 4-Channel VHF Lavalier Omnidirectional Microphone System</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HILIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Four switchable channels to keep you free from interference</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Detachable and flexible antenna can be rotated 360&deg;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; accordingly as per sound requirement</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- High-band VHF provides pure sound</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Records audio up to 197&rsquo; away with no obstacle</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Real-time monitoring</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Volume control wheel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- LED indicator light indicates battery life</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Power provided by two AA size alkaline batteries</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Includes a belt-pack transmitter, camera-mountable&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; receiver and an omnidirectional lavalier microphone</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The compact Wireless 4-Channel</strong>&nbsp;VHF Lavalier Omnidirectional Microphone</p>\r\n\r\n<p>System from Saramonic is an audio recording solution which includes a</p>\r\n\r\n<p>camera-mountable receiver, belt-pack transmitter and omnidirectional lavalier</p>\r\n\r\n<p>microphone. The slim and low-profile omnidirectional microphone transmits its</p>\r\n\r\n<p>signal via the transmitter to the receiving unit. Both the receiver and transmitter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>are lightweight and easy to use, offering flexibility without sacrificing high-quality</p>\r\n\r\n<p>audio. This system is ideal for film making, conducting broadcast interviews</p>\r\n\r\n<p>and business presentations, or other applications that require portability.</p>\r\n', '08022117382860217714308c9.jpg', 4100, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:38:28', 0, '2021-02-08 17:38:28'),
(698, '', 'Saramonic Wireless TX9 Set 1 UHF Wireless Microphone Package', 8, 78, '', 'ไมค์โครโฟนไวเลส Saramonic', '', '<p><strong>Saramonic Wireless TX9 Set 1 UHF Wireless Microphone Package</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HILIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- UHF Wireless Microphone Package&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- UwMic9-TX9 + UwMic9-RX9</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 1 x transmitter (TX9)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 1 x receiver (RX9)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 1 x lavalier microphone&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Saramonic TX9</strong>&nbsp;Digital UHF Wireless Bodypack trasnmitter with</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lavaliermicrophone provides stable, interference free audio in portable,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>compact and low cost package. This system is a perfect fit for DSLR</p>\r\n\r\n<p>videography, field recording and interviews, broadcast TV, electronic</p>\r\n\r\n<p>news gathering (ENG), - or anyone who needs mobile, dependable audio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>broadcasting and recording.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The TX9</strong>&nbsp;system includes the TX transmitter bodypack and clip on lavalier</p>\r\n\r\n<p>microphone. Receiving unit sold separately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Reliable, broadcast-quality audio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Wireless UHF bodypack transmitter compatible with RX-9 receiver</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- UHF frequency range: 514MHz - 596MHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 96 selectable channels in 2 groups</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Operating Range: Over 330&#39; (100m) in open areas. 200&#39; (60m)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;with obstacles&nbsp;Easy-to-read LCD displays</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Transmitter :&nbsp;</strong>Bodypack, wireless microphone transmitter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Features a compact, metallic body</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Easy-to-read LCD display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- RF power switch and a PLL synthesizer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- It has a built-in antenna, a muting function and power lock function.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; The channel of the TX9 is synced up with the receiver via an infrared</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; connection.&nbsp;The RF power output can be switched among high,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; middle and low.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product: Saramonic TX9 Bodypack Digital UHF Wireless Transmitter</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Manufacturer: Saramonic&nbsp;</strong><strong>Model: UWMIC9 - TX9&nbsp;</strong><strong>SKU: UWMIC9 - TX9</strong></p>\r\n', '08022117390060217734513a7.jpg', 10900, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:39:00', 0, '2021-02-08 17:39:00'),
(699, '', 'Saramonic Wireless TX9 Set 2 UHF Wireless Microphone Package', 8, 78, '', 'ไมค์โครโฟนไวเลส Saramonic', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย Saramonic UwMic9 Set 2 ราคา 16,000.-</strong><br />\r\n<strong>The Saramonic RX9+TX9 UHF Wireless Lavalier Microphone</strong>&nbsp;System provides stable, interference free audio in portable, compact and low cost package. This system is a perfect fit for DSLR videography, field recording and interviews, broadcast TV, ENG, providing dependable audio broadcasting and recording.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The system includes a camera-mountable, wireless receiver, wireless body-pack transmitter and clip-on lavalier mic.</p>\r\n', '08022117393660217758550a1.jpg', 16000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:39:36', 0, '2021-02-08 17:39:36'),
(700, '', 'Saramonic UwMic9-TX9 Digital UHF Wireless Bodypack trasnmitter', 8, 78, '', 'ไมค์โครโฟนไวเลส Saramonic', '', '<p><strong>Saramonic UwMic9-TX9 Digital UHF Wireless Bodypack trasnmitter&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HILIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-1 x transmitter (TX9)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-1 x lavalier microphone&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Saramonic TX9 Digital UHF Wireless Bodypack</strong>&nbsp;trasnmitter with</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lavalier&nbsp;microphone provides stable, interference free audio in portable,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>compact and&nbsp;low cost package. This system is a perfect fit for DSLR videography,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>field&nbsp;recording and interviews, broadcast TV, electronic news gathering (ENG),</p>\r\n\r\n<p>or anyone who needs mobile, dependable audio broadcasting and recording.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The TX9</strong>&nbsp;system includes the TX transmitter bodypack and clip on lavalier</p>\r\n\r\n<p>microphone. Receiving unit sold separately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Reliable, broadcast-quality audio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Wireless UHF bodypack transmitter compatible with RX-9 receiver</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- UHF frequency range: 514MHz - 596MHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 96 selectable channels in 2 groups</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Operating Range: Over 330&#39; (100m) in open areas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; 200&#39; (60m) with obstacles&nbsp;Easy-to-read LCD displays</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Transmitter :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Bodypack, wireless microphone transmitter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Features a compact, metallic body</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Easy-to-read LCD display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- RF power switch and a PLL synthesizer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It has a built-in antenna, a muting function and power lock function.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The channel of the TX9 is synced up with the receiver via an infrared connection.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The RF power output can be switched among high, middle and low.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product: Saramonic TX9 Bodypack Digital UHF Wireless Transmitter</p>\r\n', '08022117400260217772f1bff.jpg', 5400, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:40:02', 0, '2021-02-08 17:40:02'),
(701, '', 'Saramonic UWMIC10-TH Set 2 96-Channel Digital UHF Wireless Lavalier Microphone System', 8, 78, '', 'ไมค์โครโฟนไวเลส Saramonic', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>จำหน่ายไมค์วายเลส 2 ตัวส่ง 1 ตัวรับ&nbsp;<br />\r\nSaramonic UWMIC10-TH Set 2 96-Channel Digital UHF Wireless Lavalier Microphone System</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>Saramonic RX10+TX10</strong>&nbsp;UHF Wireless Lavalier Microphone System provides stable, interference free audio in portable, compact and low cost package. This system is a perfect fit for DSLR videography, field recording and interviews, broadcast TV, ENG, providing dependable audio broadcasting and recording.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The system includes a camera-mountable, wireless receiver, wireless body-pack transmitter and clip-on lavalier mic.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Receiver&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Saramonic UwMic10-RX10 is a camera-mountable integrated wireless receiver. It features a wide switching RF bandwidth, an easy-to-read LCD display and infrared synchronization between transmitter and receiver.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipped with an auto-scan function, the RX10 can automatically search for an available transmission frequency. The headphone jack enables real-time monitoring or the receiver via headphones, especially useful for cameras that lack a monitor output.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Transmitter&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This compact transmitter employs a crystal-controlled PLL synthesizer. It is equipped with a muting function and a BMP-type mic input. The RF power output can be switched among high, middle and low.</p>\r\n', '0802211740266021778a646f5.jpg', 16000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:40:26', 0, '2021-02-08 17:40:26'),
(702, '', 'Vacotek Pro300 Wireless HD Video Tranmission ระยะรับ-ส่งสัญญาณ 300 เมตร', 9, 106, '', 'Vacotek', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp; Vacotek Pro300 Wireless HD Video Tranmission ระยะรับ-ส่งสัญญาณ 300 เมตร</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vacotek Pro300 เป็นอุปกรณ์สำหรับใช้รับ-ส่งสัญญาณและข้อมูล วีดีโอภาพและเสียงไร้สายระยะไกลถึง 300 เมตร&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>คุณภาพระดับ Professional input HD-SDI / HDMI 4:4:4 ข้อมูลและสัญญาณวิดีโอที่รับ-ส่ง แบบ Real-Time ไม่มีการบีบอัด มีขนาดเล็ก&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>สามารถติดตั้งกับตัวกล้องได้เลยและยังสามารถใช้แบตเตอรรี่ร่วมกับตัวกล้องได้</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vacotek Pro300 ทำงานในย่านความถี่ 5Ghz.(5.1-5.9GHz.) มีไฟบอกสถานะที่ตัวเครื่อง&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ทั้งตัวส่งและตัวรับ สามารถเลือกความถี่ได้ถึง 10 ช่อง ซึ่งสามารถทำงานพร้อมกันได้ 4 ชุดในพื้นที่เดียวกัน&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>รองรับไฟบ้าน AC&nbsp; และ DC แบตเตอรี่กล้อง รองรับการใช้งานต่อเนื่อง ทนต่อสภาพความร้อน เหมาะสำหรับทีม Production ระดับมืออาชีพ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wireless HD Video System เหมาะสำหรับงาน film production, live broadcasting&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>รองรับ input &amp; output SDI/HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ใช้ความถี่ย่าน 5GHz(5.1-5.9)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>สามารถเชื่อมต่อ Wireless HD Video Transmission ได้ถึง 4 ตัวในพื้นที่เดียวกัน</p>\r\n\r\n<p>รองรับการใช้งานแบบ Point to Point และ Multi Point</p>\r\n\r\n<p>รับ - ส่ง Resolutions 1080p/60Fps 4:4:4 ไม่บีบอัดและไม่มีดีเลย์</p>\r\n\r\n<p>มี LED บอกสถานะการทำงาน ระดับคุณภาพสัญญาณของการเชื่อมต่อ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>รับ-ส่ง ระยะไกลสุดถึง 400 เมตร (ระยะทางในที่โล่ง)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ทนต่อความร้อน ที่อุณหภูมิ -10 ํ ถึง 60 ํ<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/8l/oe/9d.png\" style=\"height:806px; width:570px\" /></p>\r\n', '08022117532360217a93a4512.png', 139000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:53:23', 0, '2021-02-08 17:53:23'),
(703, '', 'CAME-TV Video transmitter Crystal-800', 9, 105, '', 'CAME-TV', '', '<p><strong>อุปกรณ์ส่งสัญญาณภาพและเสียงแบบไร้สาย&nbsp;&nbsp;CAME-TV Video transmitter Crystal-800</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>PRODUCT DETAILS:</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT INFORMATION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAME-TV Crystal-800 is a long range wireless video system that can transmit HD video up to 1080p/60fps at a distance of 800 meters (or 2,600 feet). The unique feature of the Crystal-800 is that the receiver will also create a Wifi SSID that allows you to use an iOS device such as an iPhone, iPod touch, or iPad as a wireless monitor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>Crystal-800</strong>&nbsp;is powered from typical Sony L-Series batteries (i.e. Sony NP-F570, NP-F970, etc). Both the RX and TX have (3) 1/4&quot;-20 threads along the sides and bottom allowing for flexible mounting options.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Up to 1080/60p stream</li>\r\n	<li>800m [2,600 feet] Transmission Distance (Clear LOS)</li>\r\n	<li>Wall Penetration ability 3 cement walls; 1 ferroconcrete wall</li>\r\n	<li>Output Power 25mw-800mw adjustable</li>\r\n	<li>Sensitivity -95dbm&plusmn;2dbm</li>\r\n	<li>Frequency 5G</li>\r\n	<li>Wifi Viewing on iPhone / iPad with APP</li>\r\n	<li>Latency &lt;300ms</li>\r\n	<li>Type A HDMI input on TX (transmitter)</li>\r\n	<li>Type D HDMI Output from RX (receiver)</li>\r\n	<li>Powers off Sony L Series batteries (example: Sony NPF-970) *not included</li>\r\n	<li>DC Input: DC-12V (suggest the output power is more than 12W)</li>\r\n	<li>Transmitter: L.114mm x W. 70mm x H. 25mm [weight] 178g</li>\r\n	<li>Receiver: L.127mm x W. 72mm x H. 28mm [weight] 233g</li>\r\n	<li>Supported Resolutions: 1080p@60/50/30/25/24fps; 720p@60/50/30/25fps (If changing resolutions, restart Device)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/he/6h/wa.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '08022117542060217acc8a9a7.jpg', 26500, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:54:20', 0, '2021-02-08 17:54:20'),
(704, '', 'Vaxis Storm 500+ Wireless Streaming System 200 เมตร', 9, 103, '', 'Vaxis', '', '<p>จำหน่ายอุปกรณ์ส่งสัญญาณภาพและเสียงแบบไร้สาย<br />\r\nNew Arrival - Vaxis Storm 500+ Wireless Streaming System ระยะ 200 เมตร<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.vaxis.cn/upfile/2017/11/20171123183109_399.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hello everyone, we launched Vaxis Storm 500+ few days ago,&nbsp;It&#39;s the most affordable Professional Wireless HD-SDI Video Transmission System for Broadcasters and Filmmakers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;*<strong>Key Features</strong>*</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;1. Wirelessly transmit visually lossless 1080p60 Video/Audio up to 200 meters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;2. TX: SDI In &amp; HDMI In.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;RX: SDI Out x1, HDMI Out x1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;3. Built In HDMI/SDI Converter.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;4. Has 2 stick antennas in transmitter side, and 5 internal antennas in receiver side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;5. Mounting: Transmitter side with Sony NP-970 plate, Receiver side with V mount/ Gold mount plate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;6. Support metadata, timecode, and start/stop flags from many camera manufacturers, including RED, ARRI, Canon, Sony, and Panasonic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;7. Signal indicators for wireless power status, Temperature, Video status and receiver RSSI,useful OLED display and channel setting by tact switch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;8. USB firmware upgrade.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;9. All-metal housing, durable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10.Pure hardware connection; Plug and Play.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '08022117553160217b131f93b.jpg', 56000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:55:31', 0, '2021-02-08 17:55:31'),
(705, '', 'อุปกรณ์สื่อสารไร้สาย Hi-light LHWL005 Video Wireless HDMI/SDI HD Output', 9, 103, '', 'Vaxis', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่ายอุปกรณ์สื่อสารไร้สาย Hi-light LHWL005 Video Wireless HDMI/SDI HD Outpu&nbsp;</strong><strong>Hi-light LHWL005 Wireless HDMI/SDI HD Video Transmission Suite Techspec</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Interface</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;SDI output (BNC,female)</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;HDMI output (Type A,female)</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;DC input</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>Output Video Format</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>HDMI Type A:</li>\r\n	<li>525i, 625i, 720p 50/50.94/60, 1080i 50/59.94/60, 1080p 23.98/24/25/29.9/30/50/59.94/603G/HD/SD-SDI (1x BNC, Auto-Selected):SMPTE-259/274/292/296/372/424/425</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Output Audio FOrmat</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SDI embedded 4-channel 24-bit/48 kH</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Frequency Band&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5.1 to 5.9 GHz, configurable with China, North America, Europe, etc&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Occupied Bandwidth</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>40 MHzSupply Voltage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>-7 to 36 VDC</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Power Consumption</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>&lt;7.5W</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>6.0 x 3.7 x 0.9&quot;(152 x 95 x 23 mm)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Weight</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>12.5 oz (355 g)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '08022117580060217ba87f55f.png', 55000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:58:00', 0, '2021-02-08 17:58:00'),
(706, '', 'Wireless VDO SWIT CW-S150 SDI 150m Wireless System', 9, 103, '', 'Vaxis', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp;SWIT CW-S150 SDI 150m Wireless System</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>WHDI wireless transmission</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SDI 150 meters (LOS)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>CW-S150 wireless system is based on WHDI wireless technology, 5.1-5.9GHz license free bands, DFS comply, , supports uncompressed 3G/HD-SDI to transmit 150 meters (Line-of-Sight) distance, and less than 1 millisecond latency. The system is pure hardware connection, plug and play, which is widely used in director monitoring, drone, ropeway camera, steadicam etc.</p>\r\n', '08022117583560217bcbc7a5a.jpg', 68000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:58:35', 0, '2021-02-08 17:58:35'),
(707, '', 'Vaxis Storm 500+ Wireless Streaming System', 9, 103, '', 'Vaxis', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย Vaxis Storm 500+ อุปกรณ์ส่งสัญญาณภาพและเสียงแบบไร้สายระยะ 200 เมตร</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features*</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;1. Wirelessly transmit visually lossless 1080p60 Video/Audio up to 200 meters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;2. TX: SDI In &amp; HDMI In.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; RX: SDI Out x1, HDMI Out x1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;3. Built In HDMI/SDI Converter.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;4. Has 2 stick antennas in transmitter side, and 5 internal antennas in receiver side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;5. Mounting: Transmitter side with Sony NP-970 plate, Receiver side with V mount/ Gold mount plate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;6. Support metadata, timecode, and start/stop flags from many camera manufacturers, including RED, ARRI, Canon, Sony, and Panasonic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;7. Signal indicators for wireless power status, Temperature, Video status and receiver RSSI,useful OLED display and channel setting by tact switch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;8. USB firmware upgrade.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;9. All-metal housing, durable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10.Pure hardware connection; Plug and Play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/tl/q6/9m.jpg\" style=\"height:2784px; width:564px\" /></p>\r\n', '08022117590260217be660b70.jpg', 56700, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 17:59:02', 0, '2021-02-08 17:59:02'),
(708, '', 'Zoom H4n Pro 4-Channel Handy Recorder', 8, 79, '', 'Microphone Zoom', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่ายเครื่องบันทึกเสียง Zoom H4n Pro 4-Channel Handy Recorder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Adjustable Stereo X/Y Microphone</li>\r\n	<li>Can Record 4 Tracks Simultaneously</li>\r\n	<li>2 x XLR / 1/4&quot; Combination Input Jacks</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm Mic Input with 2.5V Plug-In Power</li>\r\n	<li>28 &amp; 48V Phantom Power</li>\r\n	<li>Record &amp; Play WAV &amp; MP3 Formats</li>\r\n	<li>AD/DA Conversion up to 24-Bit / 96 kHz</li>\r\n	<li>Built-In Metronome and Chromatic Tuner</li>\r\n	<li>2-In/2-Out Interface via USB</li>\r\n	<li>Rubberized Body with Locking XLR Jacks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '08022118000160217c21bdb2f.jpg', 7750, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:00:01', 0, '2021-02-08 18:00:01'),
(710, '', 'Zoom AR-96 AERO RHYTHMTRAK', 8, 79, '', 'Microphone Zoom', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่ายเครื่องให้จังหวะ Zoom AR-96 AERO RHYTHMTRAK<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTHE POWER TO CREATE EVERYTHING ANEW.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ZOOM ARQ AR-96</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>All-In-One Production and Live Performance Instrument</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Music is a voyage of discovery. One that now goes much further with the creation of the&nbsp;<strong>ZOOM ARQ AR-96</strong>&nbsp;Aero RhythmTrak.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The<strong>&nbsp;ZOOM ARQ AR-96</strong>&nbsp;is an all-in-one production and live performance instrument which includes an integrated drum machine, sequencer, synthesizer, looper, and MIDI controller with a built-in accelerometer. Even more, ARQ is freedom. With its wireless Bluetooth&reg; Ring Controller, you can escape the booth, move the music, and get in front of the crowd.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Base Station and Ring Controller</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Base Station</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The AR-96 Base Station houses 468</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>drum/instrument sounds (&quot;one-shot&quot; sampled</p>\r\n\r\n<p>waveform sounds), 70 types of synthesizer sounds,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>and dozens of digital effects. Dual 1/4&quot; line-level</p>\r\n\r\n<p>audio inputs enable phrase recording and looping.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are also stereo 1/4&quot; line-level outputs, as</p>\r\n\r\n<p>well as a dedicated 1/4&quot; headphone jack with its</p>\r\n\r\n<p>own volume control. A USB port allows connection</p>\r\n\r\n<p>to your computer, and an SD card slot lets</p>\r\n\r\n<p>you save patterns and loops, import prerecorded</p>\r\n\r\n<p>audio, and update firmware.</p>\r\n', '08022118014360217c87e6f46.jpg', 22500, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:01:43', 0, '2021-02-08 18:01:43'),
(711, '', 'Zoom MSM-1 Mic Stand Mount for Q4 Handy Video Recorder', 8, 79, '', 'Microphone Zoom', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย Zoom MSM-1 Mic Stand Mount for Q4 Handy Video Recorder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Clamps onto Microphone Stand</li>\r\n	<li>3-Prong Mounting Interface</li>\r\n	<li>Mounts a Zoom Q4 or GoPro Camera</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zoom MSM-1&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Zoom MSM-1 Mic Stand Mount</strong>&nbsp;allows you to mount your Q4 Handy Video Recorder onto a microphone stand to capture unique and exciting angles of musicians in the rehearsal studio or on stage. The camera attaches via a 3-prong mounting interface, which is also compatible with GoPro HERO housings and frames, as well as other cameras that utilize the GoPro-style mount. Additionally, the mount can be used with a Zoom Q8 when paired with a 1/4&quot;-20 to 3-prong adapter.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zoom MSM-1 Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packaging Info</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package Weight 0.5 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Box Dimensions (LxWxH) 7.0 x 4.0 x 2.3&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/it/f7/2y.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '08022118020560217c9dcf658.jpg', 960, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:02:05', 0, '2021-02-08 18:02:05'),
(712, '', 'Zoom SSH-6 Stereo Shotgun Microphone for H5, H6, U-44 and Q8', 8, 79, '', 'Microphone Zoom', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย Zoom SSH-6 Stereo Shotgun Microphone for H5, H6, U-44 and Q8</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mid-Side Recording</li>\r\n	<li>Adjust the Width of the Stereo Image</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain Full Mono Compatibility</li>\r\n	<li>Mix Direct and Ambient Sounds Together</li>\r\n	<li>Location Recording for Film, Video, TV</li>\r\n	<li>Interchangeable Capsule Design</li>\r\n	<li>Includes Professional Hairy Windscreen</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zoom SSH-6 Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>Zoom SSH-6</strong>&nbsp;Stereo Shotgun Microphone Capsule is designed to work with the company&#39;s H5 and H6 audio recorders as well as the hybrid Q8 audio and video recorder and their U-44. The capsule includes a super-directional microphone for picking up sound on center that can be combined with a bidirectional side microphone for picking up sound from the left or right to record a fully mono-compatible stereo image for film, video, and television projects. For example, you can record dialogue with the center microphone and then mix the desired amount of environmental sound captured by the side microphone with the Zoom recorder. A hairy windscreen is included for helping reduce wind noise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zoom SSH-6 Specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Type Mid-side stereo shotgun microphone</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Polar Pattern Hyper cardioid</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compatibility Zoom H5 Recorder</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zoom H6 Recorder</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zoom Q8</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions Not specified by the manufacturer</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight Not specified by the manufacturer</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://fv.lnwfile.com/_/fv/_raw/25/hc/xp.jpg\" /></p>\r\n', '08022118022660217cb2ea504.jpg', 4200, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:02:26', 0, '2021-02-08 18:02:26'),
(713, '', 'Zoom Q8 Handy Video Recorder', 8, 79, '', 'Microphone Zoom', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย Zoom Q8 Handy Video Recorder</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Records up to 2304x1296 Video at 30 fps</li>\r\n	<li>Wide-Angle 160&deg; Lens</li>\r\n	<li>Detachable X/Y Condenser Microphone</li>\r\n	<li>Compatible with Zoom Microphone Capsules</li>\r\n	<li>Dual XLR/TRS Combo Inputs</li>\r\n	<li>Records up to Four Simultaneous Channels</li>\r\n	<li>Record up to 24-Bit / 96 kHz Audio</li>\r\n	<li>2.7&quot; LCD Touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>Doubles as USB Webcam &amp; Audio Interface</li>\r\n	<li>1/4&quot;-20 to Three-Prong Adapter Included</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '08022118030860217cdc7c734.jpg', 13800, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:03:08', 0, '2021-02-08 18:03:08'),
(714, '', 'RODE VideoMic Directional On-camera Microphone', 8, 80, '', 'Microphones Videomic', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย Rode VideoMic with Rycote Lyre Suspension System</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ไมโครโฟน Rode VideoMic มาพร้อมกับ Rycote ป้องกันเสียงรบกวน และ ลดการสั่นไหวในขณะที่มีเคลื่อนที่ สำหรับการใช้งานติดกับกล้องและงานบันทึกเสียง รูปแบบการรับเสียงแบบ Supercardioid&nbsp; ตอบสนองความถี่ 40Hz &ndash; 20kHz,&nbsp; 9V battery power, Impedance 200&Omega;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The VideoMic with Rycote Lyre Suspension System from Rode is a shotgun microphone that can easily be mounted on a DSLR camera. It features a Rycote suspension system that attaches to the camera&rsquo;s shoe. The VideoMic is lightweight, and when mounting on a camera it does not appear in the frame. The VideoMic can also mount to Rode&rsquo;s boompoles for elevated audio capture. Its super-cardioid polar pattern attenuates sounds from the sides. The result is a signal that sounds closer to the camera, even when shooting in noisy environments or at moderate distances.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The included Rycote Lyre is a non-elasticated suspension structure composed of a hard-wearing thermoplastic. It is more effective at acoustically decoupling microphones from unwanted vibrations, handling and cable-borne noise than elasticated suspensions. The lyre remains effective at a wide range of temperatures and is virtually indestructible. It will never wear out, sag, snap or require any rethreading to maintain its effectiveness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An attached, coiled cable terminates to a 1/8&Prime; (3.5mm) mini output connection. The VideoMic features a condenser element that utilizes a standard 9V battery (sold separately). The microphone will run for approximately 100 hours on a single battery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>videomic-rycote</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '0902210241536021f67175d65.jpg', 61000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:04:38', 0, '2021-02-09 02:41:53'),
(715, '', 'RODE NTG1 Shotgun Microphone', 8, 80, '', 'Microphone Shotgun', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp;RODE NTG1 Shotgun Microphone</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Broadcast sound quality</li>\r\n	<li>Low noise circuitry</li>\r\n	<li>Super-cardioid polar pattern</li>\r\n	<li>Condenser transducer</li>\r\n	<li>Rugged metal construction</li>\r\n	<li>Two step High Pass Filter (Flat/80Hz)</li>\r\n	<li>Low handling noise</li>\r\n	<li>Low weight - 105g (3 oz.)</li>\r\n	<li>Includes mic clip, wind shield and zip case</li>\r\n	<li>Ideal for professional applications within the film, video, television and production industries</li>\r\n	<li>10 year extended warranty when you register your microphone</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '0902210247576021f7ddefe86.jpg', 10700, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:05:08', 0, '2021-02-09 02:47:57'),
(716, '', 'RODE NTG2 Multi-Powered Shotgun Microphone', 8, 80, '', 'Microphone Shotgun', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp;RODE NTG2 Multi-Powered Shotgun Microphone</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Broadcast sound quality</li>\r\n	<li>Low noise circuitry</li>\r\n	<li>Condenser transducer</li>\r\n	<li>Rugged metal construction</li>\r\n	<li>Two step High Pass Filter (Flat/80Hz)</li>\r\n	<li>P48 phantom power or AA battery option</li>\r\n	<li>Low handling noise</li>\r\n	<li>Low weight - 161g (5.17 oz.)</li>\r\n	<li>Includes mic clip, wind shield and zip case</li>\r\n	<li>Ideal for professional applications within the film, video, television and production industries</li>\r\n	<li>10 year extended warranty when you register online at www.rodemic.com/warranty</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '0902210244506021f72238dbc.jpg', 11800, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:05:32', 0, '2021-02-09 02:44:50'),
(717, '', 'RODE NTG3 RF-Bias Shotgun Microphone', 8, 80, '', 'Microphone Shotgun', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp;RODE NTG3 RF-Bias Shotgun Microphone</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Superior broadcast sound quality</li>\r\n	<li>High Sensitivity</li>\r\n	<li>Super-cardioid polar pattern</li>\r\n	<li>Designed to withstand adverse environmental conditions</li>\r\n	<li>50% less self-noise than the majority of shotgun microphones</li>\r\n	<li>Extremely low handling noise</li>\r\n	<li>High level of immunity to radio frequency interference</li>\r\n	<li>True Condenser (external RF biased)</li>\r\n	<li>Includes durable aluminium storage cylinder for transport, pop filter, mic clip and large zip pouch</li>\r\n	<li>Designed for professional use on film, television, ENG &amp; wherever high resolution broadcast audio is required</li>\r\n	<li>10 year extended warranty when you register your microphone</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '0902210246286021f7844ca67.jpg', 31300, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:05:58', 0, '2021-02-09 02:46:28'),
(718, '', 'RODE NTG3B RF-Bias Shotgun Microphone', 8, 80, '', 'Microphone Shotgun', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย&nbsp;RODE NTG3B RF-Bias Shotgun Microphone</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Superior broadcast sound quality</li>\r\n	<li>High Sensitivity</li>\r\n	<li>Super-cardioid polar pattern</li>\r\n	<li>Designed to withstand adverse environmental conditions</li>\r\n	<li>50% less self-noise than the majority of shotgun microphones</li>\r\n	<li>Extremely low handling noise</li>\r\n	<li>High level of immunity to radio frequency interference</li>\r\n	<li>True Condenser (external RF biased)</li>\r\n	<li>Includes durable aluminium storage cylinder for transport, pop filter, mic clip and large zip pouch</li>\r\n	<li>Designed for professional use on film, television, ENG &amp; wherever high resolution broadcast audio is required</li>\r\n	<li>10 year extended warranty when you register your microphone</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '0902210236426021f53a79a59.jpg', 31300, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:06:52', 0, '2021-02-09 02:36:42'),
(719, '', 'Vaxis Storm 1000+ , LONG range Quality&Affordable Wireless Transmission Kit', 9, 103, '', 'Vaxis', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่ายอุปกรณ์ส่งสัญญาณภาพและเสียงแบบไร้สาย</strong><br />\r\nอุปกรณ์ส่งสัญญาณภาพและเสียงแบบไร้สายระยะ 300 เมตร&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vaxis Storm 1000+ , LONG range Quality&amp;Affordable Wireless Transmission Kit</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vaxis is proud to announce the introduction of an exciting new player in the world of wireless video devices - Vaxis Strom 1000+</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Longer range, more reliable, and smaller than ever before, the Storm 1000+ is the new standard in LONG range Quality&amp;Affordable zero delay wireless transmission.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Main features:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;1. 1000ft+(300m+) Stable working distance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;2. Video transmission &amp; Audio communication.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;3. Less than 0.001s latency, no compression.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;4. TX: SDI In &amp; Loop out.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;5. RX: SDI Out x2, HDMI Out x1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;6. Signal indicators for wireless power status, Temperature, Video status and receiver RSSI, useful OLED display and channel setting by tact switch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;7. Mounting: Optional Sony U-30 / Canon LP-E6 / Sony NP-970 battery plates.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;8. Time code supported.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;9. USB firmware upgrade.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. All-metal housing, durable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;11. Pure hardware connection; Plug and Play.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '08022118075260217df81882f.jpg', 94000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:07:52', 0, '2021-02-08 18:07:52'),
(720, '', 'COMICA CVM-WM300TX Transmitter เครื่องส่งไมค์ติดกล้องไร้สาย 80 ชาแนล ย่าน UHF', 8, 81, '', 'Wireless COMICA', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย COMICA CVM-WM300TX Transmitter เครื่องส่งไมค์ติดกล้องไร้สาย 80 ชาแนล ย่าน UHF&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>COMICA CVM-WM300TX UHF(794MHz~806MHz)</strong><br />\r\n80-channels Metal Wireless Microphone with One transmitters (Lithium Battery Version) (Coming Soon)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>COMICA CVM-WM300TX เครื่องส่งสัญญาณไมค์ ย่านความถี่ UHF(794MHz~806MHz) 80 ช่องสัญญาณ มาพร้อมแบตเตอรี่รีชาร์ตในตัว</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>เครื่องส่งสัญญาณไมค์ติดกล้องไร้สาย 80 ชาแนล ย่าน UHF ตัวเครื่องผลิตจากเหล็ก มีความแข็งแรงทนทาน มาพร้อมแบตเตอรี่รีชาร์ตในตัวเครื่อง เครื่องส่งสัญญาณไมค์ติดกล้องไร้สาย ส่งสัญญาณด้วยเทคโนโลยี UHF พร้อมกับหน้าจอแสดงผลแบบแอลซีดี(LCD) ที่มีความละเอียดสูง มีช่องสัญญาณให้เลือกใช้งานได้ถึง 80 ช่อง สามารถปรับระดับสัญญาณเสียงได้ถึง 16 ระดับ</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>มาพร้อมฟังก์ชั่น LCF สำหรับกรองเสียงย่านความถี่ต่ำออก</li>\r\n	<li>สแกนเลือกใช้งานช่องสัญญาณความถี่ได้ทั้งแบบออโต้และแมนนวล</li>\r\n	<li>พร้อมระบบซิงโครไนจับคู่ออโต้ผ่านช่องอินฟราเรด</li>\r\n	<li>มีโหมดให้เลือกรับสัญญาณเสียงใช้งานทั้งแบบสเตริโอ/โมโน</li>\r\n	<li>สามารถปรับความแรงของสัญญาณกำลังส่งได้</li>\r\n	<li>มีช่องรับเสียงสัญญาณขาเข้าให้เลือกใช้งานทั้ง ไมค์และออดิโอ</li>\r\n	<li>มอนิเตอร์พลังงานแบตเตอรี่ของเครื่องส่งสัญญาณได้ผ่านหน้าจอแสดงผลของเครื่องรับสัญญาณ</li>\r\n	<li>แสดงระดับความแรง-เบาสัญญาณเสียงผ่านหน้าจอ พร้อมไฟแบคไลท์ส่องสว่างอัตโนมัติขณะปรับตั้งค่าเครื่อง</li>\r\n	<li>มีระบบป้องกันคลื่นสัญญาณรบกวน เหมาะสำหรับงานบอร์ดคลาสและงานการบันทึกวีดีโอทั่วไปที่ต้องการคุณภาพเสียงสูงระดับโปรเฟสชันนอล</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '08022118084360217e2b87370.jpg', 6900, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:08:43', 0, '2021-02-08 18:08:43'),
