(727, '', 'Hollyland Cosmo 400 Wireless transmission HDMI / SDI 120m', 9, 104, '', 'Hollyland', '', '<p><strong>Hollyland Cosmo 400 Wireless transmission HDMI / SDI 120m</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nCOSMO400 เป็นไวเลสภาพคุณภาพสูงที่มีความสามารถรับส่งสัญญาณภาพและเสียงได้ไกลถึง 120 เมตรในที่โล่ง และรองรับอุปกรณ์ทุกชนิดที่มี Port HD-SDI / HDMI รองรับ Resolution สูงสุด 1080/ 60fps หรือต่ำกว่า&nbsp; โดยไม่มีการบีบอัดสัญญาณแต่อย่างใด สามารถทำงานเป็น Splitter ได้ โดย 1 ตัวส่งสามารถเชื่อต่อตัวรับได้สูงสุด 4 ตัว ใช้งานร่วมกับแบตเตอร์รี่&nbsp; SONY Type L โดยแบตรุ่น F970 สามารถใช้งานได้ต่อเนื่อง 8ชม&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Cosmo 400 Wireless HDMI/SDI HD Video Transmission Suite from Hollyland transmits uncompressed 3G-SDI and HDMI video signals at a distance up to 400&#39;, with no compression and zero delay. The suite includes one transmitter and one receiver, with the transmitter providing 3G/HD-SDI and HDMI inputs, and the receiver providing 3G/HD-SDI and HDMI outputs. The wireless HD suite has two stick antennas in the transmitter side, and five stick antennas in the receiver side, and can work in the 5.1 to 5.9 GHz frequency bands. The software can be configured to licensed or for ISM bands of different global regions. The side panel of both transmitter and receiver comes with a frequency selection knob that provides a maximum of 10 workable frequency channels, and supports a maximum of four working sets simultaneously. The receiver is enclosed in an industrial-grade metal case and employs an efficient heat dissipation mechanism for durability and reliability. This suite can accept a wide DC power input range, and is suitable for use with many camera battery models.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximum resolution of 1080p, 60 Hz with no delay and no compression</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AES-128 encryption with air interface HD video data stream</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI and 3G/HD/SD-SDI inputs and outputs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supports point-to-point and point-to-multipoint network topologies</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built-in receiver antenna that is compact in size</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5 GHz ISM frequency band with Wi-Fi and a maximum of 10 frequency channels, selected by user knob</p>\r\n\r\n<p>400&#39; maximum transmission distance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Signal indicators for wireless power status, video status, and receiver RSSI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power voltage input range adapts most kinds of camera batteries</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Input and output ports with &plusmn;8 kV ESD protection level (HBM, contact discharge)</p>\r\n', '08022118121460217efe7bc41.jpg', 42000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:12:14', 0, '2021-02-08 18:12:14'),
(728, '', 'Hollyland Cosmo 600 Wireless HDMI/SDI Transmission System ระยะ 200 เมตร', 9, 104, '', 'Hollyland', '', '<p><strong>จำหน่าย Hollyland Cosmo 600 Wireless HDMI/SDI Transmission System อุปกรณ์ส่งสัญญาณภาพและเสียงแบบไร้สายระยะ 200 เมตร</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>HDMI/SDI Input, SDI Loop, 3.5mm Audio</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI/Dual SDI Outputs</li>\r\n	<li>600&#39; 1080p60 Transmission,</li>\r\n	<li>5.1-5.9 GHz Frequency Band</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>In a lighter, slimmer design than the COSMO 400, the Hollyland COSMO 600 allows you to transmit an HDMI/SDI signal up to 600&#39; to an HDMI or dual SDI outputs. The transmitter/receiver set supports up to 1080p60 signals with a latency of<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The transmitter and receiver both feature an L-series battery plate. Additionally, D-Tap to LEMO cables are included for powering both devices off compatible batteries. The transmitter uses two antennas while the receiver has a built-in antenna. Three highly flexible antennas that are less disposed to accidental damage are supplied for the transmitter, one as a spare, and two mushroom antennas are also provided as replacements for the standard ones.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Transmit up to a 1080p60 HDMI/SDI signal to an HDMI or dual SDI outputs</li>\r\n	<li>600&#39; line-of-sight transmission with</li>\r\n	<li>SDI loop-through out</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm stereo audio input</li>\r\n	<li>5.1-5.9 GHz frequency band</li>\r\n	<li>AES-128 encryption</li>\r\n	<li>OLED screen</li>\r\n	<li>Timecode</li>\r\n	<li>Automatic synchronization with camera recording</li>\r\n	<li>L-series battery plates</li>\r\n	<li>D-Tap to LEMO cables</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '08022118123960217f1755963.jpg', 45000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:12:39', 0, '2021-02-08 18:12:39'),
(729, '', 'Hollyland Cosmo 1000 SDI/HDMI Wireless Video Transmission System ระยะ 300เมตร', 9, 104, '', 'Hollyland', '', '<p>Key Features<br />\r\nHDMI/SDI Input, SDI Loop, 3.5mm Audio<br />\r\nHDMI/Dual SDI Outputs, OLED Screen<br />\r\n1000&#39; Line-of-Sight 1080p60 Transmission<br />\r\n5.1-5.9 GHz Frequency Range</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hollyland Cosmo 1000 SDI/HDMI Wireless Video Transmission System ระยะ 300เมตร</strong><br />\r\n<strong>อุปกรณ์ส่งสัญญาณภาพและเสียงแบบไร้สายระยะ 300 เมตร</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI/SDI Input, SDI Loop, 3.5mm Audio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HDMI/Dual SDI Outputs, OLED Screen</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1000&#39; Line-of-Sight 1080p60 Transmission</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.1-5.9 GHz Frequency Range</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Hollyland Cosmo 1000Plus allows you to transmit an HDMI/SDI signal up to 1000&#39; line-of-sight to an HDMI or dual SDI outputs. The transmitter/receiver set supports up to 1080p60 signals with a latency of &lt;1 ms. The transmitter offers one HDMI and one SDI&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hollyland COSMO 1000 Overview</strong></p>\r\n', '08022118125960217f2bf210c.jpg', 115000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:12:59', 0, '2021-02-08 18:12:59'),
