(738, '', 'โปรเจคเตอร์ Panasonic PT-RW430E LED/Laser Hybrid Projector WXGA 3500 lm', 12, 87, '', 'โปรเจคเตอร์ Panasonic', '', '<p><strong>โปรเจคเตอร์ Panasonic PT-RW430E LED/Laser Hybrid Projector WXGA 3500 lm&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Panasonic PT-RW430E LED/Laser Hybrid Projector WXGA 3,500 lm (Portrait)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>DLP Display Technology</li>\r\n	<li>3500 ANSI Lumens</li>\r\n	<li>Wide XGA Resolution</li>\r\n	<li>20000 hour lamp life (typical)</li>\r\n	<li>20000:1 Contrast Ratio</li>\r\n	<li>3 collect/return with loan if available warranty</li>\r\n	<li>11kg (24.3lb.)</li>\r\n	<li>Scheduling Function</li>\r\n	<li>Wide zoom range for flexible placement</li>\r\n	<li>1080p/24FPS compatible</li>\r\n	<li>3D Projection Ready</li>\r\n	<li>Can Be Installed Vertically</li>\r\n	<li>DICOM Simulation Mode</li>\r\n	<li>Digital (HDMI/DVI) Input</li>\r\n	<li>Edge Blending</li>\r\n	<li>HDCP Compliant DVI</li>\r\n	<li>Lens Shift</li>\r\n	<li>Lens-centred Design</li>\r\n	<li>Native Widescreen</li>\r\n	<li>Network Control</li>\r\n	<li>PIN Code Security</li>\r\n	<li>Portrait Mode</li>\r\n	<li>Quick Power Off</li>\r\n	<li>Quick Power On</li>\r\n	<li>Warrantied for 24/7 use</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '0902210202116021ed23dca30.jpg', 137500, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:18:14', 0, '2021-02-09 02:02:11'),
(739, '', 'โปรเจคเตอร์ Panasonic PT-RZ370U Solid Shine DLP Projector', 12, 87, '', 'โปรเจคเตอร์ Panasonic', '', '<p><strong>โปรเจคเตอร์ Panasonic PT-RZ370U Solid Shine DLP Projector</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Highlights</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Brightness of 3500 Lumens</li>\r\n	<li>Full-HD (1920 x 1080) DLP Chip</li>\r\n	<li>Solid Shine Lamp Free Design</li>\r\n	<li>20,000 Hours of Continuous Operation</li>\r\n	<li>LED/Laser Combined Light Source</li>\r\n	<li>30x Drive Switching</li>\r\n	<li>Heat Pipe Cooling System</li>\r\n	<li>Dust-Resistant Structure</li>\r\n	<li>DICOM Simulation Mode</li>\r\n	<li>Easy Remote Monitoring Over a LAN</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Panasonic PT-RZ370U Overview</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many projector issues have been addressed with the Panasonic PT-RZ370U Solid Shine DLP Projector. From the moment you turn on the projector, you&#39;ll notice the difference with the quick on and immediate full brightness. No more lamps and air filters, which lets you enjoy maintenance-free use for about 20,000 hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Because the PT-RZ370 does not use a lamp, has an efficient cooling system, and uses a DLP chip that has a long life, they are capable of 24/7 operation. The rate of brightness deterioration in the LED/Laser-combined light source is extremely slow compared to lamp based projectors. The Solid Shine drive uses a built-in sensor to constantly detect the light intensity of the light source and correct corresponding changes in white balance. This all helps to maintain picture quality for a long period of time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The PT-RZ370 features 3500 lumens of brightness. Contrast ratio is at 10,000:1, and images are reproduced with a wide dynamic range. The PT-RZ370 features a full-HD (1920 x 1080) DLP chip, allowing highly detailed full-HD images without resizing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To enhance permanent installation use, Panasonic has added Digital Link support so you can transmit video, audio and control signals up to 328&#39; (100 m) over a single LAN cable. System capabilities have also been improved with 2x zoom and an exceptionally wide lens shift range, providing flexibility for easy first time and replacement installations.</p>\r\n', '0902210202186021ed2a2c1bb.jpg', 150000, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:18:38', 0, '2021-02-09 02:02:18'),
(740, '', 'โปรเจคเตอร์ EPSON EB-95 Installation or desktop projector.', 12, 88, '', 'โปรเจคเตอร์ EPSON', '', '<p><strong>โปรเจคเตอร์ EPSON EB-95&nbsp; Installation or desktop projector.</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make education brighter with the Epson EB-95, which gives a super-clear XGA picture, has smart features to enhance lessons and is easy to set up.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Epson EB-95 [240v]</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Project a perfect XGA image, even in daylight, and keep the lights on so students can take notes; Epson&rsquo;s 3LCD technology and a White and Colour Light Output of 2,600 lumens deliver superb clarity in all conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Make lessons more effective:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The powerful 16W integrated speaker helps your students hear clearly, and there&#39;s a handy microphone input - ideal for music lessons. Share 3D objects or science experiments on the big screen by connecting to Epson&rsquo;s ELP-DC06 document camera. You can also share pictures with the class by projecting directly from your USB drive, camera or portable hard drive using the EasyMP slideshow feature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hassle-free installation:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whatever your classroom layout, installing the EB-95 is straightforward. Even if the projector is at an angle to the screen, you can quickly align the picture using automatic vertical and manual horizontal keystone correction. And for desktop use, the projector&rsquo;s pull-out foot supports a tilt angle of up to 16 degrees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Easy control and maintenance:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Control and monitor your projector fleet using Epson&rsquo;s EasyMP advanced networking features. Broadcast image and sound over your network via the LAN input. Save time and hassle by adjusting settings, such as projector on/off times, from a single point on your network. And remove the need for physical checks and free up your IT staff by setting up automatic email alerts for temperature and lamp status.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wide connectivity:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The EB-95 has several connectivity options to suit your needs, including an HDMI input. Connect to your wireless network and present instantly with the optional wireless module and quick wireless connection key. A single USB cable is all that&rsquo;s needed to connect your laptop to the projector thanks to 3-in-1 USB display.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Low TCO:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Helping ease demands on your budget, enjoy the low total cost of ownership resulting from the long lamp life of 6,000 hours (in eco mode) and improved dust filter for a longer maintenance cycle of up to 5,000 hours.</p>\r\n', '0902210158326021ec48b61b3.jpg', 35900, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:19:33', 0, '2021-02-09 01:58:32'),
