(759, '', 'Blackmagic decklink 8k pro', 10, 100, '', 'CAPTURE & PLAYBACK', '', '<p><em><strong>Blackmagic Design DeckLink 4K Pro 12G-SDI Video Capture &amp; Playback Card</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></em><em><strong>Blackmagic Design DeckLink 4K Pro 12G-SDI Video Capture &amp; Playback Card&nbsp;</strong></em>DeckLink capture and playback cards are used every day on Hollywood feature films, episodic television programs, music videos, commercials and more! Featuring the latest cutting edge technologies such as 12G-SDI and 8K support, DeckLink cards give you the highest quality video and work with more applications and platforms than any other card. Every DeckLink PCI Express card can be installed in Mac, Windows and Linux based workstations and servers, giving you ultimate&nbsp;flexibility!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"DeckLink capture cards\" src=\"https://images.blackmagicdesign.com/images/products/decklink/landing/hero-lg.jpg?_v=1510637362\" /></p>\r\n', '0802211835006021845406673.jpg', 25750, 0, 0, '2021-02-08 18:35:00', 0, '2021-02-08 18:35:00');
